NG0569:424: keng rus ri rab mtha' ma lcags ris bskor //
NG0569:425: de lta bu yi gnas de na /
NG0569:426: ro yi tshogs rnams gnas pa ni /
NG0569:427: rlon dang skams dang rul pa dang *//
NG0569:428: gsar dang rnying dang phyed dal dang *//
NG0569:429: bam dang dpungs dang mnam pa dang *//
NG0569:430: rangs pa dang ni stod smad dang *//
NG0569:431: rengs dang rnam par rengs pa dang *//
NG0569:434: langs pa dang ni 'greng ba dang *//
NG0569:435: lhu rdum mgo dang phyed ma dang *//
NG0569:436: keng rus brul dang tshal bu dang *//
NG0569:437: khrag dang rnag dang chu ser dang *//
NG0569:438: zhag dang lha rkang nang rol dang *//
NG0569:439: rgyu ma dri zhen pags pa la //
NG0569:440: ro la 'brad dang gshog pa dang *//
NG0569:442: de lta bu yi dur khrod na //
NG0569:443: 'jig rten yi dwags srog la za ba dang *//
NG0569:444: stag gzig dom dred bya rog kang ka dang */
NG0569:445: byan lag spyang ki khwa 'ug lin du kha //
NG0569:446: srin 'bu la sogs de dag thams cad kyang *//
NG0569:447: sha za khrag 'thung rus pa 'cha' ba dang *//
NG0569:448: ldag nyog byed dang lta dang rgod pa dang *//
NG0569:449: ngu dang cho nges 'debs dang khu cos 'don /
NG0569:450: 'phyong dang rgol dang srog la 'jab pa dang *//
NG0569:451: mig bsgrims lag rjes brgyug pa @#//
NG0569:453: rngam dang srog len bla rku bdud kyang bcod //
NG0569:454: mo la sems 'phyor 'jug cing mngal kyang skems //
NG0569:455: drag po'i rkan rdebs ltas ngan sgra sgrogs dang *//
NG0569:456: gzugs mi sdug dang 'dzum pa'i mdangs ston dang *//
NG0569:457: 'khor lo'i bro brdung lcags kyi mda' 'phen dang *//
NG0569:458: spyugs pa'i glu len mgo yi dung 'bud dang *//
NG0569:459: dar gyi g.yab 'dor rang la rang 'khro dang *//
NG0569:460: sha za khrag 'thung snying 'byin srog gcod dang *//
NG0569:461: lag pa gar bsgyur rdo rje'i thog 'phen dang *//
NG0569:462: gti mug ma sa'i dur khrod ri ltar spungs pa dang *//
NG0569:463: 'dod chags rak+ta'i dur khrod rba glo 'khyil ba dang */
NG0569:464: zhe sdang keng rus dur khrod brag ltar gtam pa dang */
NG0569:465: rab tu 'jigs shing shin tu skyi g.ya' ba /
NG0569:466: las las grub pa'i dur khrod chen por bshad gsang ba'i dur khrod kyi dkyil 'di ltar ste /
NG0569:467: rang rgyud dkyil 'khor drug dag srog shing gsum /
NG0569:468: thig le bcud ldan yi ge'i rnam par ldan //
NG0569:469: rang rang rtsa dang kha dog ye shes gsal //
NG0569:470: yum gyi b+ha ga mkha' dbyings dag pa ru //
NG0569:471: rnam bzhi gnas kyi dkyil 'khor nyi zla'i gdan //
NG0569:472: thig le'i ye shes rol ba'i bde chen sku //
NG0569:473: snang srid ka dag lhun gyis grub par bzhugs //
NG0569:474: de nyid gsang ba bde chen dkyil 'khor bshad //
NG0569:476: des 'khor gyi tshogs thams cad mgu bar gyur te /
NG0569:477: bcom ldan 'das la ngag 'thun par 'di skad ces bstod do //
NG0569:479: mnyam nyid ngang las dreg pa'i skur sprul nas //
NG0569:480: gdug pa can rnams ma lus dbang du bsdus //
NG0569:481: bstan pa gnas phyir 'khor du sprul nas 'gyed //
NG0569:482: don gyi dkyil 'khor chen po ngo mtshar che //
NG0569:483: rdo rje 'chang chen khro bo'i rgyal //
NG0569:484: rnam dag chos sku gnyis med mkha' //
NG0569:485: ye shes rol pas 'jigs pa'i sku //
NG0569:488: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis skye 'gag dang bral ba'i don 'di bstan to //
NG0569:489: skye 'gro ma lus chos sku bde ba'i ngang *//
NG0569:490: ye shes thams cad de yi ngang la rdzogs //
NG0569:491: 'khor ba'i skyon bral bsam yas dpag med sku //
NG0569:492: 'dul ba'i dbang gis sna tshogs sprul pa bstan //
NG0569:494: 'khor thams cad mgu bar gyur te /
NG0569:495: bcom ldan 'das la ngo mtshar brjod de /
NG0569:496: 'gro ba las kyis rmongs pa la //
NG0569:497: 'dul ba'i sku yis las rim bstan //
NG0569:498: bstan pa gnyis med mnyam sbyar bas //
NG0569:499: gdug pa thabs bsgral ngo mtshar che //
NG0569:501: don gyi snying po 'khrul 'khor rin po che rgyal
NG0569:502: mtshan 'phrul gyi me long khri drug stong pa'i rgyud
NG0569:503: las // dkyil 'khor don gyi le'u ste gsum pa'o
NG0569:504: // // de nas nyid kyi thugs las sprul pa'i
NG0569:508: chos sku byang chub sems kyi ngang nyid las //
NG0569:509: 'phags pa'i rgyal po rdo rje 'chang rgyal @#//
NG0569:511: 'gro ba'i don du khro rgyal gshin rje gshed //
NG0569:512: sku gsung thugs kyi 'phrin las mchog bsdus pas //
NG0569:513: mi dge mtshams med dman pa kun bsgrol ba'i //
NG0569:514: las kyi rgyal po sbyor ba smin pa'i mchog / mchong chen gdug pa gnad tshul dregs pa yis //
NG0569:515: yan lag brgya gnyis bzhi dang yang bzhi dang *//
NG0569:516: gzer thun nag po'i dmod pa rgyas par mdzod //
NG0569:518: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsan nas bka' bstsal pa //
NG0569:519: snying po byang chub sems bsdus nas //
NG0569:520: byin rlabs ldan pas gsang bcud bstan //
NG0569:522: 'gro ba ma lus dregs pas myos //
NG0569:523: bstan pa rin chen rgya lam cig / snying po
NG0569:524: 'phrul gyi sbyor pa gcig / lus kyi las sbyor
NG0569:525: brgya phrag brgya // yan lag nyis brgya stong bcu
NG0569:526: drug / 'phra bsgyur bye bas khri phrag gcig /
NG0569:527: bsgrub pa'i dngos gzhi lnga dang gcig / bgrod pa'i
NG0569:529: yan lag sngon dang bcas pa bzhi //
NG0569:530: rten gyi sbyor ba las bcu gnyis //
NG0569:531: 'dren pa'i gsang lam bcu gnyis ldan //
NG0569:532: sgo dgu gsang bcud e ka'i thog / drag po'i sbyor ba bzhi dang stong *//
NG0569:533: dbang gi rim pa lnga dang bcas //
NG0569:535: rang bzhin sprul dang sgrub byed las /
NG0569:536: ye shes ya ma pany+tsa ti /
NG0569:537: las mchog thabs mchog gnyis dang tsa //
NG0569:538: dkar nag las gsang brgya dang bcu //
NG0569:539: gshin rje ma mo mkha' 'gro ging *//
NG0569:540: bdud dang srin po sha za klu //
NG0569:541: smyo byed rgyal po dkar srungs gza' //
NG0569:542: sa bdag sde brgyad srog gcod gnyan //
NG0569:543: rlag byed chu srin mu stegs sri //
NG0569:544: log 'dren 'byung po dur khrod bdag dri za lha gdon drang srong 'byung //
NG0569:545: gnod sbyin gnon po grib gnon shan //
NG0569:546: smyo byed skem byed brjed byed bshed //
NG0569:548: dbugs len drod nyul sha za rngam //
NG0569:549: khyung khra dur bya dur bya 'ug kha rgod lce spyang stag dom wa //
NG0569:550: khyi sbrul bung ba sdig sdom 'bu //
NG0569:551: 'jig rten dregs pa srog dbang 'phrog / thams cad sregs shing las la myos //
NG0569:553: gshin rje gshed kyi dge 'dun kun //
NG0569:555: sbyor ba du ma'i bcas gzhir bshad //
NG0569:556: don gyi snying po 'khrul 'khor rin po che'i rgyal
NG0569:557: mtshan 'phrul gyi me long khri drug stong pa'i rgyud
NG0569:558: las / sbyor ba du ma'i bcas gzhi bstan pa'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o //
NG0569:559: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'gro ba yongs su
NG0569:560: rtog ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas
NG0569:562: bde dang rang bzhin 'brel ba yis //
NG0569:563: snod dang ngang tshul yul du brtag / bde lam gsang sgo dregs pa yis //
NG0569:564: gter sgo yang thog sha za'i srog / mtshon cha'i rgyal po 'khor lo can //
NG0569:565: rten dang grol ba sems dpag med //
NG0569:566: dri med sems kyi rgyan ldan mchog / @#//
NG0569:567: 'joms byed ya ma za yi lus //
NG0569:568: myos bar dug gi sbu dri can //
NG0569:569: dbang po brtan dang rdo rje ma //
NG0569:570: ya ma brtan ma lus srin mo //
NG0569:571: rdo rje snying po stobs dpag med //
NG0569:573: las kyi 'dren pa'i srog lus brgyan //
NG0569:574: dregs pa dbang phyug bde ba'i gnas //
NG0569:575: 'pho ba gsum gyi bdag nyid can //
NG0569:577: bde byed ya ma'i zhing khams nas //
NG0569:578: 'joms byed ya ma ka li'i srog / 'dren pa stobs kyi lam las gzung *//
NG0569:579: rkyen gsum lus gcig brda yis sbyar //
NG0569:580: shes pa gsum bsdus gcig la rten //
NG0569:581: dbye ba'i las ni bcu gnyis brgyad //
NG0569:582: rgyal mtshan rgyud kyi 'phrul dbang bcas /
NG0569:583: rig pa stobs kyi lam dang ldan //
NG0569:584: 'phen pa'i sbyor ba stobs dang sdud //
NG0569:585: rdo rje srin po sbyor ba gcig / 'khor lo rin chen sgyu ma'i gter //
NG0569:586: dbang can bran dang las dbang g.yog / mun khang mtsho gling ya ma'i gnas //
NG0569:587: nam mkha'i rgyal po khams dang chu //
NG0569:588: lo yi dgra dang rang dbang 'joms //
NG0569:589: gsang mchog rlung khams yan lag lus //
NG0569:590: gcod pas mtshon cha gshed dbang sgyur //
NG0569:591: me yis 'jigs pa yang dag skyed //
NG0569:592: las kyis sprod pa'i snying po sa //
NG0569:593: don dang ldan pa'i las sbyangs la //
NG0569:594: las chen thig le nam mkha'i khongs //
NG0569:595: rig pa'i phyag rgya chen po'i stobs //
NG0569:596: snying po gsum la yang dag sdud /
NG0569:597: khams lnga'i dbyibs su bde ba bcud //
NG0569:598: sangs rgyas kun bdag lnga yi ngang *//
NG0569:599: lnga nyid stobs bdag rang gnas mchog / gsang ba'i ri gcan rin chen mdzod //
NG0569:600: mchog gi las dang sbyor ba'i las //
NG0569:601: 'khor lo rgyal po bde ba'i gnas //
NG0569:602: 'phrul gyi snying po gsang ba'i gter //
NG0569:603: gsang ba dbang gis rang rgyas btag / mi mthun lus la gnod byed gdon //
NG0569:604: dus dang len pa'i khams su sbyar //
NG0569:605: yul dang dbang po skye mched la //
NG0569:606: dbab pa'i sbyor ba gcig dang bcas //
NG0569:607: gshin rje nag po bdud dang gshed //
NG0569:608: rang lus phyag rgya'i stobs dang ldan //
NG0569:609: che ba'i thig les dregs pa 'khol //
NG0569:610: zil gnon phyag rgyas kun dbang sdud //
NG0569:611: las kyi phyag rgya dbang rim brtsegs /
NG0569:612: khams gsum 'khor ba'i sems can ni //
NG0569:613: dug lnga'i nad kyis gdungs shing 'khyams //
NG0569:614: de la sngags kyi dmod pa dbab //
NG0569:615: lus la gnag pa'i sdig pa gzhug / gsum bsdus
NG0569:616: dril la yul dbang dbrog / las kyi 'khor ba
NG0569:617: las la mngag / lam sbyangs yul bgrod gnas dang
NG0569:618: sprad // phyag rgya'i lus la gsum gyis brlab //
NG0569:619: sku gsung thugs kyi bde gnas su //
NG0569:623: dri ma gsum dang drug la smin //
NG0569:624: nus pa'i stobs kyis dbang po sdud //
NG0569:625: gcig gi khams dang thams cad sbyar //
NG0569:626: 'du ba nad kyis lus la smin //
NG0569:627: b+ha ga bde ba'i pho brang du //
NG0569:632: bde ba chen po'i gnas phab la //
NG0569:633: sems dang dri ma gnyis bsdus la //
NG0569:634: sa bon dag pa'i dbyings su 'phangs //
NG0569:635: bde ba dang bcas gnas su 'khyil //
NG0569:636: sngags dang mchog las gzi brjid 'bar //
NG0569:637: zhing khams kun spros sbyang bgrod bsdu //
NG0569:638: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bde gnas ldan //
NG0569:641: 'khor lo khro chung stong dpag med //
NG0569:642: dkrugs pas phyag rgya gzhan dbang sgyur //
NG0569:643: lus bcud dngas ma sems dang bral //
NG0569:644: pho brang sgo ru rten bzhi dbral //
NG0569:645: dbus kyi pho brang e la bsdu //
NG0569:646: rdo rje snying po brda yis dkru //
NG0569:647: bde lam bde gnas dgu thog dang *//
NG0569:648: gsang lam rdo rje bgrod lam 'phang *//
NG0569:649: tshul gsum sbyor ba bzhi dang ldan //
NG0569:650: stobs bzhi yan lag bzhi dang ldan //
NG0569:651: be bag ta yi khu ba dang *//
NG0569:652: rdo yis mtsho gling ka 'phangs dang *//
NG0569:653: bde ba gsang mchog rgyal lam bskyed //
NG0569:654: ya ma ka li'i zhing khams nas //
NG0569:656: dbang po snyings ma yul la rol //
NG0569:657: dngas ma'i srog mdangs bde gnas gsal //
NG0569:658: rnyig pa thod pa'i snying por bsdu //
NG0569:659: gsang gsum bde ba'i yul dang sprad //
NG0569:660: don gsum thabs kyis bgrod par bshad //
NG0569:661: don gyi snying po 'khrul 'khor rin po che'i rgyal
NG0569:662: mtshan 'phrul gyi me long khri drug stong pa'i rgyud
NG0569:663: las // brda gsum thabs kyi le'u ste lnga pa'o
NG0569:664: // // de nas ya ma ra dzas gsol ba
NG0569:665: las // // bde chen gsang ba'i 'khor lo mchog / bgrod cing lta ba ji ltar lags //
NG0569:667: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje rngam pa'i rgyal pos //
NG0569:668: gsang ba'i 'khor lo bgrod ba'i thabs 'di gsungs so //
NG0569:669: rig pa sems kyi lta ba ni //
NG0569:670: bde ba'i 'khor lo ye shes can //
NG0569:672: myos pa rten dang dbral ba nyid //
NG0569:673: srog gi dbang po kun bsdus la //
NG0569:674: tshe gnas rdo rje'i lam du sbyang *//
NG0569:675: dbang po rdo rje yul la bstim //
NG0569:676: srog gi rdo rje dbang bsdus la //
NG0569:677: rdo rje srin po'i stobs la bstim //
NG0569:678: rdo rje thig le stobs ldan la //
NG0569:680: nyi ma'i rdo rje las dbang dkrug / brtan pa'i rdo rjes gzir byas nas //
NG0569:682: gnyis ldan rdo rje'i brda yis dbye //
NG0569:683: don gyi rdo rje phyag rgya'i sku //
NG0569:684: dbang po mchog gi rdo rjer 'gyur //
NG0569:685: don ldan rig pa chos sku'i klong *//
NG0569:686: rdo rje'i rgyal po'i bcud sdud dbab //
NG0569:687: rang gnas tshe yi lam du gzud //
NG0569:689: yul gyi dmigs pa rang la gzud //
NG0569:695: b+ha ga sha dz+hu na b+ha la t+hi / @#//
NG0569:696: [(]sah+ye[)]r+b+ha ya ma ra ka sha'i 'bru /[(]la'aho[)]g+ha s+t+ri ra [(]bahahwam[)(]shahwam[)]tri /
NG0569:697: hung lham na na 'u sti ru tra /[ (]saham[)(]kah+yi[)]b+h+ra
NG0569:698: b+hu d+h+ru b+hi lham /[ (]stashri[)(]k+shagra[)(]nyashrahi[)]lha b+ha ska ya d+he
NG0569:699: d+hal d+hum [(]ah+yam[)(]yaam[)]/ sa ga'i sbyor ba tshul gsum sbyar /
NG0569:701: las kyi 'khrul 'khor gnyis dang gcig / ye shes
NG0569:702: 'khrul 'khor gnyis dang gcig / rnal 'byor can la
NG0569:703: gnas bya'i phyir // 'khrul mig drag po 'khrul 'khor gyi //
NG0569:704: rgyu dang tshad dang gzer dang gnad //
NG0569:706: bsnyen dang bsgrub dang las dang gzer //
NG0569:707: dus dang gnas dang rdzas dang thabs //
NG0569:708: phyogs dang blang dang rgod dang 'pho //
NG0569:710: rdzas dang gnas dang rgyu dang thun //
NG0569:712: las dang dngos grub thun mong mchog / lus dang yan lag thabs gnad dang *//
NG0569:713: bde ba smin byed dbang bsdu 'phang *//
NG0569:714: sangs rgyas kun mnyam mthu stobs bdag / rin chen rdo rje sa ma ta //
NG0569:716: me tog mdog ldan bcud phyung ba //
NG0569:717: rtsi thog ma sbyar len dang 'khyams //
NG0569:718: rtsa ba dbang gi 'grod ba'i mchog / mdangs bcas bsgrol ba thabs ldan blang *//
NG0569:719: bcu drug rkyang pa bzhi ldan gcig / mtshon cha'i 'khor lo bde dbang sgyur //
NG0569:720: 'bigs dang gcod la sogs pa'i las //
NG0569:721: bsrungs dang skyob pa kun byed pa'o //
NG0569:722: 'khrul mig drag po gnyis dbang gcig / 'khor lo mi 'gyur brtan pa yi //
NG0569:723: phyag rgya rdo rje sngags kyi gzer //
NG0569:724: mtshon cha'i lo ma spu gri'i gnas //
NG0569:726: gnyis med mthun pa'i las nyid las //
NG0569:727: 'khor lo chos sku phyag rgyar gsal //
NG0569:728: zla ba shar ltar brtan brjid la //
NG0569:731: mtshon cha'i 'khor los rtsa lam gcod //
NG0569:732: sngags kyis 'khor los sreg cing sdud //
NG0569:734: rdo rje 'khor lo bde mchog gsal //
NG0569:735: gsang ba'i 'khor lo gsang bcud len //
NG0569:737: shugs kyis 'khor los rang dang ldan //
NG0569:738: bag chags 'khor lo rten la sdud //
NG0569:739: nag po 'khor lo rten la sdud //
NG0569:740: nag po 'khor lo'i lto bar gzhug / 'byung ba'i 'khor lo stobs kyis mnan //
NG0569:741: gnyis ldan 'khor lo gcig gi ngang *//
NG0569:742: bskul ba'i 'khor ba'i 'khor lo gcig zhing 'bar //
NG0569:743: dmigs pa'i 'khor lo bde bas gang *//
NG0569:745: bde ba'i 'khor lo rtsa lam brgyud //
NG0569:746: gsang ba'i 'khor lo bde bas gang *//
NG0569:747: sa bon 'khor lo las kyi dbab //
NG0569:750: thugs kyi sbyor ba bsam yas mchog / chos sku phyag rgya'i 'os ldan @#//
NG0569:754: thabs dang shes rab gnyis ldan la //
NG0569:755: las kyi 'khor lo sa ra pa //
NG0569:756: gshin rje nag po 'joms pa yi //
NG0569:757: bde ldan 'khor lo brtsegs pa yi //
NG0569:758: pho brang gnas dang sbyar ba'i lus //
NG0569:759: zhi ba'i gnas su las dang sbyar //
NG0569:760: gnyis med sbyor ba'i 'khor lor bshad //
NG0569:761: don gyi snying 'khrul 'khor rin po che'i rgyal mtshan
NG0569:762: 'phrul gyi me long khri drug stong pa'i rgyud las
NG0569:763: / gsang ba'i 'khor lo lta ba'i le'u ste drug
NG0569:764: pa'o // /// de nas bcom ldan 'das rdo rje
NG0569:765: khros pas rang rgyud kyi thig le 'di bshad do
NG0569:766: / // bde ba'i sbyor ba bgrod pa'i mchog / rang rgyud thig le mchod pa'i phul //
NG0569:767: ye shes rol pa mnyes pa'i rgyan //
NG0569:768: bde ba rgyan gyi mchod pa dang *//
NG0569:769: yid 'ong glu yi dbang phyug rtsal //
NG0569:770: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'o //
NG0569:771: las chen sbyor ba'i yul dbang sgrol //
NG0569:774: byin rlabs mchog ldan mchod pa'i mchog / rig pa rang dbang rgyun mi 'chad //
NG0569:775: g.yas nas bde lam bskul lam dbab //
NG0569:776: tshangs pa'i gnas su mchod rgyun 'khril //
NG0569:777: bde chen mchod rgyun lhun mnyam gsal //
NG0569:778: sngags kyi stobs kyi rlung bskul la //
NG0569:779: drod kyi dbang po rtsa lam bzhu //
NG0569:780: rkyen dang ldan pas mchod rgyun 'bebs //
NG0569:781: g.yas nas bskul nas g.yon nas 'bebs //
NG0569:782: rak+ta chags pa'i mchod pa yi //
NG0569:783: g.yon nas bskul nas g.yas nas 'bebs //
NG0569:784: g+hu b+hin dri yi mchod pa yin //
NG0569:785: g.yas g.yon gnyis nas bskul nas su //
NG0569:786: dbu ma'i thig le rgyun shar ba //
NG0569:787: byang chub sems kyi mchod pa yin //
NG0569:788: rtsa gsum bskul nas gang zhing 'bar /
NG0569:789: sna tshogs b+ha ling mchod pa yin //
NG0569:790: rtsa rnams bde bas mdzes gang ba //
NG0569:791: me tog rgyan gyi mchod pa yin //
NG0569:792: ye shes rang gnas 'od gsal ba //
NG0569:794: bskyed pa ha si cir yang g.yo /
NG0569:795: bde ldan sgra yi mchod pa yin //
NG0569:796: thams cad gnyis med ro mnyam gcig / kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa yin //
NG0569:797: ye shes thig le gcig tu 'khyil //
NG0569:798: sbyor ba dbang gi mchod pa yin //
NG0569:799: shes pa gnyis 'dzin rtog bral ba //
NG0569:800: stobs chen shugs bsgrol mchod pa yin //
NG0569:801: rdo rje 'od ldan phyag rgya yis //
NG0569:802: ye shes chen po rang nyams gsal //
NG0569:803: rang gnas thig le'i mchod pa yin //
NG0569:804: lnga rdzogs bde ba gcig tu 'khyil //
NG0569:805: lhun gyis grub pa'i mchod pa yin //
NG0569:806: bdag dbang rdo rje brtan pa'i sku //
NG0569:807: rang byung lnga dang mdzes pa'i ro //
NG0569:808: 'chi med bdud rtsi mchod pa yin //
NG0569:809: mtshan mar mi gnas dbyings su thim //
NG0569:810: gnyis su med pa'i mchod pa yin //
NG0569:811: mchod rgyun don ldan 'grod pa'i mchog / bdag nyid bdag la rol zhing mchod //
NG0569:814: ye shes nyi zla thig le dgug / phyag rgya'i lus la bstam zhing gnas //
NG0569:815: gang yin dbang po legs bskor gzhug / sgo gnyis rtsal sbyangs thig ler bstim //
NG0569:816: yang dang ma la dngas ma bsdu //
NG0569:817: ya tshogs brgyad dang lnga drug gnyis //
NG0569:818: stobs gsum rdo rje'i lam bsgrod nas //
NG0569:819: yang dag bde ba'i gnas su spro //
NG0569:820: bde bas gang nas shes rab bskyod //
NG0569:821: gnyis med phyag rgyas rang gang gsal //
NG0569:822: rgyun dang bde ba'i mchod par rol //
NG0569:823: rdo rje rgyal po bskyod pa yis //
NG0569:825: de ba gu h+ya ra dza la /
NG0569:826: brtan pa'i thig le bzlas pa bya //
NG0569:827: bde ba chen po'i sku la gsal //
NG0569:828: nyon mongs bde ba rang gnas 'bar //
NG0569:829: sgrol ba'i ye shes rang 'bar rtsal //
NG0569:830: sbyor ba sgra yi thig le dbab //
NG0569:831: gshin rje sku yi dbyings su thim //
NG0569:832: ngam gling dgu 'dus rdo rje'i rtse //
NG0569:833: b+ha ga brtsegs pa'i pho brang du //
NG0569:834: 'bru yi dngas ma dril bsdus la //
NG0569:835: phyag rgya chen po'i bstan pas bzung *//
NG0569:836: byin dbang rdo rje ngang gi rdzogs //
NG0569:837: sbyor ba du ma'i skabs kyi brtsam //
NG0569:838: gang 'dod las la thog med 'jug / thun mong mchog gi dgongs par ldan //
NG0569:839: gsang ba'i phyag rgya bgrod par bshad //
NG0569:840: tra tan garba tsakra ma ni rat+na ke du a ta ra she u tra tan tra /
NG0569:841: gsang ba'i thig le lta ba'i le'u ste bdun pa'o //  // gsang ba'i don gyi skabs so //
NG0569:842: de nas yang 'khor gyi nang nas sprul ba'i sku gshin rje'i rgyal po rang gi stan langs te /
NG0569:843: bskor ba lan brgya phrag stong du byas te /
NG0569:844: thal mo sbyar pus mo'i lha nga sa la btsugs nas /
NG0569:845: rdo rje 'chang chen po la gsol ba /
NG0569:846: kye ho bcom ldan rdo rje 'chang */
NG0569:847: sku gsung thugs kyi longs spyod rdzogs //
NG0569:848: 'jam dpal nag po khro chen gyi //
NG0569:849: bsnyen pa'i gleng gzhi sngon 'gro gang *//
NG0569:850: dngos nyid las rims bya thabs tshul //
NG0569:851: 'khor la rgyas par mdzad du gsol //
NG0569:853: de bzhin gshegs pa khro bo'i rgyal po rdo rje snying pos bka' bstsal pa /
NG0569:854: ye shes bsnyen pa'i gleng gzhi ni //
NG0569:855: bgrod pa'i rim pas sngon 'gro brtsams //
NG0569:856: zhi ba'i ting 'dzin sbyor ba las //
NG0569:857: khro bo'i rgyal po gshin rje gshed //
NG0569:858: myos par bya ba'i lus la gdon //
NG0569:859: 'khor lo brgya phrag sbyor ba gcig / rim pa du ma las kyi gnad //
NG0569:860: yan lag rgyan gyi 'khor lo gsum /
NG0569:861: rdo rje srin po las mon gshed //
NG0569:862: khro ba'i rgyal po yang dag gzud //
NG0569:863: dbang gi gnas su phyag rgyar 'bar //
NG0569:864: de dag rgyas pa 'di lta ste //
NG0569:865: sku gsung thugs khro mi bzad pa //
NG0569:866: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi yab //
NG0569:867: zhi khro rab 'byams rang bzhin dpal //
NG0569:868: gdul bya drag phyir shin tu khros //
NG0569:869: che btsan drags pa bran du 'khol //
NG0569:870: tshe yi dngos grub thob 'dod pas //
NG0569:871: phyi dang nang dang gsang ba yi //
NG0569:872: bgrod pa'i rim pa rdzogs par bya //
NG0569:873: sems nyid ye shes 'od gsal zhing *//
NG0569:876: chos sku chen po'i rol bsam yas //
NG0569:877: nyi shu lnga yi bdag nyid la //
NG0569:878: gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs pas //
NG0569:879: 'jam dpal gshed kyi gnas mchog ni //
NG0569:880: ngam ri brag nag gnam lcags 'dar //
NG0569:881: sog po khros 'dra srin mdung rtse //
NG0569:882: ngam grog g.yang sa skyi g.ya' 'jigs //
NG0569:883: gu 'dus mi ro gsar rnying yod //
NG0569:884: sha zan srog gcod 'dab chags ling *//
NG0569:885: gcan gzan gdug pa 'drim zhing gnas //
NG0569:888: lho ru kha ltas gnag la gzir //
NG0569:889: gnas der gshin rje gshed po gnyen //
NG0569:890: sems kyi chos nyid ma bcos la //
NG0569:891: de bzhin nyid kyi blo bzhag ste //
NG0569:892: gnyis med rtsol bral ngang nyid dang *//
NG0569:893: dpa' bos yun ni ring du gnas //
NG0569:894: de ma yin pa'i gang zag gis /
NG0569:895: dus gsum phyogs bcu'i bdag nyid can //
NG0569:896: 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa' yis //
NG0569:897: thun mong ma yin mtshan dper ldan //
NG0569:898: nyi zla'i tshul sgom thig le grang *//
NG0569:899: shes rab pha rol phyin ma yis //
NG0569:900: gsung gi thig le yang dag bsgrags //
NG0569:902: glu yi mtshan rnams yang dag brjod //
NG0569:903: de sogs mdo sde ci nus bgrangs //
NG0569:904: sku yi phyag rgya sna tshogs bzhengs //
NG0569:905: srog gdon skyabs dang sbyin pa bsgye //
NG0569:906: sbyin gtor phyi mchod dag par bya //
NG0569:907: sku gsung thugs kyi las rdzogs nas //
NG0569:908: sa blang sbyang brtsig dngos la 'jug / 'don yon mchod pa lnga dang gtor ma gsum //
NG0569:909: chang phud rin chen sman dang 'bru sna tshogs //
NG0569:910: bshams la dkon mchog gsum po dang *//
NG0569:911: rgyal po bzhi dang gtsang rigs sde brgyad 'khor //
NG0569:912: sa bdag sa srin yi dwags dang *//
NG0569:913: lha mo bstan ma bgegs kyi rigs //
NG0569:915: mnyes shing mgu bar bya ba'i phyir //
NG0569:917: byin gyis brlabs te tshim gyur na //
NG0569:918: gnas mchog chen po'i sa phyogs 'dir //
NG0569:919: rnal 'byor dam ldan dpa' bo bdag / gshin rje gshed chen khro rgyal gyi //
NG0569:920: gsang ba'i dngos grub len byed pa //
NG0569:921: lha klu bgegs chen khyed rnams la //
NG0569:922: sa slong las kyi grogs 'chol gyis //
NG0569:924: bar chad ma byed grogs stong gyis //
NG0569:925: sangs rgyas bstan pa yun du srung *//
NG0569:926: dam las ma 'da' zhes brjod do //
NG0569:927: bdag nyid khro chen thugs kha nas //
NG0569:928: thig le ye shes rol pa las //
NG0569:929: 'byung ba'i snying po rnam gsum gyis //
NG0569:930: 'phros pas sa gzhi bsregs stor dkrug / don dam stong nyid ngang du gnas //
NG0569:931: de nas rgyud la man+dal rtsig / khro bo'i nga rgyal phyag rgya che //
NG0569:932: rdo rje 'gros dang gar gyi bskor //
NG0569:933: de nas mtshams gsum dang po gcod //
NG0569:934: rgyang grags phyogs mtshams bzhi gnyis su //
NG0569:935: mtho brgyad rang rang gtsang rigs mgon //
NG0569:936: de nang phyogs bzhir tho chen bzhi //
NG0569:938: chen sde bzhir mnga' yang gsol //
NG0569:939: mchod yon gtor ma byin nas kyang *//
NG0569:940: bar chod byed pa'i dam sri kun //
NG0569:941: mtshams kyi nang du shor ra re //
NG0569:942: phyogs mtshams srung ba'i las mdzod cig / nang nas dngos grub nyams pa re //
NG0569:943: zhes brjod las kyi gnyer gtad bya /
NG0569:944: de nas nang du+u ra sogs sam //
NG0569:945: khyi sogs sa 'dzul sogs pa la //
NG0569:946: bar chod dam sri logs 'dren gyis //
NG0569:947: ming gzugs snying po stobs bcus bri //
NG0569:948: phag thod dang bcas them 'og dang *//
NG0569:949: lam chen rgya gram srang du mnan //
NG0569:950: khro rgyal gshed kyi stobs kyis gzir //
NG0569:951: sngon du 'gro ba'i rim par bshad //
NG0569:952: don gyi snying po 'khrul 'khor rin po che'i snying po khri drug stong pa'i rgyud las /
NG0569:953: sngon du 'gro ba'i le'u ste brgyad pa'o ///
NG0569:954: / de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis gsang bdag gnad
NG0569:955: kyi phyag rgya zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la
NG0569:956: zhugs nas / ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NG0569:957: ting 'dzin sbyor ba'i nyams ldan pa //
NG0569:958: rang rig sems kyi sgron ma 'bar /
NG0569:959: phyi rol yul la rten mi gzung *//
NG0569:960: dbang phyug khro bdag gshed kyi gzo //
NG0569:961: dbyings phyug ro langs gsang ba'i yul //
NG0569:962: thugs khar thugs mchog yab yum gnas //
NG0569:963: yan lag gshed po yum dang bcas //
NG0569:964: de bzhin gnas su phyogs skyong 'bar //
NG0569:965: bu ga thar byed yab dang yum //
NG0569:966: stod smad tshigs la sgrol ba'i ging *//
NG0569:967: ba spu bu ga las grub mon //
NG0569:968: sprul pa yang sprul dpag tu med //
NG0569:969: mdun rgyab lta zur sgo srungs ma //
NG0569:970: ye shes stobs ldan rol pa 'phro //
NG0569:971: gsang gnas khyams dang sbu gu dang *//
NG0569:972: za ma tog dang ge sar la //
NG0569:973: phyag rgya rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor gsal //
NG0569:974: ha si bde sgra sngags kyi tshig / thig le 'phro 'du byin dbang sdud //
NG0569:975: bde ba'i ye shes mchod pa'i phul //
NG0569:976: sman pa rang gi dbang po la //
NG0569:977: rim pa las kyi gnad chen bskor //
NG0569:978: bdud sgor rten zhal 'chi bdag gshed //
NG0569:979: tshangs pa'i gnas su chos rgyal rngam //
NG0569:980: dran po'i dbang po 'chi bdag rgyal //
NG0569:981: dregs pa'i ngag lam lto pa nag / srid pa'i rten tsar me dbal gcod //
NG0569:982: gsang ba dgu khri sa ta las //
NG0569:983: de bzhin gnas su sha za bdud //
NG0569:984: ba spu bu ga me mtshon 'bar //
NG0569:985: bdag nyid chen po'i dkyil 'khor la //
NG0569:986: ye shes 'khor lo de nyid dbab //
NG0569:987: thabs dang shes rab sprul pa 'gyed //
NG0569:988: rol pa rjes mthun cho gar ldan //
NG0569:989: rang 'byung ye shes lha bsnyen mchog / thig le rol pa me mtshon thogs //
NG0569:990: sreg gcod sgrol ba'i ngar dang ldan //
NG0569:991: dbugs kyi rta zhon yul la bskyod //
NG0569:992: bskyod bskul las kyi bsnyen pa mchog / dman pa dngos nyid ling ga la //
NG0569:993: dregs pa gtum chen mtshon dpal ngar //
NG0569:994: shing sring bzhin du bsad pa'i mchog / las gsum rdzogs pa'i thugs su bshad //
NG0569:995: ta tan ga rba tsakra ma ni rat+na ke d+hu a ta ri sha u kram tan tra las /
NG0569:997: dgu pa'o //  // sngon 'gro thabs kyi skabs so //
NG0569:998: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis bsnyen pa dngos kyi sbyor ba 'di bshad do //
NG0569:999: rten gyi gnas der las gzugs pa //
NG0569:1000: rabs chad nag po'i khang pa dang *//
NG0569:1001: g.yul bkye sa dang mi phung shul //
NG0569:1002: ri rgod 'gram dang thal chen dang *//
NG0569:1003: de dag rgyu la man+dal cig / khru bzhi rgya la dbangs khru gang *//
NG0569:1004: mi rta'i snying khrag btsan dug dang *//
NG0569:1005: bdud rtsi lnga yis chag chag gdab //
NG0569:1006: ba su srad bu rak+ta'i tshal //
NG0569:1007: gsang ba yum gyi mkha' las dgye //
NG0569:1008: thig g.yon mtshan ldan bar nas dra //
NG0569:1009: thig gdab byin ldan rdul tshon bri //
NG0569:1010: nri rangs su yi sbyor ba yis //
NG0569:1011: rak+sha dug shing nyung lim lo /
NG0569:1012: kha dog lnga ldan ye shes brlab //
NG0569:1013: gzugs brnyan 'bar ba yongs la snang *//
NG0569:1014: gsang mdzod dgu ldan pho brang mchog / dbus mthing zla khams bzhi 'khor lo //
NG0569:1015: de bzhin 'khor lo dmar nag sngo //
NG0569:1016: gru chad mtsho gling ngam gling khrag / sgo khyud bzhi yi 'khor lor bcas //
NG0569:1017: phyi yi bar khyams de bzhin sgo //
NG0569:1018: phyogs kyi kha dog rab tu 'bar //
NG0569:1021: sprul pa'i 'khor lo dgu gnyis ldan //
NG0569:1022: bar khyams gru chad sgo khyud gnyis //
NG0569:1023: dkyil 'khor gru bzhi bzhi ldan bya //
NG0569:1024: bam chen ma he nyi zla dregs //
NG0569:1025: rtsa ba'i gdan stengs gzhan ro rkyang *//
NG0569:1026: zhing rgyan bla re thod sprul bcas //
NG0569:1027: 'phring ba g.yer ka dra phyed dar //
NG0569:1028: 'dod yon lha mo don rnams bsam //
NG0569:1029: dbus la sogs pa'i go rims bzhin //
NG0569:1030: de la gnas pa'i rim pa ni //
NG0569:1031: gshed bdag gtso bo yab dang yum //
NG0569:1032: gshed pho bdud mo bzhir ldan bcas //
NG0569:1033: mu khyud dang por dgod par bya //
NG0569:1034: gnyis pa 'khor lo'i rim pa la //
NG0569:1035: phyogs skyong yab yum bcas pa dgod //
NG0569:1036: bar chod gshed kyi bdud rnams kun //
NG0569:1037: gong nas 'dus pa'i tshul du dgod //
NG0569:1038: gsum pa 'khor lo'i rim pa la //
NG0569:1039: sgrol ba'i ging chen bco brgyad dang *//
NG0569:1040: ging mo bco brgyad bka' nod tshul //
NG0569:1041: khrag mtsho ro langs lce spyang rngam //
NG0569:1042: bar khyams nang gi 'khor lo la //
NG0569:1043: thar byed yab yum brgyad gnyis rngam //
NG0569:1044: sgo khyud sgrod byed 'khor lo la //
NG0569:1045: ya ma bstan ma la sogs dgod //
NG0569:1046: phyi yi bar khyams snam bu la //
NG0569:1047: mon pa mon mo las kyi gshed //
NG0569:1048: bdun bdun gnyis gnyis gnyis bcu brgyad //
NG0569:1049: yang sprul drug khri drug stong gnas //
NG0569:1050: sgo bzhi sgo srungs bse mo bzhi //
NG0569:1051: rten bzhi gnas kyi 'khor lo la //
NG0569:1052: rten pa lha yi 'khor lo brtan //
NG0569:1053: ye shes byin rlabs stobs ldan bya //
NG0569:1054: rjes su mthun pa'i chos gar ldan //
NG0569:1055: rten rdzas gnyis dang mchod rdzas dgram //
NG0569:1056: rgyan rdzas rol rdzas gtor ma khrag / dur khrod
NG0569:1057: rdzas la rdzas dgus byug / gshin rje gshed kyi
NG0569:1058: phyag rgya bzhengs // rab gnas byin ldan lha tshogs dgram //
NG0569:1059: sa gsum la sogs bdud rtsi khrag / sbyong bgrod dang ldan phyag @#//
NG0569:1061: dbang bskur mchod bstod lho ru dgram //
NG0569:1062: dmug chen dmug chung bdud rtsi bcud //
NG0569:1063: mtshan dang ldan pa'i ka pa lar //
NG0569:1064: steng 'og phyag rgya'i yab yum dgod //
NG0569:1065: sku gsung thugs kyi thig ler ldan //
NG0569:1066: mthing nag dang bcas ru sprod gdab //
NG0569:1067: phyi yi mchod pa go rims bzhin //
NG0569:1068: nang gi mchod pa bdud rtsi phung *//
NG0569:1069: rak+ta sna mangs thod par sbyar //
NG0569:1070: dpal gyi gtor ma sna tshogs dbul //
NG0569:1071: sras mchog gtor ma sha khrag lho //
NG0569:1072: las kyi ya ma'i gtor ma shar //
NG0569:1073: ma mo mkha' 'gro drug gtor byang *//
NG0569:1074: ging bdud mon gyi gtor ma nub //
NG0569:1075: zhing chen zhing chung bla ri 'phan //
NG0569:1076: rgyu ma'i zhags pa thod pa'i 'phreng *//
NG0569:1077: mchog chen gling bu ltag sprod rnga //
NG0569:1078: ban d+ha'i cha lang keng rus rgyan //
NG0569:1079: bsur chen dud pa sha chen cal //
NG0569:1080: tsit+ta'i pho long khrag gi mtsho //
NG0569:1081: phyogs bcu khor yug sbrin du gtibs //
NG0569:1082: gri lcags mchog dang seng ldeng skyer //
NG0569:1083: phur pa rtsang bcas rang rang grangs //
NG0569:1084: dbus la sogs pa'i gdan la 'god //
NG0569:1085: zla ba dgun 'bring nya la gdams //
NG0569:1086: yang na gshin rje gshed nyid kyis //
NG0569:1087: zla ba zhag dus snying la rab //
NG0569:1088: de bzung yon tan 'phel bar bshad //
NG0569:1089: don gyi snying po 'khrul 'khor rin po che'i rgyal
NG0569:1090: mtshan 'phrul gyi me long khri drug stong pa'i rgyud
NG0569:1091: las / bcas bzhi rtsa ba'i le'u ste bcu pa'o //
NG0569:1092: de nas yang rdo rje khros pa'i rgyal pos sngon du 'gro ba'i don 'di gsungs so //
NG0569:1093: mnyam nyid dag pa'i ye shes las //
NG0569:1094: mkha' dkyil nyi shar brdal pa bzhin //
NG0569:1095: bdag nyid gshed chen gar gyi sku //
NG0569:1096: thugs kyi snying po ring du bskul //
NG0569:1098: snang srid bde 'chang de bzhin nyid //
NG0569:1099: sprin ltar rngam sgra phyogs bcur g.yo //
NG0569:1100: de bskul me ri mtshon char 'khrigs //
NG0569:1101: khro bo 'bar bcas gtum rngam bltams //
NG0569:1102: log 'dren dam sri rdul du brlag / skrag cing bar mtshams phyogs bcu bsrungs //
NG0569:1103: chos rnams stong nyid rtogs dang bral //
NG0569:1104: dmigs med rang bzhin byang chub sems //
NG0569:1105: mkha' ltar mnyam pa chos kyi dbyings //
NG0569:1106: skye 'gag bral ba'i ngang nyid las //
NG0569:1107: yod pa ma yin med pa min //
NG0569:1108: stong pa nyid las cho 'phrul byung *//
NG0569:1109: de nyid ye shes rol pa'i dbyings //
NG0569:1110: sems nyid ngang las g.yo ba med //
NG0569:1111: sems kyi rol pa snang nga yang *//
NG0569:1112: sprin dang 'ja' tshon khu rlangs bzhin //
NG0569:1113: ye shes sgyu ma'i rang bzhin las //
NG0569:1114: dngos po skye ba nyid kyis stong *//
NG0569:1115: chos rnams thams cad thig ler 'dus //
NG0569:1116: thig le rol ba'i byin rlabs las //
NG0569:1117: dug gsum sbyong ba'i 'phreng ba gsum //
NG0569:1118: sreg sbyangs sel ba'i rang bzhin las //
NG0569:1119: thabs dang shes rab mtshan mar 'bar //
NG0569:1120: gnyis med ga bur nyon mongs lnga //
NG0569:1121: gnas bdag yon tan lhun grub pa'i //
NG0569:1122: 'phreng ba rin chen rim par brtsegs //
NG0569:1123: rkyen dang ldan pas 'byung ba'i rim //
NG0569:1126: rang shar mtshan ma gzhal yas khang *//
NG0569:1128: rjes mthun cho gas rdzogs pa'i sku //
NG0569:1129: rkyen ldan yab yum phyag rgya che //
NG0569:1131: thig le dbyibs ldan mkha' la 'phro/ /de las dkyil 'khor gsal bar snang *//
NG0569:1132: bdag nyid thig le'i rnam pa de //
NG0569:1133: gtso chen thugs kyi sgo nas zhugs //
NG0569:1134: sku yi dbyig tu bdag gyur te //
NG0569:1136: cho 'phrul gsum ldan phyag rgya yis //
NG0569:1137: dkyil 'khor bdag nyid sras mchog nyid //
NG0569:1138: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor bcas //
NG0569:1139: dbyings nas rang bzhin shugs kyis bskyod //
NG0569:1140: rang snang dkyil 'khor dbyer med mnyam //

NG0569:1508: chos dbyings 'og min phyogs bcu'i zhing khams na //
NG0569:1509: skye mched chos sku longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NG0569:1510: sprul sku chos nyid dge 'dun sras bcas la //
NG0569:1511: lus ngag yid gsum dang bas phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0569:1512: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod sprin rgya chen po //
NG0569:1513: dngos sbyor yid kyi rnam srul 'jig rten bkang *//
NG0569:1514: sku gsum lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas thams cad du //
NG0569:1515: byang chub sems sogs kun la rgyas par 'bul //
NG0569:1516: 'dod chags la sogs nyon mongs dbang gis na //
NG0569:1517: lus ngag yid kyis sdig pa ci bgyis pa //
NG0569:1518: thams cad sku gsum rdo rje'i bde gshegs dang *//
NG0569:1519: byang chub spyan sngar ma lus bshags par @#//
NG0569:1521: phyogs bcu dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad du //
NG0569:1522: byang chub sems dpa' dag dang 'gro ba yi //
NG0569:1523: rgya chen rab zab bsod nams dge ba'i tshogs //
NG0569:1524: de dag kun gyi rjes su bdag yi rangs //
NG0569:1525: phyogs bcu 'jig rten bsam yas dpag med na //
NG0569:1526: sku gsung rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ji snyed cig / bzhugs shing mnyam bzhag 'gro 'dul de dag la //
NG0569:1527: chos kyi 'khor lo bla med bskor bar bskul //
NG0569:1528: dus gsum bde gshegs mya ngan 'da' bzhed pa //
NG0569:1529: de dag kun la bdag gis thal sbyar te //
NG0569:1530: 'gro ba'i don du bskal pa dpag med du //
NG0569:1531: bzhugs shing thugs rjes don mdzad gsol ba 'debs //
NG0569:1532: skye med ngang las ye shes skur ston cig / thugs rje chen pos kun la khyab mdzad pa'i //
NG0569:1533: dpa' bo bdud 'dul sangs rgyas thams cad la //
NG0569:1534: byang chub bar du bdag ni skyabs su mchi //
NG0569:1535: phyag 'tshal mchod dang sdig pa bshags la sogs //
NG0569:1536: dge ba gzhan gyis de dag thams cad kun //
NG0569:1537: bla med byang chub chen po thob bya'i phyir //
NG0569:1538: bdag gis yang dag yongs su bsngo bar bgyi'o //
NG0569:1539: de ltar sngon du 'gro ba yis //
NG0569:1540: lam gyi yan lag brgyad rdzogs bya'o //
NG0569:1541: 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa' rtog pa'i rgyal po khri drug stong pa'i rgyud chen po las /
NG0569:1542: yan lag brgyad kyi le'u ste sum brgya tham pa'o //  // de nas rdo rje 'chang rgyal pos //
NG0569:1543: lam gyi sbyor ba 'di bshad do //
NG0569:1544: nga ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NG0569:1545: ye shes yin te thugs la gnas //
NG0569:1546: de yi mtshan gyi gdon thabs la //
NG0569:1547: gang zag mos pa tha dad phyir //
NG0569:1548: bsam gyis mi khyab pa yod kyang *//
NG0569:1549: mdor bsdus rnam pa gsum yin te //
NG0569:1550: dbang po rab kyis brjod pa ni //
NG0569:1551: mi rtog ye shes bltas te gdon //
NG0569:1552: dbang po 'bring gi brjod pa ni //
NG0569:1553: gsang sngags tshul du bltas te gdon //
NG0569:1554: dbang po tha mas mtshan brjod pa //
NG0569:1555: che ba'i yon tan bltas te gdon //
NG0569:1556: de gsum thabs gyi sngon du ni //
NG0569:1557: khrus bya ba dang sems skyed dang *//
NG0569:1558: dam tshig sdom pa gzung bar bya //
NG0569:1559: de dag rgyas pa 'di dag ste //
NG0569:1560: khrus la phyi nang gnyis yin te //
NG0569:1561: phyi khrus chu gtsang dri zhim btsas //
NG0569:1562: dang po'i sangs rgyas rnal 'byor gyis //
NG0569:1563: chu nang zla stengs a dkar bsam //
NG0569:1565: 'od du zhu bas dri ma'i tshogs //
NG0569:1566: ma lus bar ni dag par gsam //
NG0569:1567: lhag ma dzam+b+ha la la sbyin //
NG0569:1568: nang khrus bdag med rnam dag la //
NG0569:1569: lhag par mos pa'i bsam pa'o //
NG0569:1570: sems skyed pa yi sbyor ba ni //
NG0569:1571: ye shes lnga dang snying rje gsum //
NG0569:1572: bsgoms pas mngon par byang chub pa'o //
NG0569:1574: snang ba'i chos rnams ma lus kun //
NG0569:1575: snang ba rang bzhin med pa yi //
NG0569:1576: sgrib med ye shes chen por gsal //
NG0569:1577: dper na me long gzugs brnyan bzhin //
NG0569:1578: sna tshogs snang yang dngos ma grub //
NG0569:1582: de ltar chos kun dngos med pas //
NG0569:1583: gcig dang du mar bral ba yis //
NG0569:1584: rang bzhin stong nyid chen po la //
NG0569:1585: mtshan mar grub pa yang dag med //
NG0569:1586: dper na nam mkha' dngos med bzhin //
NG0569:1587: skye med rtag dka' 'dus ma byas //
NG0569:1588: rang bzhin dag pa'i chos de la //
NG0569:1589: bzang ngan che chung ye nas med //
NG0569:1590: phyogs dang ris med mtha' dbus med //
NG0569:1591: mngon sum mi gnas kun la snyoms //
NG0569:1592: mnyam pa nyid kyi snying po la //
NG0569:1593: rim par bkod pa ye nas med //
NG0569:1594: de ltar rab tu gsal bar bsgoms //
NG0569:1595: chos rnams so so'i mtshan nyid kyang *//
NG0569:1596: ma 'dres sna tshogs rnam par snang *//
NG0569:1597: de yang sgrib med rang gsal ba //
NG0569:1598: thams cad mkhyen pa'i rig pa nyid //
NG0569:1599: bye brag sna tshogs rnam pa yang *//
NG0569:1600: rtags na rig pa'i ye shes nyid //
NG0569:1601: de las gzhan pa'i chos med bsgoms //
NG0569:1602: lam dang 'bras bu la sogs te //
NG0569:1603: yon tan bya ba'i 'dod don rnams //
NG0569:1604: ma btsal lhun gyis grub pa yi //
NG0569:1605: rang rig snying po sgrib med de //
NG0569:1606: 'gro don shugs la grub par byed //
NG0569:1607: ma 'khrul rdzogs pa'i rang bzhin bsgom //
NG0569:1608: de ltar ye shes lnga bsgoms nas //
NG0569:1609: snying rje rnam par gsum bsgom pa //
NG0569:1610: ma rig rgyu la log rtog rkyen //
NG0569:1611: des bskyed sdug bsngal phung bor smin //
NG0569:1612: mgon med 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor phyin //
NG0569:1613: sems can de dag sdug bsngal las //
NG0569:1614: thar par bsgral te don bya sbyor //
NG0569:1615: chos rnams bdag med stong pa nyid //
NG0569:1616: rang bzhin dag pa'i mtshan nyid las //
NG0569:1617: chos kun gzhan med de bzhin nyid //
NG0569:1618: de rtogs mnyam pa nyid du sbyor //
NG0569:1619: bdag dang gzhan du dbyer med pas //
NG0569:1620: don bya snying rje'i yul dngos med //
NG0569:1621: dmigs med rang bzhin yongs dag pa'i //
NG0569:1622: rang bzhin dag pa'i chos nyid bsgoms //
NG0569:1623: sdom pa bzung ba'i rim pa ni //
NG0569:1624: sku gsum sangs rgyas thams cad dang *//
NG0569:1625: byang chub sems dpa' chen por bcas //
NG0569:1626: dus 'di nas ni dgongs su gsol //
NG0569:1627: bdag ni byang chub snying po la //
NG0569:1628: nam zhig gnas kyi bar dag tu //
NG0569:1629: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed kyi //
NG0569:1630: rang bzhin dag pa'i chos nyid de //
NG0569:1631: dngos po med pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NG0569:1632: stong nyid de bzhin nyid dbyings las //
NG0569:1633: de bzhin rigs mchog sdom pa gzung *//
NG0569:1634: 'dus ma byas pa'i byang chub sems //
NG0569:1635: skye 'gag med pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
NG0569:1636: dbyer med rnam rtog kun 'joms pa //
NG0569:1637: rdo rje rigs mchog sdom pa gzung *//
NG0569:1638: mnyam pa nyid kyi rang bzhin las //
NG0569:1639: yon tan thams cad lhun rdzogs pa'i //
NG0569:1640: blang dor med pa'i byang chub sems //
NG0569:1641: rin chen rigs mchog sdom pa gzung *//
NG0569:1642: chos gang dri ma med pa'i ngang *//
NG0569:1643: skyon gyis ma gos 'od gsal ba'i //
NG0569:1644: rang gi mtshan nyid ma 'dres rdzogs //
NG0569:1645: pad+ma rigs mchog sdom pa gzung *//
NG0569:1646: bla med byang chub sems kyi mchog thugs rje thabs rol cir yang snang *//
NG0569:1649: las kyi rigs mchog sdom pa gzung *//
NG0569:1650: mtha' yas sems can kun don phyir //
NG0569:1651: byang chub mchog tu bdag sems bskyed //
NG0569:1652: sdom pa ma lus gzung bar bgyi //
NG0569:1653: ngan song bdag gis bsgral bar bgyi //
NG0569:1654: 'khor ba bdag gis grol bar bgyi //
NG0569:1655: rgyu yis sa las dbugs dbyung bgyi //
NG0569:1656: sems can ma lus thams cad kun //
NG0569:1657: bdag gis byang chub mchog la dgog / ces ni sdom pa gzung bar bya //
NG0569:1658: gzhan gyi bzhad pa dag gis kyang *//
NG0569:1659: sdom pa rab tu gzung ba'o //
NG0569:1660: dam tshig thun mong khyad par gyis //
NG0569:1661: thun mong dam tshig dran pa ni //
NG0569:1662: nyams na gso bar khas blangs te //
NG0569:1663: spyi yi dam tshig bzhin du srung //
NG0569:1664: khyad par dam tshig rnam bzhi ste //
NG0569:1665: phyi nang khrus dang bya ba dang *//
NG0569:1666: ming tshig dag gis bar ma bcad //
NG0569:1667: gzhan gyis mi thos klag pa dang *//
NG0569:1668: sems ni ma yengs gsol ba'o //
NG0569:1669: de dag sngon 'gro'i yan lag go / 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa'i rgyud las //
NG0569:1670: sngon du 'gro ba'i le'u ste sum brgya gcig pa'o //  // lam gyi yan lag gi skabs so //
NG0569:1671: de nas rdo rje 'chang chen la //
NG0569:1672: ya ma ra dzas gsol btab pa //
NG0569:1673: gang zag dbang po rab don du //
NG0569:1674: mtshan ni mi rtog ye shes su //
NG0569:1675: bltas te gdon pa ji ltar lags //
NG0569:1676: de skad gsol pas bka 'a stsal pa //
NG0569:1677: nyon cig gshin rje gshedakyi sras //
NG0569:1678: sngon du bya ba'i las rdzogs nas //
NG0569:1679: stong pa nyid kyi ngang las kyang *//
NG0569:1680: dang po'i sangs rgyas bdag nyid bskyed //
NG0569:1681: thugs khar nyi zla kha sbyor gyi //
NG0569:1682: bar du a ni dkar po bsgom //
NG0569:1683: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NG0569:1684: don dam skye med brjod dang bral //
NG0569:1685: ye shes spros bral rang bzhin bsgom //
NG0569:1687: phyi nang snod bcud ma lus kun //
NG0569:1688: chos nyid byang chub sems su sbyangs //
NG0569:1689: bsdus te thim pas bdag nyid kyang *//
NG0569:1690: ye shes sgyu ma'i sku ru bsgoms //
NG0569:1691: skye med yi ge shel ltar dag shin tu gsal la dri med bsgom //
NG0569:1692: rdo rje nyi ma snang ba che //
NG0569:1693: rdo rje zla ba dri med 'od //
NG0569:1694: a ni yig 'bru kun gyi mchog don chen ye ge dam pa yin //
NG0569:1695: khong nas 'byung ba skye ba med //
NG0569:1696: dngos po dag la mtshan brjod pas //
NG0569:1697: thugs kha'i skye med yi ge de //
NG0569:1698: tshig tu brjod pa spangs pa ste //
NG0569:1699: stong pa nyid kyi rang sgra 'byung *//
NG0569:1700: brjod pa kun gyi rgyu yi mchog des ni stong gsum stong chen po //
NG0569:1701: 'jig rten khams ni mtha' yas su //
NG0569:1702: stong nyid rang gsal sgra bsgrags te //
NG0569:1703: tshig kun rab tu gsal bar byed //
NG0569:1704: bdag dang 'khor dang chos thams cad //
NG0569:1705: stong nyid rang sgra rig pa des //
NG0569:1706: skye ba med cing 'gag pa med //
NG0569:1707: brjod du med cing tha snyad med //
NG0569:1708: brtag tu med cing btung du med //
NG0569:1709: thog ma med cing tha ma med //
NG0569:1710: 'gyur ba med cing dngos po med //
NG0569:1712: ngo bo nyid med bdag gzhan @#//
NG0569:1714: yongs su shes par bya ba'ang med //
NG0569:1715: rnam par rtog med mi rtog med //
NG0569:1716: g.yo ba med cing mi g.yo med //
NG0569:1717: gting zab brtag dka' ma bcos pa //
NG0569:1718: blos ma rig cing sgrib med pa'i //
NG0569:1719: rang gsal dngos med dbyings su gsal //
NG0569:1720: de ltar bsgom zhing brjod pa ni //
NG0569:1721: nyin mtshan dus gsum rgyun du gdon //
NG0569:1722: skyo ba mtshan gyi yang snying gis //
NG0569:1723: stong nyid dang po'i sangs rgyas su //
NG0569:1724: byas te langs la rjes thob la //
NG0569:1725: dngos po thams cad ye shes brgyan //
NG0569:1726: chos nyid rol pa rang snang ba //
NG0569:1727: bde stong dbyer med klong na gnas //
NG0569:1728: de ltar bsgoms zhing lta byas na //
NG0569:1730: chos sku rnam dag thob gyur na //
NG0569:1731: longs spyod rdzogs sku ye shes kyis //
NG0569:1732: rol pa'i rang snang sprul pa'i sku //
NG0569:1733: bde gshegs byang chub sems dpa' dang *//
NG0569:1734: sems can rnams la mngon snang ngo *//
NG0569:1735: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa'i rgyud las //
NG0569:1736: mtshan mi rtog pa'i ye shes su bltas te gdon
NG0569:1737: pa'i le'u ste sum brgya gnyis pa'o // // sras
NG0569:1738: mchog gshin rjes yang gsol pa //
NG0569:1739: bcom ldan rdo rje 'chang rgyal po //
NG0569:1740: mtshan ni zab mo gsang sngags kyis //
NG0569:1741: don du bltas te gdon pa zhes //
NG0569:1742: bgyi ba gang lags bshad du gsol //
NG0569:1743: de skad gsol pas bka' stsal pa //
NG0569:1744: zhus don bshad kyis legs par nyon //
NG0569:1745: chos rnams rang bzhin med pa yi //
NG0569:1746: dngos med stong nyid ngang las kyang *//
NG0569:1747: sgyu 'phrul lta bu'i tshul gyis ni //
NG0569:1748: nam mkha' dbyings kyi rang bzhin bsgoms //
NG0569:1749: gsal ba skar ma lta bu yi //
NG0569:1750: ye shes 'od zer las byung ba //
NG0569:1751: hu~m ni sngon po 'od zer gyi //
NG0569:1752: tshogs dang ldan par rab tu bsgom //
NG0569:1753: de las 'od zer dpag med pa'i //
NG0569:1754: rtse mo la ni sangs rgyas sku //
NG0569:1755: mang po rab tu 'phros pa yi //
NG0569:1756: sems can rnams kyi don byas nas //
NG0569:1757: slar 'dus hu~m la thim gyur pas //
NG0569:1758: 'od du zhu bas rdo rje che /
NG0569:1759: kha dog drug ldan rtse drug gyur //
NG0569:1760: khro zhal drug gis rab mdzes pa'o //
NG0569:1761: bum pa'i nang du b+h+rum dkar las //
NG0569:1762: rin po che yi mchod rten ni //
NG0569:1763: stong gsum stong chen tshad tsam bsgom //
NG0569:1764: mchod rten de yi bum nang du //
NG0569:1765: ye ge hri la chos 'byung bsam //
NG0569:1766: de nas sna tshogs rdo rje yi //
NG0569:1767: lte bar b+h+rum las gzhal yas khang *//
NG0569:1768: gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs bcas //
NG0569:1769: rin chen lnga yi rtsig par bcas //
NG0569:1771: rin chen pha gus rnam par mdzes //
NG0569:1772: dra ba dra phyed dril bur bcas //
NG0569:1773: dar bu kha dang pad+ma dang *//
NG0569:1774: rin chen ka ba za ra tshags //
NG0569:1775: ta ra na da 'khor lo gdugs //
NG0569:1776: rdo rje ye shes me rir ldan //
NG0569:1777: de lta'i nang na srog chags gdan //
NG0569:1778: seng ge glang chen rta mchog dang *//
NG0569:1779: rma bya shang shang pad+ma yi //
NG0569:1780: gdan rnams rab tu gsal bar bsgom //
NG0569:1781: de nas dbus kyi gdan stengs su //
NG0569:1782: a ni dkar po yongs gyur las //
NG0569:1785: sku mdog dkar po zhal bzhi pa //
NG0569:1786: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NG0569:1787: ral pa'i dbu brgyan rgyan med bsgom //
NG0569:1788: de yi thugs kha zla stengs su //
NG0569:1789: d+hi las dang po sangs rgyas bsgom //
NG0569:1790: zhal lnga phyag bzhi skyil krung bzhugs //
NG0569:1791: sku mdog dkar po rgyan gyis brgyan //
NG0569:1792: g.yas bzhi ral gri g.yon bzhi na //
NG0569:1793: shes rab po ti bzhi yang bsnams //
NG0569:1795: de yi thugs khar bsgom pa na //
NG0569:1796: rten 'brel bcu gnyis dag pa ni //
NG0569:1797: pha rol phyin pa bcu gnyis mtshon //
NG0569:1798: sangs rgyas bcu gnyis bgrod pa yi //
NG0569:1799: rang bzhin las byung shes rab kyi //
NG0569:1800: 'khor lo lte mthar mu khyud bzhi //
NG0569:1801: rtsibs drug kha dog drug dang ldan //
NG0569:1803: a nyid las thim de stobs kyis //
NG0569:1804: mu khyud nang la rtsa sngags dgod //
NG0569:1805: rtsibs drug dang po nas brtsams te //
NG0569:1806: sngags drug rang rang kha dog bzhin //
NG0569:1807: phyi bskor mu khyud nang ma la //
NG0569:1808: yang snying 'phreng sngags dag gis bskor //
NG0569:1809: phyi la sgra yig gsal byed sgom //
NG0569:1810: de dbus ye shes thig le yi //
NG0569:1811: a ni dkar po yongs gyur las //
NG0569:1812: bcom ldan ye shes sems pa'i sku //
NG0569:1813: zhal drug phyag gnyis sprin dkar mdog zhabs gnyis rdo rje skyil krung bzhugs //
NG0569:1814: phyag g.yas ut+pal dmar po la //
NG0569:1816: steng na shes rab po ti bsnams //
NG0569:1817: yod pa zhi ba'i ngang tshul can //
NG0569:1818: in+ta ni la'i gtsug phud mdzes //
NG0569:1820: rgyan rnams rdzogs par rab tu bsgom //
NG0569:1821: de yi thugs khar zla stengs su //
NG0569:1822: don dam yi ge a dkar bsgom //
NG0569:1824: sems can kun gyi sgrib bsal nas //
NG0569:1825: tshur 'dus bdag lus snang bar bya //
NG0569:1827: stong gsum stong chen 'jig rten khams //
NG0569:1828: ye shes 'od kyis snang bar byas //
NG0569:1829: de nas rdo rje sgo drug nas /
NG0569:1830: kha dog drug gi 'od byung ste //
NG0569:1831: sangs rgyas zhing khams thams cad kun //
NG0569:1832: ye shes 'od kyis snang byas na //
NG0569:1833: sangs rgyas sems can thams cad kun //
NG0569:1834: mchod dang don byas slar 'dus te //
NG0569:1835: ye shes rdo rje de nyid la //
NG0569:1836: lan gsum dag tu bskor byas nas //
NG0569:1837: de nyid la ni rab bzhugs pas //
NG0569:1838: bdag med chos nyid rtogs par byas //
NG0569:1839: zla ba la gnas snying po dang *//
NG0569:1840: sngags dang gcig tu gyur par bsgom //
NG0569:1841: des ni sgrib pa ma lus pa //
NG0569:1842: dag cing byang nas ye shes gsal //
NG0569:1843: de ltar rgyun du ma yengs pa //
NG0569:1844: bsgom zhing brjod pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NG0569:1845: tshe 'di ring por mi thogs par //
NG0569:1846: sku dang zla ba a gsum gyi //
NG0569:1847: sgo nas chos sku longs spyod sku //
NG0569:1848: sprul sku rnam gsum thob par 'gyur //
NG0569:1849: thun mong dngos grub sangs rgyas kyi //
NG0569:1850: sku dang zhing khams bsam yas mthong *//
NG0569:1851: spyan lnga mngon shes drug la sogs //
NG0569:1852: phan yon ji bzhin thob par @#//
NG0569:1854: 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa' rtog pa'i rgyal po khri drug stong pa'i rgyud las /
NG0569:1855: rigs bsdus pa'i le'u ste sum brgya gsum pa'o //  // de las gzhan yang bshad bya ba //
NG0569:1856: rigs ni so sor dbye ba yis //
NG0569:1857: gdon thabs rnal 'byor rim pa ni //
NG0569:1858: rnam par mi rtog ye shes kyi //
NG0569:1859: phyag rgya rdo rje dbyings kyi dal //
NG0569:1860: byang sems rdo rje bsgom pa ni //
NG0569:1861: dkyil 'khor dbus kyi gdan stengs su //
NG0569:1862: a ni dkar po yongs gyur las //
NG0569:1863: byang chub sems ni rdo rje ste //

NG0569:4726: mnyam pa nyid ces ji ltar lags /

NG0569:4890: dgongs pa'i mtshan dpe ji ltar lags //

NG0569:5032: rdo rje 'chang chen gyis bshad gsol //

NG0569:5982: kun gyi zhal nas drag po sngags kyi sgra //
NG0569:5983: thog dang lce 'bab bzhin du thog chen sgrogs //
NG0569:5984: stong gsum 'jig rten khams kun gang bar bsam //
NG0569:5985: bdag nyid ya man ta kas sngags bzlas pa //
NG0569:5986: thugs kha'i sngags las ye shes 'od 'phros pas //
NG0569:5987: gshed po gzhi yi thugs dam rgyud kyang bskul //
NG0569:5988: gshed bzhi rang dbang med par las byed do //
NG0569:5989: de bzhin gshed bzhis phyogs skyong bcu rnams bskul //
NG0569:5990: phyogs skyong bcu yis bdud pho mthar byed dang *//
NG0569:5991: las kyi gshin rje mon pa bdud rnams bskul //
NG0569:5992: des ni ma mo mkha' 'gro ging pho ging mo dang *//
NG0569:5993: gnod sbyin sha za srin po pho mo bskul //
NG0569:5994: skad cig 'dug dbang med par las byed do //
NG0569:5997: rang dbang med par drag po'i las byed do //
NG0569:5998: de rnams dmigs pa'i gnas su sprin ltar gtibs //
NG0569:5999: dgra bo du yod skye nas zhags pas bzung *//
NG0569:6000: dkar nag snying nas lcags kyus bzung nas drangs //
NG0569:6001: rgyab nas rlung gis 'phul zhing me yis 'khor lo
NG0569:6002: bsreg / rtar mtshan rtsi sbur mi chags pa bzhin
NG0569:6003: du // bkrag dang gzi mdangs nyams sreg sol ba gzhog tu song *//
NG0569:6004: lus po 'dar zhing skra g.yengs gnag la rid //
NG0569:6005: 'on thong skad ngan 'dzer zhing mig rtsa rig rig nyams //
NG0569:6006: de lta bu de las kyi gshin rjes yis //
NG0569:6007: rang dbang med par bkug ste 'khrul 'khor gyi //
NG0569:6008: gsang mdzod bzhi ru bcug cing ling gal thims bsam //
NG0569:6009: de lta bu yi las mkhan tshogs rnams kyis /
NG0569:6010: kho yi bsrung skyob byed pa'i lha bzhi po //
NG0569:6011: rlung gi 'khor los phral zhing bskyod g.yeng nam mkhar bskyal //
NG0569:6012: me yi 'khor los bsreg cing thal bar brlag de ltar gsal bas dgug bstim lha dbye ba'i //
NG0569:6013: drag sngags drod rtags mthong nas bzlas //
NG0569:6014: des ni sred med bu yi bla yang khugs //
NG0569:6015: don po'i bla tshe srog khugs the tshom med //
NG0569:6016: 'jam dpal khri drug stong gsang sngags snying po'i rgyud las //
NG0569:6017: las la sbyor ba'i le'u ste lnga brgya bdun cu
NG0569:6018: bzhi pa'o // // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen
NG0569:6019: pos // drag po las kyi 'dzab dgongs bshad //
NG0569:6020: bdag nyid ya man ta kar gnas pa yi //
NG0569:6021: thugs kha'i rdo rje snying po ye ge ya //
NG0569:6022: sngo nag gsal la 'tsher ba me lce 'bar //
NG0569:6023: mtha' mar nyi ma bzhi pa'i sngags kyis bskor //
NG0569:6024: me lce 'bar zhing tsha tshar 'phro bar bsam //
NG0569:6025: bdag gi zhal nas gsad pa'i sngags zlas pas //
NG0569:6026: 'od zer 'phros pas rno myur glog ltar 'gyu //
NG0569:6027: 'od zer dang ni 'gro ba thams cad kun //
NG0569:6028: las kyi gshin rje sku mdog mthing nag khros //
NG0569:6029: sku che yan lag rags pa mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs //
NG0569:6030: shin tu gtum rngam 'jigs pa dur khrod chas kyis brgyan //
NG0569:6031: me dpung 'bar ba'i glong na mi bzad 'jigs pa'i gar //
NG0569:6032: de las ye shes lnga yi 'od zer 'phros //
NG0569:6033: 'od zer gtum rngam 'jigs pa dur khrod chas kyis brgyan //
NG0569:6034: me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na mi bzad 'jigs pa'i gar //
NG0569:6035: de las ye shes lnga yi 'od zer 'phros //
NG0569:6036: 'od zer mtshon cha rnon po sna tshogs 'gyur //
NG0569:6037: zhal nas drag po gsang ba'i ngan sngags ni //
NG0569:6038: spu gri sos gcod lta bu 'brug gi sgra ltar sgrogs //
NG0569:6039: de lta bu yis stong gsum 'jig rten khams //
NG0569:6040: gting mtha' med dbyings thams cad til gyi gang bu bzhin /
NG0569:6041: khengs par bsams te de dag thams cad kyis //
NG0569:6042: brnab pa'i lus la snags kyi 'od zer dang *//
NG0569:6043: mtshon cha rnon po sna tshogs char du phab //
NG0569:6044: me lce'i kha la sbrang bus mi chags bzhin //
NG0569:6045: don po'i snying kha dkar nag mtshams de ru //
NG0569:6047: sngags 'od zer rtsa bzhi nas zhugs te //
NG0569:6048: sa chu me rlung 'byung pa bzhi po de //
NG0569:6049: rlung mkhris bad kan 'dus pa'i nad gzhir bslang *//
NG0569:6050: sha rus drod dbugs 'byung bzhi dkrags //
NG0569:6051: chos nyid ye shes yon tan rab rgyud kyi //
NG0569:6052: dngas ma'i rtsa bzhi bcad nas srog gi me mar gsod //
NG0569:6053: lus ni rdul phran tsam song shes pa dwangs snyigs phye //
NG0569:6054: srog dbugs phyi ru phyung ste lus srog phye mar bsam //
NG0569:6055: sha khrag phung po thams cad las kyi gshin rje dang *//
NG0569:6056: sha za srin po srin mo khrag 'thung dang *//
NG0569:6057: rdo rje ging pho ging mo la sogs tshogs rnams kyis //
NG0569:6058: btod cing zos te the shul med par bsam //
NG0569:6059: ngams ni tshangs pa lha yi tshe yod kyang *//
NG0569:6060: skad cig yud la 'chi 'gyur gzhan dag smos ci dgos //
NG0569:6061: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa las sngags drag po'i rgyud las //
NG0569:6062: gsad pa'i 'dzab dgongs kyi le'u ste lnga brgya bdun
NG0569:6063: cu lnga'o // // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen
NG0569:6064: pos // nyi ma bzhi pa'i sbyor ba bshad //
NG0569:6067: brnag pa gcod cing rlag byed bsam //
NG0569:6068: dbus kyi lcags mkhar ya las kyang *//
NG0569:6069: 'chi bdag gshin rje'i sku ru bskyed //
NG0569:6070: phyogs gzhi'i ya me tak+she las //
NG0569:6071: srog gshed bzhi yi sku ru skyed //
NG0569:6072: phyi rim lcags mkhar 'khrul mig gi / ra dza la sogs bcu gnyis so //
NG0569:6073: phyogs skyong gshin rje'i sku ru bskyed //
NG0569:6074: mtha' ma'i spu gri nyin bzhi po //
NG0569:6075: mtshon cha sna tshogs me dpal bskyed //
NG0569:6076: bar gyi snying po sku gsung thugs //
NG0569:6077: ye shes 'od zer stobs chen gyis //
NG0569:6078: pha rol stobs 'joms las mkhan bskul //
NG0569:6079: nyi ma bzhi pa thams cad kyi //
NG0569:6080: skya rengs dang po shar ba la //
NG0569:6082: gtor ma byin te pho nyar dgye //
NG0569:6083: rbad cing bla dgug lha dang dpral //
NG0569:6084: ling ga'i rten la bstim par bya //
NG0569:6085: de nas nyi ma dang po yi //
NG0569:6086: nyi ma rtse la shar pa la //
NG0569:6087: sha khrag sna tshogs gtor ma bca' //
NG0569:6088: bdag nyid gshed chen skur gsal ba'i //
NG0569:6089: thugs khar nyi gdan ye ge ya //
NG0569:6091: de mthar drag sngags 'bru bdun bskor //
NG0569:6094: bde bshegs thugs rje'i thugs las kyang *//
NG0569:6095: khro rgyal ya man ta ka bskul //
NG0569:6096: de yi ye shes 'od zer gyis //
NG0569:6097: gshed po ya ma ra dza bskul //
NG0569:6098: de yis kong rtse brag 'joms dang *//
NG0569:6099: rdo rje bdud 'jom a ba glang mgo bskul //
NG0569:6100: de yi bdud po brang dkar rngam pa dang *//
NG0569:6101: nag po bkrag med ma ha srog bdag bskul //
NG0569:6102: de yis gshin rje mthar byed log 'dren mthar byar bskul //
NG0569:6103: de yis rdo rje rigs kyi mkha' 'gro dang *//
NG0569:6104: ma mo dkar mo'i tshogs dang ging pho ging mo bskul //
NG0569:6105: de yi klu gnyan sa bdag gdug pa bskul //
NG0569:6106: de yi brnag pa gang yin klad pa'i @#//
NG0569:6108: gti mug rmongs pa'i gnas nas byol song rgyal po ste //
NG0569:6109: 'thoms pa'i gshed bskul tshangs pa'i gtsug rtsa gcad //
NG0569:6110: sha rus sa yi khams las bad kan blang *//
NG0569:6111: klad pa dar nyams mgo 'khor las byed do //
NG0569:6112: be con phyag rgya brnag pa'i spyi bor brdeg / dgongs ka'i nyi ma dmar thag chad pa la //
NG0569:6113: gshed po ya ma ra dza la sogs lnga rnams la //
NG0569:6114: sha khrag sna tshogs gtor ma dgra bor dmigs te dbul //
NG0569:6115: drag tu bskul zhing gtor ma dgra phyogs btang *//
NG0569:6116: de bzhin nyi ma kun la shes par bya //
NG0569:6117: khro rgyal gshed pos myos byed 'bar ba bskul //
NG0569:6118: de yis ya ba ya ti phya sangs bskul //
NG0569:6119: de yis nag po 'dzub med mi dur sa 'dar bskul //
NG0569:6120: de yis byol song thar byed yi dwags thar byed bskul //
NG0569:6121: de yi shugs kyis mkha' 'gro mon mo'i tshogs //
NG0569:6122: ging pho ging mo klu gnyan sa bdag bskul //
NG0569:6123: de yis brnag pa gang yin lte ba yi //
NG0569:6124: 'dod chags zhen pa'i gnas nas dmyal ba'i dbang po ste //
NG0569:6125: gsol byed sdud bskul srid pa'i rten rtsa bcad //
NG0569:6126: dbugs ni rlung gi khams las rlung nad bslang *//
NG0569:6127: lus rgyal myos blangs yid 'khrug las byed do //
NG0569:6128: ral gri phyag rgya brnag pa'i lte bar brdeg dgongs ka nyi ma dmar thag chad pa la //
NG0569:6129: myos byed 'bar ba la sogs gtor ma dgrar dmigs dbul //
NG0569:6130: de bzhin nyi ma gsum pa dag la yang *//
NG0569:6131: khro rgyal gshed pos ar+ya dmar po bskul //
NG0569:6132: de yis gshin rje dmigs pa mig dmar bskul //
NG0569:6133: de yis swa 'dar 'khrigs pa tho yo 'thoms pa rje //
NG0569:6134: bdud pho thod bdag thod pa rje rnams bskul //
NG0569:6135: de yis srin po mthar byed klu dbang mthar byed bskul //
NG0569:6136: de yis chags pa'i mkha' 'gro ma mo dmar nag tshogs //
NG0569:6137: ging pho ging mo klu gnyan sa bdag bskul //
NG0569:6138: de yis brnag pa gang yin mgrin pa yis //
NG0569:6139: nga rgyal dregs pa'i gnas nas lha min dbang po ste //
NG0569:6140: srog gi gshed bskul ngag gi rgyun rtsa gcad //
NG0569:6141: khrag gi chu yi khams las khrag nad bslang *//
NG0569:6142: lus zungs khrag skyug khong khrag 'dzag pa'i las byed do //
NG0569:6143: 'khor lo'i phyag rgya brnag pa'i mgrin par brdeg nyi ma dmar thag chad na ar+ya dmar po dang *//
NG0569:6144: ging bdud ma mo rnams la gtor ma dgrar dmigs dbul //
NG0569:6145: de bzhin nyi ma bzhi pa'i las la yang *//
NG0569:6146: khro rgyal gshed pos ras pa tshar dgu bskul //
NG0569:6147: de yis chos kyi rgyal po lha mchog rtel pa bskul //
NG0569:6148: de yis ral pa spyi bcings rngam pa klu 'dul rje //
NG0569:6149: sa to nag po mtshal bdud dregs pa bskul //
NG0569:6150: de yis gnod sbyin mthar byed dmyal ba mthar byed dang *//
NG0569:6151: dam sri mthar byed dbang med las la bskul //
NG0569:6152: de yi las kyi mkha' 'gro ma mo sngon mo'i tshogs //
NG0569:6153: ging pho ging mo klu gnyan sa bdag bskul //
NG0569:6154: de yi brnag pa gang yin snying kha yi //
NG0569:6155: zhe sdang gtum pa'o gnas nas mi rgod @#//
NG0569:6157: srog gcod gshod bskul dngas ma'i rtsa bzhi dang *//
NG0569:6158: srog pa rtsa bcad dbugs de phyi ru phyung *//
NG0569:6159: drod ni me yi khams las mkhris nad langs //
NG0569:6160: spu gri'i phyag rgya bcas te snying khar brdeg / srog gi me gsad srog gcad sha khrag rnams //
NG0569:6161: las kyi gshin rje sha za srin po'i tshogs //
NG0569:6162: ma mo khrag 'thung ging pho ging mo dang *//
NG0569:6163: srin mo la sogs tshogs kyis bstod cing sha khrag zos //
NG0569:6164: rjes shul tsam yang med cing brlag par bsam //
NG0569:6165: srog gi me mar gsad nas shes pa dwangs snyigs phye //
NG0569:6166: dwangs ma 'bring gis phyag rgya gcig par bskyed //
NG0569:6167: rab kyis skye ba chos kyi dbyings su bskul //
NG0569:6168: mtha' ma bdag nyid lus kyi go char bya //
NG0569:6169: srog gi snyigs ma thod pa'i rten la bstim //
NG0569:6170: sa bdag kla gnyan la sogs gdug pa can la gtad //
NG0569:6171: des ni mi 'gyur nag po'i bdud kyang gsod //
NG0569:6172: srog chags mi la sogs pa kun la smos ci dgos //
NG0569:6173: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa don gyi snying po'i rgyud las //
NG0569:6174: nyi ma bzhi pa'i le'u ste lnga brgya bdun cu
NG0569:6175: drug go / // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen
NG0569:6176: pos // 'khrul 'khor don rnams rgyas bshad do //
NG0569:6178: man ngag don dang ma ldan na //
NG0569:6180: des na don rnams rgyas bshad pa //
NG0569:6181: 'khor lo'i ka bzhi ma tshugs na //
NG0569:6182: 'khor lo kha sbyor gnad mi tshugs //
NG0569:6184: steng 'og sngags kyi ka ba rdib //
NG0569:6185: las kyi gshin rje mun khang 'khor //
NG0569:6187: 'khor lo'i gzer bzhi ma thebs na //
NG0569:6188: mtshon cha'i 'khor lo lto dral nas //
NG0569:6189: sngags pa'i 'khor du rkyen byung ngo *//
NG0569:6190: bcun phur bzhi dang ma ldan na //
NG0569:6191: las kyi gshin rje gnas 'khyams nas //
NG0569:6192: bsgrub pa'i las rnams don med 'gyur //
NG0569:6193: ka ba bzhi yi don ni rtsa ba'i yi ge bzhi //
NG0569:6194: don ni yid la yi ge'i gzugs su gsal ba dang *//
NG0569:6195: ngo bo gshin rje gshed po bzhi ru gsal ba dang *//
NG0569:6196: rang bzhin mtshon cha'i rnam par gsal ba dang *//
NG0569:6197: nus mthu 'byung ba nang gcod gshed //
NG0569:6199: gdung bzhi tshangs thig bzhis mtshon nas //
NG0569:6200: rtsa bzhi'i sbubs nas 'byung ba'i dngas ma bzhi gnas pa //
NG0569:6201: phyi nang snod bcud kun gyi gzhi rten byed //
NG0569:6202: de la nyi ma bzhi po las gnyer gtad pa'o //
NG0569:6203: yang na spyi bo mgrin pa snying lte yi //
NG0569:6204: 'khor lo'i don gsal sngags bzlas las rdzogs pa'o //
NG0569:6205: 'khor lo'i gzer bzhi'i don ni 'di dag ste //
NG0569:6206: bsnyen pa drod rtags thob pa byin rlabs lha yi gzer //
NG0569:6207: rdzas rnams tshogs pa rten 'brel sbyor ba'i gzer //
NG0569:6208: bcu drug khang pa'i gzer dang 'phro bdun dgongs pa'i gzer //
NG0569:6209: 'khor lo'i bcun phur bzhi ni rnal 'byor dbang rnams rdzogs //
NG0569:6210: man ngag gdeng thob dgongs ldan @#//
NG0569:6212: bsnyen pa bya ba tshad skyol phyi nang gsang rtags ldan //
NG0569:6213: gshin rje ma mo las la tshud pa ni //
NG0569:6214: rtsol ba ting nge 'dzin gyi btsun phur dang *//
NG0569:6215: ye shes lha yi stobs kyis las kyi gshin rje dang *//
NG0569:6216: ma mo dbang med las la btsud de khu zlog mi nus pas //
NG0569:6217: ye shes lha yi byin rlabs bcun phur dang *//
NG0569:6218: de dag srog nas bskul zhing las bcol te //
NG0569:6219: drag sngags bzlas na dgra bo dbang med par //
NG0569:6220: bla 'brel srog gcod drag po'i bcun phur ro //
NG0569:6221: gsad pa drag sngags don bzhi shes bya ba //
NG0569:6222: 'phen byed skyes bu lta bu ma shes na //
NG0569:6223: bsgrub bya dmigs pa'i yul la mi bskyed do //
NG0569:6224: skyed byed rkyen gzhu lta bu ma shes na //
NG0569:6225: bsgrub bya'i yul la sngags kyi gzer mi 'phro //
NG0569:6226: 'phang bya mda' 'dra'i drag sngags ma shes na //
NG0569:6227: dmigs pa'i srog yul rgyud la mi 'phrog go gcod byed mde'u 'dra'i drag sngags ma shes na //
NG0569:6228: dmigs pa'i rtsa dbugs srog gzugs mi chod do //
NG0569:6229: de dag don rnams gsal bar bya ba ni //
NG0569:6230: 'phen byed dbus yig ya las drang bskor 'phen pa'o //
NG0569:6231: skyod byed rkyen gyi ting 'dzin 'phro 'du gsal ba'o //
NG0569:6232: mda' ni las sbyor drag sngags bcu drug pa'o //
NG0569:6233: gcod byed spu gri'i drag sngags mtshan pa bzhis //
NG0569:6234: drag po'i rtsa dbugs srig gzungs gcod pa'o //
NG0569:6235: de dag rab tu gces pa'i sngags kyi sdebs brgyad do //
NG0569:6236: srog gzungs gcad cing lus srog 'byed lugs ni //
NG0569:6237: 'grod stabs brgyad kyis gsad pa dang *//
NG0569:6238: bcu gnyis tshul gyis gsad pa dang *//
NG0569:6239: gnad dgu sdebs la gsad pa'o //
NG0569:6240: 'gros stabs brgyad ni gang zhe na //
NG0569:6242: 'khril pa sprul 'gros stag mchongs drag po'i 'gros //
NG0569:6243: srin bu ka ta ring 'gros bi bag rta yi 'gros //
NG0569:6244: rta lam nag po'i 'gros dang rus sbal 'phye bo'i 'gros //
NG0569:6245: bcu gnyis tshul gyis gsad pa ni //
NG0569:6246: rgyu bzhi bsdus te gsad pa dang *//
NG0569:6247: dug gsum ar la gtad de gsad pa dang *//
NG0569:6248: 'byung ba lnga po rtsad gcad gsad //
NG0569:6249: phung po lnga yi stobs gzhom dang *//
NG0569:6250: nang grol smad lnga gtub pa dang *//
NG0569:6251: tshogs drug sgo rnams dag pa dang *//
NG0569:6252: dngas ma bdun gyis rtsad gcod dang *//
NG0569:6253: dbugs kyi lam dgu dgag pa dang *//
NG0569:6254: rnam shes tshogs brgyad sgo dgag dang *//
NG0569:6255: lus ngag yid gsum mthu bsdu dang *//
NG0569:6256: shes pa dwangs snyigs dbye ba dang *//
NG0569:6257: rten gcig me mar gsad pa'o //
NG0569:6258: gnad dgu phab la gsad pa ni //
NG0569:6259: gzas pa po yi rang rgyud la //
NG0569:6260: bla gnas sa dgu bla rten mtshan ma dgu /
NG0569:6261: de 'jom drag sngags dgu dang skyod byed ting 'dzin
NG0569:6262: dgu sngags rtag thun rdzas dgu dang sngags 'jug sgo
NG0569:6263: dgu dang *// bag chags bsreg pa'i ye ge me
NG0569:6264: 'bar dgu / gnad dgu bsdus nas 'joms pa'i man
NG0569:6265: ngag dgu / shes pa dwangs snyigs phye la bsgrod
NG0569:6267: de dag 'khrul 'khor spyi ru dgos pa ste //
NG0569:6268: spyi rgyug ces pa thabs kyi man ngag go / 'khor lo bskor thabs 'bum yod dang *//
NG0569:6269: bcu bdun 'bum bskor ma shes na //
NG0569:6270: mtshon cha med pa'i dpa' bo 'dra //
NG0569:6271: spyi rgyug drag sngags bcu bdun pa //
NG0569:6272: 'di yi drang thabs bskor shes na //
NG0569:6273: bsgrub dang dmod dang gdab pa yi //
NG0569:6274: drag sngags thams cad 'di la tshang *//
NG0569:6275: des na gsang sngags kun gyi mchog / 'jam dpal
NG0569:6276: khri drug stong pa gsang sngags mchog gi rgyud las
NG0569:6277: / 'khrul 'khor man ngag gi le'u ste lnga brgya
NG0569:6278: bdun cu bdun pa'o // // ya ma ra dzas
NG0569:6279: / yang gsol pa // rdo rje 'chang chen khro rgyal gtso //
NG0569:6280: 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed sgrub pa'i //
NG0569:6281: spyi yi gdam ngag bshad du gsol //
NG0569:6282: de skad gsol pas bka' stsal pa //
NG0569:6284: mche gtsigs khros tshul bsgyings pa lta //
NG0569:6285: 'jigs tshul rngam pa'i sku yis ni //
NG0569:6286: gshin rje dregs pa 'joms mdzad pa //
NG0569:6287: gshin rje gshed bsgrub man ngag 'di //
NG0569:6288: ngas bshad legs par nyon las zung *//
NG0569:6290: sngags pa dpa' brtul ldan pa des //
NG0569:6291: dang por dam tshig gzhung bzhin bsrung *//
NG0569:6292: dam tshig bla ma mched dang sngags //
NG0569:6293: phyag rgya gsang bcu rtsa ba dang *//
NG0569:6294: spyad dang mi spang dang du blang *//

NG0569:6318: rtsa ba sham ring dur khrod gnas //
NG0569:6319: rtswa shing me tog ri dgas bya //

NG0569:6321: byin che bkra shis nyams dga' ba'i //

NG0569:6323: bsnyen dang nye bsnyen bsgrub pa dang *//

NG0569:6325: bsnyen pa dag la rnam gsum ste //
NG0569:6326: sbyor ba goms dang sngon du 'gro'o //

NG0569:6331: mchod sbyin gtor ma rgya chen dang *//

NG0569:6335: 'jam dpal mtshan mchog brgya rtsa brgyad //
NG0569:6336: gzungs sngags rgya chen bstod la sogs //
NG0569:6337: ma nyams dag par rgyun du gdon //
NG0569:6338: sbyor ba goms pa'i bsnyen pa'o //
NG0569:6339: sngon du 'gro ba'i bsnyen pa la //
NG0569:6340: dang por gnas pa de nyid la //
NG0569:6341: rtsa ba'i chus sbyangs man+dal rtsig khru gang 'dom gang rgya dang dpangs //

NG0569:6343: dri dang khrag sna bdud rtsis byug / zhing gi
NG0569:6344: srad bu byin brlabs thig tshangs thig zur thig cha
NG0569:6345: chen chung *// phyed 'gres sum cha bya rog rjes //
NG0569:6346: legs btab rdul tshon byis gyis brlab //
NG0569:6347: rus chen kha dog ma ru dbye //
NG0569:6348: khrag sna dur khrod sol ba dang *//
NG0569:6349: skyer pa me tog ut+pal rams //
NG0569:6350: de dag byin gyis brlabs la bri //
NG0569:6351: dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa //
NG0569:6352: dbus mthing rtsibs bzhi phyogs dang bstun //
NG0569:6353: de phyir 'khor lo rtsibs bcu pa //
NG0569:6354: sngon po rtsibs mchan khrag mtsho smug thod skam rlon pa'i 'phreng bas bskor //
NG0569:6355: gru chad khrag mtsho bar khyams phyogs //
NG0569:6356: sgo bzhi lnga rtsibs 'dod yon dmar //
NG0569:6357: pha gu dra phyed dar bu kad //
NG0569:6358: rta babs brgyad rtser 'khor lo gdugs //
NG0569:6359: ri dgas zla phyed rdo rje sgo //
NG0569:6360: rdo rje rgya gram lte ba la //
NG0569:6361: rdo rje thod skam me ris bskor //
NG0569:6362: pho brang rang gzhung bzhin du'o //
NG0569:6363: de la dgod pa'i rim pa ni //
NG0569:6364: dbus su gri thod lcags phur dgod //
NG0569:6365: g.yas g.yon mchog chen seng ldeng dgod //
NG0569:6366: 'jam dpal gshed chen khro rgyal dang *//
NG0569:6367: sbyor sgrol gsang ba'i yum gnyis su //

NG0569:6370: thugs mchog yab yum byin gyis brlabs //
NG0569:6371: rtsibs bzhir seng ldeng skyer ba dang *//

NG0569:6374: rtsibs bcur shing lcags mchog phur dgod //
NG0569:6375: phyogs skyong yab yum byin gyis brlabs //
NG0569:6376: gru chad lha snam sgo bzhi ru //
NG0569:6377: de bzhin rtsang phud gdug pa'i shing *//
NG0569:6378: ro langs las kyi gshin rje dang *//
NG0569:6379: lce spyang kang ka mon pho mo //
NG0569:6380: ging bdud sgo bzhi las mkhan rnams //
NG0569:6381: rang rang gzhung bzhin byin gyis brlabs //

NG0569:6383: de nas rdzas kyi rim pa lnga //
NG0569:6384: rten rdzas dam rdzas mchod rdzas dang *//
NG0569:6385: rgyan rdzas drag po sbyor ba'i rdzas //

NG0569:6387: mtshan ldan rdo rje ka pa lar //
NG0569:6388: bdud rtsi grub sman bsil chen dang *//
NG0569:6389: g+hi ham gur kum khrag sna tshogs //

NG0569:6391: tshon rtsi sbyar te steng thod la //
NG0569:6392: khro rgyal nyid dang thugs mchog dang *//
NG0569:6393: gshed po bzhi dang phyogs skyong bcu //
NG0569:6396: yab yum phyag rgya gsal rdzogs bri //
NG0569:6397: mtha' mar sku gsung yon tan thugs //
NG0569:6399: phyi ru spos sna gla rtsi dang *//
NG0569:6400: tshil chen dri ldan sman gyis byug de ni rten rdzas zhes bya'o //
NG0569:6401: smug chen sar pa ma rul skams //
NG0569:6402: gong gi rdzas kyi sngags rnams bri //
NG0569:6403: rtse mo bcud bdun hu~m rnams dgod //
NG0569:6404: smug chung la sogs snying sna tshogs //
NG0569:6405: bdud rtsi grub sman khrag sna tshogs //
NG0569:6406: 'bru sna spos sna sman sna tshogs //
NG0569:6407: sbyar lugs mthing nag dar gyis dril //
NG0569:6408: ru sprod rgyas btab dal bus bzhag de dag dam rdzas zhes bya'o //
NG0569:6409: 'bru sna tshogs kyi gtor ma ni //
NG0569:6410: dpal bshos sha chen rnam lnga sogs //
NG0569:6411: sha khrag sna tshogs brgyan pa gnyis //
NG0569:6412: khro rgyal dpal chen he ru ka'i //
NG0569:6413: gtor ma rgyan ldan nub tu bzhag / 'jam dpal gshin rje'i 'khor bcas kyi //
NG0569:6414: gtor ma rgyan ldan lho ru bzhag / ma mo yul rnams mkha' 'gro yi //
NG0569:6415: gtor ma nal bu dre 'u mdzo //
NG0569:6416: gtor ma byang shar mtshams su bzhag spos dang me tog mar me dang *//
NG0569:6417: dri chab gtsang bshos phyi mchod bsham //
NG0569:6418: zhing chen ma nyams gzugs kyis mchod //
NG0569:6419: rkang chen gling bu thod pa'i rnga //
NG0569:6420: mi mgo'i dung 'bud sgra yis mchod //
NG0569:6421: tshil chen gsur dang dri chen spos //
NG0569:6422: khrag chen sha chen spos dris mchod //
NG0569:6423: 'bru sna'i lha bshos tshil chen brgyan //
NG0569:6424: sha rus sna tshogs ro yis mchod //
NG0569:6425: zhing chen glang chen stag lpags gos //
NG0569:6426: reg bya'i mchod pa bla med bsham //
NG0569:6427: phud rgor rak+ta bdud rtsi bsham //
NG0569:6428: de dag mchod pa'i rdzas zhes bya //
NG0569:6429: zhing chen bla re zhing chung 'phan //
NG0569:6430: rgyu zhags dra ba keng rus bcal //
NG0569:6431: sha chen lhu rdum lho phyogs dgram //
NG0569:6432: brten rdzas skyes bu bu don te //
NG0569:6433: gzhan la mi bstan mthong mi rung *//
NG0569:6434: gzhan yang drag po sbyor ba'i rdzas //
NG0569:6435: 'khor lo ling ga thun rdzas dang *//
NG0569:6436: sbyin sreg 'brub khung mnan pa'i rdzas //
NG0569:6437: thams cad ma chad rdzogs par bsham //
NG0569:6438: bsgrub pa la 'jug dus tshod ni //
NG0569:6439: gshin rje'i lo dang zla ba dang *//
NG0569:6440: zhag dang dus tshod snying bzhi 'am //
NG0569:6441: dgun zla gsum spyir dbyar ston gyi //
NG0569:6442: rab 'bring tha chungs mar ngo la'o //
NG0569:6443: gza' sbyang phur pa mig dmar lag bra nye nam
NG0569:6444: gru rta thogs skag de dag dus la 'jug par
NG0569:6445: bya'o // 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa'i rgyud las //

NG0569:6447: brgya bdun cu brgyad do // // de nas rdo

NG0569:6455: rgyal chen bzhi ru byin gyis brlab //

NG0569:6459: bde gshegs spyan sngar dam bcas bzhin //

NG0569:6463: zhes brjod phyi mtshams bsrung las bca' /

NG0569:6465: gang gnod dam sri'i ming gzugs bri //

NG0569:6474: gsang mtshams dam du bcad cing bsrung *//
NG0569:6475: gshegs dang byin dbab mchod pa brlab //

NG0569:6478: dbang chen 'byung ba rims brtseg bsgom //

NG0569:6480: rgyu nyid rtsa ba'i snying po las //

NG0569:6483: khro rgyal ya man ta ka bskyed //
NG0569:6484: sgrol sbyor gsang ba'i yum gnyis bskyed //
NG0569:6485: rdo rje pad+ma byin brlabs te //
NG0569:6486: thabs dang shes rab snyoms 'jug pa'i //
NG0569:6488: rgyu yi snying po hu~m nyid 'phros //
NG0569:6489: phyogs mtshams rtsibs kyi rang gdan la //
NG0569:6490: bskyed pa'i sngags kyis gshed po bzhi //
NG0569:6491: phyogs skyong bcu dang thugs mchog sras //
NG0569:6492: yab yum rdzogs shing gsal bar bskyed //
NG0569:6493: dbang bskur byin brlabs nga rgyal bskyed //

NG0569:6520: rtags ne go chas bdag lus brgyan //

NG0569:6524: pa zhib can lho bal rnams //

NG0569:6528: mi bying chu bo'i thog nas 'gro //

NG0569:6532: phyag byed lha srin bdag khur ba //
NG0569:6533: rmi nyams mngon sum phyi nang gsang *//

NG0569:6535: mtshan rtags mang po mthong mthong bzlas //

NG0569:6548: gsung thugs yon tan bcu bcu gdags //

NG0569:6550: om a kro te ka ya man ta ka ha na ma tha b+hany+dzu hu~m phat /

NG0569:6555: / bstod dang mchod pa sum yar dbul //

NG0569:6557: nyi shu gnyis sogs dus la bya //
NG0569:6558: yang na rgyun du byas na rab //
NG0569:6559: za tshogs sum yar mchod pa dbul //

NG0569:6562: tshogs la dang po rab mtha' ru //
NG0569:6563: mchod dang bshags dang drag po'i las //
NG0569:6565: gtor ma phud spro phyis kyi rta //
NG0569:6566: gzhan gsum rang rang phyogs su btang *//

NG0569:6582: bsgrub khang g.yo dang lha sku ston //

NG0569:6587: de rtsogs rmi nyams mngon sum 'byung *//
NG0569:6588: gsang rtags lus yang sems gsal zhing *//
NG0569:6589: lha sku mngon mthong lung ston dang *//

NG0569:6592: nyon mongs shes pa yul la 'bar //

NG0569:6594: rang sems sgrib sbyangs mngon shes 'byung *//
NG0569:6595: de nas ting 'dzin thabs ldan pas //
NG0569:6596: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub blang *//
NG0569:6597: des ni bdag dang yi dam lha //
NG0569:6598: gnyis med ngo bo gcig par 'gyur //
NG0569:6599: de dag gsang sngags bzlas lugs ni //
NG0569:6600: sku yi snying po bcu bdun pa //

NG0569:6602: gsung dang thugs dang yon tan sngags //

NG0569:6610: zhes bzlas nye ba'i bsnyen par bshad //

NG0569:6613: pa'i le'u ste lnga brgya bdun cu dgu'o // //

NG0569:6685: shing shags sa bon tsi tra ka / dur khrod sol ba na le sham //

NG0569:6788: mtshan mo chun dril thun du dbab //
