NG0569:13253: 'khor lo sngags bri hri dza spel //
NG0569:13254: bud med thod pa kha sbyar nang du gzhug @#//
NG0569:13255: skud pa rten 'brel dmar po dkri //
NG0569:13256: lha rnams dmar smug chags pa'i mdog / me tog dmar pos mchod cing bzlas //
NG0569:13257: co zi dmar pos ling ga byug / gdungs shing dbang sdud sems ldan pas //
NG0569:13258: 'od zer lcags skyu dmar po yis //
NG0569:13259: bsgrub bya'i snying kha'i srog rtsa zung *//
NG0569:13260: mgrin pa zhags pa dmar pos bcings //
NG0569:13261: rlung gi shugs bzhin myur 'ong bsam //
NG0569:13262: seng ldeng tsan dan me la bsra //
NG0569:13263: sngags pa bzlas ga'u rang 'og gzhug / rtag pa rgyun gyi ting 'dzin bya //
NG0569:13264: shing lo skam po rlung 'das bzhin //
NG0569:13265: bsgrub bya rang dbang med par 'gugs //
NG0569:13266: shing skam rtse mo rtsar 'gugs na //
NG0569:13267: shes ldan rnams la smos ci dgos //
NG0569:13271: rengs pa las kyi 'khor lo ni //
NG0569:13272: dur khrod ras la yung bas bri //
NG0569:13273: lam dang ming spel sngags rnams dgod //
NG0569:13274: nags ma shing gi thang chu dang *//
NG0569:13275: gar sbyin tsha la gu gul gnag / de sbyar rin rab chen po yi //

NG0569:13278: rdo rje rgya gram dbus nyid mnan //
NG0569:13279: ga'u skud pa ser po dkri //
NG0569:13280: lha rnams gser mdog 'dra bar bsgom //
NG0569:13281: lhor bltas sngags bzlas 'od zer ni //
NG0569:13282: ser po 'phros pas dmigs pa de //
NG0569:13283: ser po ri yis mnan par bsam //
NG0569:13284: ri rab rdo rjes mnan byas te //
NG0569:13286: 'khor lo rkang gcig shing gnyan nam //
NG0569:13287: ri rab chen po'i 'og tu mnan //
NG0569:13288: lcags kyi khyud mos bcings pa bzhin //
NG0569:13289: dmigs rings gnas nas 'gul mi nus //
NG0569:13290: lam sba s+tha ne s+tha ba na lam lam ya tha pra ra d+ha ka ra spya /
NG0569:13294: bskrad pa las kyi 'khor lo ni //
NG0569:13295: gro ga shing shun 'khor lo bri //
NG0569:13296: bya rog rkang snyug khrag gis bri //
NG0569:13297: rlung gi dkyil 'khor ming byang spel //
NG0569:13298: smyon pa'i thod pa kha sbyar gzhug / nim pa shing gi bcud dang sbyar //
NG0569:13299: yugs sa mo'i skra'i skud pa nag pos dkri / lha rnams sku mdog ljang sngon bsgom //
NG0569:13300: brnag pa bdag 'dun gsal byas te //
NG0569:13301: 'og tu yam las rlung gi dal //
NG0569:13302: sngon po gzhu'i dbyibs ba dan bzhi //
NG0569:13303: de stengs rlung gi rnga mo ni //
NG0569:13304: sngon po kha ser de rgyab tu //
NG0569:13305: brnag pa bzhag ste de rgyab tu //
NG0569:13306: khro bo gshin rje sngo nag pas //
NG0569:13307: dbyug thos brdeg cing lho phyogs su //
NG0569:13308: rang dbang med par de nas 'gro //
NG0569:13309: bsam zhing bzlas pa'i sngags rdzogs nas //
NG0569:13310: dur khrod ri mthon rtse la sba //
NG0569:13311: bya rog skyer gdags rlung la spur //
NG0569:13312: 'dis ni bsgrub bya gang yin de //
NG0569:13313: rigs mi gcig gi yul du skrod //
NG0569:13314: stobs chen gyis kyang mi zlogs so //
NG0569:13315: hu~m phat sba ra na ya phat /
NG0569:13316: phat u tsa ta ya u tsa ta ye yam yam hu~m phat /
NG0569:13317: b+ha ya b+ha u tsa ta ya hu~m phat /
NG0569:13318: dbye ba las kyi 'khor lo ni //
NG0569:13319: rta dang ma he'i khrag gis bri //
NG0569:13320: gnas bdun sa la de gnyis @#//
NG0569:13322: de yi snying khar 'khor lo gzhug / gcig gi steng du gcig bzhag ste //
NG0569:13323: de gnyis thod pa'i ga 'ur gzhug / skud pa

NG0569:13325: rlung la 'thab // bsam gtan ldan pas sngags bzlas pa //

NG0569:13328: steng du brnag pa zhon dmigs te //
NG0569:13329: gnyis ka'i lag na mtshon cha thogs //
NG0569:13330: gcig la gcig brdeg khro sems kyis //
NG0569:13332: sngags bzlas 'khor lo thod par bcas //
NG0569:13333: nyi ma phyed na dur khrod sba //

NG0569:13336: lus can gnyis la smos ci dgos //
NG0569:13337: nri a shag shag ya ma nri shag pra bi sha ya phat /
NG0569:13338: bi de sha ya phat phat /
NG0569:13339: de ltar 'khor lo'i sbyor ba las //
NG0569:13341: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa gsang sngags snying po'i rgyud las /
NG0569:13342: 'khor lo sbyor ba'i le'u ste brgyad brgya lnga bcu
NG0569:13343: nga lnga'o // // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen
NG0569:13344: gyis // drag po gsad pa'i 'khor lo bshad //
NG0569:13345: dur khrod ro ras zhing lpags la //
NG0569:13346: skye rtsedug dang nim pa dang *//
NG0569:13347: dur khrod sol ba tsha ba gsum //
NG0569:13348: d+ha du ra dang tsi tra ka / tsha ba'i mar khu sme ba lnga //
NG0569:13349: tsan da bi dza srin lag khrag / ka na ka yi khu ba yis //
NG0569:13350: nri rangs rgya dang skya bcad de //

NG0569:13352: shi khrag dug sna rgya sol gyis //
NG0569:13353: skra bshig lhor bltas sha chen mur //
NG0569:13355: dri bo rkang gis 'khor lo bri //
NG0569:13356: mar ngo'i brgyad dang bcu bzhi la //
NG0569:13357: nyi phyed mtshan phyed khro sems kyi //

NG0569:13359: gong bzhin legs par bris byas la //

NG0569:13361: g.yas bskor g.yon bskor kha sbyar te //

NG0569:13364: ming byang bcas // mon pa khram thod bsnol thod brnag / 'khrul 'khor ngar thar dam bskur brlab //
NG0569:13365: sngags pa khro rgyal gshin rje gshed //

NG0569:13439: ka pa sham ku ru hril hril /
NG0569:13442: om om om hu~m hu~m phat phat /
NG0569:13443: 'dus 'dus ram ram yam yam ram ram hring hring dun b+h+yo dun b+h+yo hu~m hu~m phat phat /
NG0569:13444: a mu kam ma ra ya dun b+h+yo /
NG0569:13445: gshin rje gdug pa 'dul ba'i phyir //
NG0569:13446: sangs rgyas thams cad gshin rje yi //
NG0569:13447: dgra gshed sprul te 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NG0569:13448: drag po sngags kyi rim pa'o //
NG0569:13449: 'jam dpal khri drug stong snying po mchog gi rgyud las /
NG0569:13450: drag po 'khrul 'khor gyi le'u ste brgyad brgya lnga
NG0569:13451: bcu drug go / de nas sangs rgyas thams cad
NG0569:13452: ram spyi dpal rdo rje 'chang chen po la /
NG0569:13453: 'jam dpal gzhon nus 'di skad ces gsol to /
NG0569:13454: rdo rje 'chang chen la gsol pa /
NG0569:13455: de bzhin gshegs 'jam dpal khro rgyal gshin rje gshed /
NG0569:13458: rtsa ba'i dngos grub bsgrub thabs la //
NG0569:13459: sku yi phyag rgya chen po dang *//
NG0569:13460: de nyid sgrub thabs rnam grangs dang *//
NG0569:13461: rab tu sbyor ba'i rim pa dang *//
NG0569:13462: mthar thug drag po'i sngags rgod dang *//
NG0569:13463: man ngag gsang ba'i gnas rnams dang *//
NG0569:13464: bla med byang chub thob bya rnams //
NG0569:13465: gang lags rgyas par bshad du gsol //
NG0569:13466: de skad ces ni rab zhus pas //
NG0569:13467: rdo rje 'chang chen gyis gsungs pa //
NG0569:13468: khro rgyal rdo rje 'jigs byed kyis //
NG0569:13469: thun mong khyad par dngos grub rnams //
NG0569:13470: sgrub thabs rgya chen zhus pa rnams //
NG0569:13471: ngas bshad khyod nyon legs par zung *//
NG0569:13472: chos nyid dbyings las rang shar ba'i //
NG0569:13473: rdo rje 'jigs byed gshin rje gshed //
NG0569:13474: sku yi phyag rgya chen po ni //
NG0569:13475: ye shes rol pas shar pa ste //
NG0569:13476: sku mdog mthing nag khros pa la //
NG0569:13477: zhal dgu phyag ni sum cu bzhi //
NG0569:13478: zhabs ni bcu drug brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NG0569:13479: pho mtshan gyen du sgreng ba ste //
NG0569:13480: rtsa ba ma he'i gdong khros pa //
NG0569:13481: de stengs srin po 'jigs pa'i zhal //
NG0569:13482: dmar po zhal nas khrag 'thung 'dzag / de stengs 'jam dpal ser po'i zhal //
NG0569:13484: gzhon nu zur phud lnga dang ldan //
NG0569:13485: rwa yi g.yas na zhal gsum ni //
NG0569:13486: sngon po dmar pos ser por khros //
NG0569:13487: rwa yi g.yon na zhal gsum ni //
NG0569:13488: dkar po dud ka nag por khros //
NG0569:13489: zhal dgu spyan gsum mche ba gtsigs //
NG0569:13490: sma ra smin ma glog ltar 'gyu //
NG0569:13491: shin tu gtum rngam 'jigs tshul bzhugs //
NG0569:13492: khro gnyer ljags 'dril sha khrag za //
NG0569:13493: ha ha pho mo'i rngam sgra sgrogs //
NG0569:13494: phyag g.yas dang po'i gri gug brnams //
NG0569:13495: gnyis pa mtshon cha rtse gcig pa //
NG0569:13496: gsum pa gtun shing bzhi pa gri //
NG0569:13497: lnga pa rdo rje rtse gcig pa //
NG0569:13498: drug pa sta re bdun pa mdung //
NG0569:13499: brgya pa mda' chen dgu lcags kyu //
NG0569:13500: bcu pa dbyug tho bcu gcig kha t+wam kha //
NG0569:13501: bcu gnyis 'khor lo bcu gsum rdo rje bsnams //
NG0569:13502: bcu bzhi rdo rje tho ba bco lnga ral gri bsnams //
NG0569:13504: g.yon gyi dang po thod pa khrag bkang bsnams //
NG0569:13505: gnyis pa tshangs pa lha yi mgo / gsum pa phub ste bzhi pa rkang *//
NG0569:13506: lnga pa zhags pa drug lag pa //
NG0569:13507: bdun pa rgyu ma brgyad pa gzhu //
NG0569:13508: dgu pa thod tshal bcu pa ras //
NG0569:13509: bcu gcig gsal shing bcu gnyis me thab 'bar //
NG0569:13510: bcu gsum dril bu bcu bzhi sdigs 'dzub bsgreng *//
NG0569:13511: bco lnga 'phan rtse gsum pa bsnams //
NG0569:13512: bcu drug rlung gis bskyod pa'i ras //
NG0569:13513: phyag gnyis glang chen ko rlon bsnams //
NG0569:13514: zhabs brgyad g.yas kyi dang pos mi //
NG0569:13515: gnyis pa ma he gsum pas glang *//
NG0569:13516: bzhi pas bong bu lnga pas rnga mo'o //
NG0569:13517: drug pas khyi dang bdun pas lug / brgyad pa'i zhabs kyis wa mnan pa'o //
NG0569:13518: zhabs g.yon dang pos bya rgod mnan //
NG0569:13519: gnyis pas 'ug pa gsum pas bya rog mnan //
NG0569:13520: bzhi pas ne tso lnga pas khra //
NG0569:13523: brgyad pa'i zhabs kyis bzhad mnan pa'o //
NG0569:13524: ral pa dmar ser gyen du brdzes //
NG0569:13525: thod pa skam po'i dbu rgyan can //
NG0569:13526: gcer bu gsus khyim che la brjid //
NG0569:13527: thod rlon khrag 'dzag do zhal can //
NG0569:13528: keng rus dur khrod rgyan gyis mdzes //
NG0569:13529: pho mtshan gyen bsgreng me dpung klong na bzhugs //
NG0569:13530: ha ha phem mo'i sgra sgrogs pas //
NG0569:13531: tshangs pa brgya byin dbang phyug che //
NG0569:13532: khyab 'jug gzhon nu za bar byed /
NG0569:13533: khams gsum dregs pa gsol bar mdzad //
NG0569:13536: lha rnams kun la bsdigs mdzub bsgreng *//
NG0569:13538: dur khrod dkyil 'khor gnas pa'i ma mo dang *//
NG0569:13539: mkha' 'gro lha dang gnod sbyin dang *//
NG0569:13540: ro langs gtum po rgod rnams dang *//
NG0569:13541: dregs pa can rnams bran du 'khol //
NG0569:13542: de lta bu yi gshin rje gshed //
NG0569:13543: rdo rje 'jigs byed chen po de //
NG0569:13544: dur khrod dkyil 'khor dbus na bzhugs //
NG0569:13545: dpa' bo gcig pa'i khro rgyal yin //
NG0569:13546: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud las //
NG0569:13547: sku phyag rgya chen po'i le'u ste brgyad brgya bdun
NG0569:13548: cu pa'o // // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen
NG0569:13549: gyis // de nyid bsgrub thabs rnam grangs bshad //
NG0569:13550: rtog pa bdun pa'i rim pa ni //
NG0569:13551: rtog pa dang po dkyil 'khor bstan //
NG0569:13552: sgo gcig pa ni dbye bar bya //
NG0569:13553: lhag ma yongs su bcad par bya //
NG0569:13554: rtog pa gnyis pa las kun 'grub //
NG0569:13555: gzhan yang rab tu sbyor ba zhes //
NG0569:13556: nyi ma bdun gyi mtsha'o bshad //
NG0569:13557: rtog pa gsum pa sngags btu+u ba //
NG0569:13558: ji lta ba yi cho ga zhes //
NG0569:13559: sgra dbyangs a li ka li ste //
NG0569:13560: / 'bru bcu sum cu rtsa gnyis dang *//
NG0569:13562: rtog pa bzhi pa bsgom pa ste //
NG0569:13563: shin tu mnyam par gzhag bya ba //
NG0569:13564: dpa' po'i gnas la gnas pa'o //
NG0569:13565: zhes bya ba ni gdams ngag gnas //
NG0569:13566: rtog pa lnga pa bris sku ste //
NG0569:13567: 'tshogs par byin gyis brlab par bya //
NG0569:13568: rtog pa drug pa sbyin sreg ste //
NG0569:13569: rje btsun mdun du sha chen dang *//
NG0569:13570: chang dang bcas pa zla ba drug ces pa gdams ngag gnas yin no //
NG0569:13571: rtog pa bdun pa bsam gtan gyi //
NG0569:13572: las rnams bsgrub pa'i sbyor ba ste //
NG0569:13573: snying rje chen pos yid rlan pa //
NG0569:13574: zhes nas bsam ste zhes pa'i bar //
NG0569:13575: de dag gdams ngag gnas yin no //
NG0569:13576: gzhan yang rtog pa bzhi pa nas //
NG0569:13577: de kho na nyid sbyor ba las //
NG0569:13578: shin tu mnyam par bzhag pa yi //
NG0569:13579: sngags par rtag tu bsgom par bya //
NG0569:13580: zhes pas rdzogs ba'i rim par bstan //
NG0569:13581: rgya che zab dang zung 'jug go / de dag rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NG0569:13582: rtog pa bdun pa zhes bya ba //
NG0569:13583: bskal pa dum bu'i rgyud yin zhes //
NG0569:13584: rgyud rgyal 'di las rgyas par bshad //
NG0569:13585: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa'i rgya che rol pa'i rgyud las /
NG0569:13586: rnam par dbye ba'i ste brgyad brgya @#//
NG0569:13587: don gcig pa'o //  // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen gyis //
NG0569:13588: rdo rje 'jigs byed sgrub thabs bshad //
NG0569:13589: rdo rje 'jigs byed khro rgyal mchog / bsgrub par 'dod pa'i sngags pa yis //
NG0569:13590: rgyud chen 'di nyid dbang bskur zhing *//
NG0569:13591: dam tshig ldan pas bsnyen pa bya //
NG0569:13592: de nas bsad dang bskrad pa dang *//
NG0569:13593: dgug dang dbang bsdu dbye dang rengs //
NG0569:13594: ral gri mig sman ril bu ro //
NG0569:13595: bcud len 'byung po ro langs dang *//
NG0569:13596: sha za gnod sbyin pho mo dang *//
NG0569:13597: ma mo mkha' 'gro klu sa bdag / la sogs sna tshogs yid bzhin gyis //
NG0569:13598: nor bu 'dra ba bsgrub par bya'o //
NG0569:13599: dur khrod nang stong mtshan ma gcig / chu 'gram shing gcig ri yi rtse //
NG0569:13600: grong khyer lha khang ma mo'i khyim /
NG0569:13601: khang stong bzhi mdo 'thab mo'i gnas //
NG0569:13602: byin che bkra shis bde gnas su //
NG0569:13603: phyi nang gsang ba'i mtshams bshad de //
NG0569:13604: shin tu mnyam bzhag sngags pa yis //
NG0569:13605: 'byung ba'i tshes ni bcu bzhi la //
NG0569:13606: mtshan mo yar phyed mar phyed na //
NG0569:13607: gcer bu sgra gsil thal chen dang *//
NG0569:13608: rnam par snang mdzad tshil chen gyis //
NG0569:13609: lus byug khrag chen thig le gdab //
NG0569:13610: bdud rtsi rnam lnga sha chen bza' //
NG0569:13611: cang te'u dkrol zhing dur khrod kyi //
NG0569:13612: gnas su ha ha zhes brjod cing *//
NG0569:13613: gar stabs bya zhing sngags bzlas bsgom //
NG0569:13614: rdo rje 'jigs byed chen po dges //
NG0569:13615: ci 'dod pa la dngos grub ster //
NG0569:13616: dur khrod gnod sbyin mkha' 'gro de //
NG0569:13617: thams cad rab dga' las byed khur //
NG0569:13618: de nas sngags pa dpa' bo yi //
NG0569:13619: g.yas pa rjes snang ral gri thogs //
NG0569:13620: g.yon pa thod pa rlon pa thogs //
NG0569:13621: dkyil 'khor lho phyogs gom pa bdun //
NG0569:13622: bor ba'i sa der dong khru gang *//
NG0569:13623: gru gsum bskor ba'i sa dag dang *//
NG0569:13624: gnas bdun grog mkhar sa rnams la //
NG0569:13625: las kyi gshin rje 'jigs byed cing *//
NG0569:13626: g.yas g.yon gri gug thod pa thogs //
NG0569:13627: byas la byang du kha bstan bzhag / chos nyid rnam dag sngags kyi sbyang *//
NG0569:13628: stong nyid hu~m las gri gug gyur //
NG0569:13629: de las las kyi 'jigs byed gyur //
NG0569:13630: de las 'chi bdag mdung gi phug lce spyang stag dom gcan gzan tshogs //
NG0569:13631: ro la 'drad cing bya rog kha //
NG0569:13632: kang ka 'ug pa sha za bri //
NG0569:13633: rnal 'byor gcer bu bsgrub pa po //
NG0569:13634: skra bshig phyag rgya lnga dang ldan //
NG0569:13635: thod pas dbu brgyan ha ha rgod //
NG0569:13636: thod pa cang te'u kha t+wam 'dzin //
NG0569:13637: bcom ldan khros la rtse gcig lta //
NG0569:13638: dur khrod gnas der 'jug pa bri //
NG0569:13639: gzhan gyis mi mthong rab gnas bya'o //
NG0569:13640: dkyil 'khor rdzas kyi lho phyogs dgram //
NG0569:13641: gzhan yang zhing chen zhing chung gi / bla re 'phan 'phran rgyu zhags dang *//
NG0569:13642: mi rkang gling bu thod pa'i rnga //
NG0569:13643: dur khrod keng rus rdzas rnams dgram //
NG0569:13644: khro rgyal rdo rje 'jigs byed kyis //
NG0569:13645: dam rdzas mchod rdzas rgyan rdzas yin //
NG0569:13646: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud las /
NG0569:13647: rdzas dang dkyil 'khor gyi le'u ste brgyad brgya don @#//
NG0569:13648: gnyis pa'o //  // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen gyis //
NG0569:13649: khro rgyal rdo rje 'jigs byed la //
NG0569:13650: mchod pa'i las rim 'di bshad do //
NG0569:13651: om ma ha shu n+ya ta dz+nya na badzra sa ma ti hu~m /
NG0569:13652: om d+harma na swa b+ha at+ma ko\u0f85ham /
NG0569:13654: om a ra pa tsa na d+hi /
NG0569:13655: om ya man ta ka hu~m phat /
NG0569:13656: om hrihsh+ti bi kri ta na na hu~m phat /
NG0569:13657: ya ma ra dza sa to me ya /
NG0569:13658: ya me to ru na yo ta ya /
NG0569:13659: ya ta yo ni ra ya k+she ya /
NG0569:13660: ya k+she ya dza ni ra ma ya /
NG0569:13661: dzahhu~m bam ho badzra sa b+ha ya dza /
NG0569:13672: kha kha kha hi kha hi /
NG0569:13674: pu dza sa ma ya swa ha /
NG0569:13675: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta ar+g+ham pra ti dza ho /
NG0569:13677: ka ya badzra sid d+hi om /
NG0569:13678: ba ka badzra sid d+hi ah tsit+ta badzra sid d+hi hu~m /
NG0569:13679: bla ma yi dam rdzogs sangs rgyas /
NG0569:13680: dbyings nas spyan drang phyag 'tshal mchod /
NG0569:13681: sdig pa bshags shing longs spyod tshogs /
NG0569:13682: bsgrub bya'i rnam par sbyangs spel brlab /
NG0569:13683: mchod dbul mnyes bya mnyam bzhag ste /
NG0569:13684: dpa' bo'i gnas la rtag tu 'dug sngags bzlas ma yengs bsgom par bya 'o //
NG0569:13685: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud las /
NG0569:13686: mchod pa las rim gyi le'u ste brgyad brgya don
NG0569:13687: gsum pa'o // // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen
NG0569:13688: gyis // mnyam bzhag bsgom pa'i rim pa bshad //
NG0569:13690: snying khar a las nyi ma'i dal //
NG0569:13691: de stengs hu~m las rdo rje 'chang *//
NG0569:13692: sngon po rtse dgu kha gyes gdengs //
NG0569:13693: lte bar hu~m yig sngo nag la //
NG0569:13695: bla ma dkon mchog rig pa'i lha //
NG0569:13696: rdo rje 'jigs byed la sogs rnams //
NG0569:13697: mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs te //
NG0569:13698: phyag 'tshal bdun po rnam dag bya'o //
NG0569:13699: de la sngar gyi tshig bcad kyis //
NG0569:13700: 'dod pa'i don gyis gsol ba gdab //
NG0569:13701: rjes su gnang ba byin bsams te //
NG0569:13702: badzra mu yis gshegs su gsol //
NG0569:13703: de nas bsgrub par bya ba ni //
NG0569:13704: tshangs pa'i gnas bzhi tshad med bsgom //
NG0569:13705: sdig tho mi dge'i chos rnams spangs //
NG0569:13706: dge ba rnam par spyod pa ste //
NG0569:13707: sems kyi rgyud cig yongs su dag / sdug bsngal rgya 'bras bral ba dang *//
NG0569:13708: bde ba'i rgyu 'bras phrad par ldan //
NG0569:13709: de nyid mi 'bral rgyun brtan dang *//
NG0569:13710: thams cad kun snyoms chos brgyad bral //
NG0569:13711: de ltar tshad med rnam bzhi bsgom //
NG0569:13712: de nas sngon du chos thams cad //
NG0569:13713: bdag med spros bral ma bcos ngang *//
NG0569:13714: rang bzhin rnam dag byang chub sems //
NG0569:13715: de yi ngang las chos thams cad //
NG0569:13716: snang la rang bzhin med par bsgom //
NG0569:13717: de nas ram las nyi ma'i dal //
NG0569:13718: hu~m la sna tshogs rdo rje bsgom //
NG0569:13719: lte bar hu~m 'od zu ba las //
NG0569:13720: rdo rje'i sa gzhi rwa ba gur //
NG0569:13721: de nas nam mkha'i dbyings nyid du //
NG0569:13722: yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor ni //
NG0569:13723: sngon po rgya gram ba dan mtshan //
NG0569:13724: de stengs a las gyur pa yi //
NG0569:13727: de stengs dmar ser d+hi ru gsal //
NG0569:13728: de las ral gri d+his mtshan pa //
NG0569:13729: ral gri d+his mtshan yongs gyur las //
NG0569:13730: 'jam dpal rdo rje gser mdog can //
NG0569:13731: zhi ba'i tshul 'chang rgyan gyis mdzes //
NG0569:13732: ral gri ut+pal po ti bsnams //
NG0569:13733: a las thugs khar nyi ma yi //
NG0569:13736: phyogs bcu dag na bzhugs pa yi //
NG0569:13737: de bzh-in gshegs pa thams cad dang *//
NG0569:13738: byang chub sems dpa' lha mo'i tshogs //
NG0569:13739: ye shes khro bo spyan drangs la //
NG0569:13740: nyi ma la thim 'jam dpal dang *//
NG0569:13741: de bzhin gshegs dang byang chub sems //
NG0569:13742: thams cad ro gcig chos nyid gyur //
NG0569:13743: sku yi zhing khams dag pa'o //
NG0569:13745: phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med pa'i //
NG0569:13746: dpag tshad stong phrag 'bum khyab las //
NG0569:13747: gsang sngags byin brlabs kun bsdus te //
NG0569:13748: thim pas de nyid hu~m du gyur //
NG0569:13749: mthing nag 'od zer lnga ldan bsam //
NG0569:13750: gsung gi zhing khams dag pa'o //
NG0569:13752: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas byang chub sems //
NG0569:13753: la sogs phyag 'tshan bsdus te thim //
NG0569:13754: rdo rje sngon po rtse dgu pa /
NG0569:13756: lte bar nyi ma'i gdan la hu~m //
NG0569:13757: rdo rje lte hu~m sangs rgyas las //
NG0569:13758: 'od 'phros sangs rgyas zhing yang dag / sems can yongs su smin byas pa //
NG0569:13759: thugs kyi zhing khams dag pa'o //
NG0569:13760: rdo rje phra mo'i 'od zer gyis //
NG0569:13761: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' dang *//
NG0569:13762: ye shes khro mo lha mo rnams //
NG0569:13763: nam mkha' til gyi gang bu ltar //
NG0569:13764: gang ba nyi ma la gnas bsam //
NG0569:13765: de dag rnams kyi mchog bsdus nas //
NG0569:13766: yongs su smin sbyangs byang chub bkod //
NG0569:13767: 'dus nas rdo rje la rab thim //
NG0569:13768: rdo rje de nyid yongs gyur pas //
NG0569:13769: shin tu mi bzad gshin rje gshed //
NG0569:13770: rdo rje 'jigs byed sku ru gyur //
NG0569:13771: shin tu khros shing rngam pa'i gdong *//
NG0569:13772: dus mtha' me ltar 'bar bar bskyed //
NG0569:13773: de la ye shes rigs dbang bskur //
NG0569:13774: rigs kyi bdag pos dbu brgyan la //
NG0569:13775: sku gsung thugs nyid byin gyis brlab //
NG0569:13776: skye mched drug kyang byin gyis brlab //
NG0569:13777: gong bzhin gzhal yas khang nang bsgom //
NG0569:13778: de bzhin rdul tshon dkyil 'khor du //
NG0569:13779: ting 'dzin khro bo sems dpa' bsgom //
NG0569:13781: rang bzhin dbyings kyi gnas chen nas //
NG0569:13782: ye shes sems dpa' khro rgyal nyid //
NG0569:13783: spyan drangs phyag 'tshal gnyis med bstims //
NG0569:13784: sngon du byon la mchod pa dbul //
NG0569:13785: yang na bdag nyid rab gnas pas //
NG0569:13786: de la de bzhin mchod pa dbul //
NG0569:13787: mchod pa'i rnam pa de dag kun //
NG0569:13788: lugs bzhin byin gyis brlabs la dbul //
NG0569:13789: ser mo spos khang thogs la sogs //
NG0569:13790: phyi yi mchod pa byin brlabs dbul //
NG0569:13791: yam ram a tra khang las ni //
NG0569:13794: bdud rtsi rak+ta gtor ma gsum //
NG0569:13795: stong gsum gang bar byin brlabs dbul //
NG0569:13796: yang na 'dod yon lha mor dbul //
NG0569:13797: de dag bsnyen pa'i skabs su'o //
NG0569:13798: bsgrub dang drag po'i skabs rnams su //
NG0569:13799: snang mdzad tshil chen bdug spos te //
NG0569:13800: bkrag mdangs yid 'ong me tog la //
NG0569:13801: drod dang tshil chen mar me 'o //
NG0569:13802: dri chab de bzhin shes par bya //
NG0569:13803: rak+ta de nyid srog gi khrag / gtor ma sha rus tshil la sogs //
NG0569:13804: bdud rtsi bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga //
NG0569:13805: de ltar byin gyis brlabs la dbul //
NG0569:13806: dngos su gsol mnyes tshims par bsam //
NG0569:13807: de nas dkyil 'khor lho sgo nas //
NG0569:13808: bdag nyid dpa' bo'i gnas 'jug 'dug / sngar gyi tshigs su bcad pa yis //
NG0569:13809: ye shes 'jigs byed khros la gsol ba gdab //
NG0569:13810: dpa' bo'i gnas la sngags bzlas bya //
NG0569:13811: bdag nyid thugs khar nyi ma'i gdan stengs su //
NG0569:13812: ya yig sngon po khong stong de dkyil na //
NG0569:13813: rdo rje sngon po rtse dgu kha gdengs pa //
NG0569:13814: lte bar ya dkyil nyi ma hu~m nag po //
NG0569:13815: de la yig 'bru lnga drug bcu pa dang *//
NG0569:13816: bcu bdun sum cu rtsa gnyis sngags kyis bskor //
NG0569:13817: bdag dang mdun gyi 'jigs byed gnyis la bsgom //
NG0569:13818: gsang sngags bzlas pa gang byed dus nyid du //
NG0569:13819: bdag nyid ma he'i zhal nas sngags 'os 'phros //
NG0569:13820: mdun gyi ma he'i zhal du 'od zer zhugs //
NG0569:13821: mdun gyi ma he'i zhal gyi thugs khar thim //
NG0569:13822: dngos grub mthu bsdus bdag gi thugs khar thim //
NG0569:13823: mthu stobs byin brlabs bdag la dngos grub 'dus //
NG0569:13824: mdun gyis ma he'i zhal nas 'od zer byung *//
NG0569:13825: bdag gi ma he'i zhal du 'od zer zhugs //
NG0569:13826: bdag nyid khro bo'i thugs kha nas 'od byung *//
NG0569:13827: mdun gyi 'jigs byed rdo rje'i thugs kar zhugs //
NG0569:13828: thugs dam rgyud bskul sgo gsum dngos grub bsdus //
NG0569:13829: / mdun gyi 'jigs byed thugs nas 'od zer byung *//
NG0569:13830: bdag nyid rdo rje 'jigs byed thugs khar thim //
NG0569:13831: bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum sgrib pa sbyangs //
NG0569:13832: khro rgyal sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub 'dus //
NG0569:13833: bdag dang khro rgyal mthu stobs gnyis med gyur //
NG0569:13834: de ltar gsal bar 'khor lo ltar bsgoms zhing *//
NG0569:13835: gsang sngags bar chad med par ma yengs bzlas //
NG0569:13836: thun mtshams dus su me mar gcig las kyang *//
NG0569:13837: gnyis su mched ltar gnyis byas bzlas pa bya //
NG0569:13838: nang du 'jug dus gnyis po gcig tu thim //
NG0569:13839: sngar bzhin bsam gtan ma yengs bzlas par bya //
NG0569:13840: bzlas pa'i dus su bdud rtsi ril bu'am //
NG0569:13841: me mar chen po kha ru bcug la bzlas //
NG0569:13842: thun mtshams dus su tshogs kyi 'khor lo bya //
NG0569:13843: mchod dbul bstod bskul gang 'dod 'phrin las bcol //
NG0569:13844: drod rtags mtshan ma byung byung bzlas //
NG0569:13845: de dus dngos grub blang zhing gnyis med 'gyur //
NG0569:13846: rdul tshon dkyil 'khor phyags la chu bor @#//
NG0569:13848: yang na sna tshogs nad zor dgra la 'phang *//
NG0569:13849: grangs kyi bsnyen pa bye ba chig 'bum gsum //
NG0569:13850: dus ni rlung nag 'brug sgra 'tshub nag g.yos //
NG0569:13851: mtshan ma phyi nang gsang ba gsum du 'byung *//
NG0569:13852: sngags pa dbang thob dam ldan pas //
NG0569:13853: ma yengs rtse gcig bsgom bzlas na //
NG0569:13854: thams cad las ni thogs med 'grub //
NG0569:13856: thun mong mchog gi dngos grub rnams //
NG0569:13857: ma lus myur du thob par 'gyur //
NG0569:13858: 'di la the tshom med par nges //
NG0569:13859: de skad rdo rje 'chang chen gis bshad //
NG0569:13860: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa gsang sngags snying po'i rgyus las /
NG0569:13861: bsam gtan gyi le'u ste brgyad brgya don bzhi pa'o //  // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen gyis //
NG0569:13862: drag po bsgrub pa'i las rim bshad //
NG0569:13863: mi bsad g.yul bkye ro bsregs dang *//
NG0569:13864: dur khrod mi phung khang sa la //
NG0569:13865: 'brub khung gru gsum khru gang pa //
NG0569:13866: tsher shing kha dmar gtsang gis bskor //
NG0569:13867: thod rlon 'phreng bas kha dgyer bskor //
NG0569:13868: phyi nang dug sna khrag snas byug / sngags pa'i g.yas phyogs de ltar bya //
NG0569:13869: bsgrub bya'i dri chen dri chu dang *//
NG0569:13870: rjes sa skra shad ngar snabs gos //
NG0569:13871: dri ma grog mkhar sa rnams la //
NG0569:13872: ling ga mtho gang dbang po dod //
NG0569:13873: dpral bar rus bris snying khar ni //
NG0569:13874: bla la bla gdags lto bar ming *//
NG0569:13875: dug dang khrag snas bris la gzhug / gri mon
NG0569:13876: rabs chad thod par brnag / dong du bcug la
NG0569:13877: byad kyis bcing *// gzhan yang dur khrod shing gcig dang *//
NG0569:13878: chu 'gram lam gyi bzhi mdo dang *//
NG0569:13879: grog mkhar mtshan ma gcig pa dang *//
NG0569:13880: rgyal po'i sgo dang ri rgod sa //
NG0569:13881: las kyi gshin rje gnas sa la //
NG0569:13882: chu rgod shi khrag lngas sbyar te //
NG0569:13883: gshin rje'i gzugs bya khru gang tshad //
NG0569:13884: zhal gcig phyag gnyis gsus khyim che //
NG0569:13885: gcer bu skra bsil mche ba gtsigs //
NG0569:13886: g.yas g.yon ral gri zhags pa 'dzin //
NG0569:13887: dur sol shing khrag rams kyis byug / snying khar
NG0569:13888: gru gsum brnag pa gzhug / de la dur khrod
NG0569:13889: thod mkhar nas // las kyi gshin rje bkug la bstim //
NG0569:13890: gtor ma byin te las rnams bcol //
NG0569:13891: 'brub khung gzugs la kha bstan bzhag / de nas 'khrul 'khor gzhung bzhin bri //
NG0569:13892: dkyil 'khor bri zhing gtor ma bsham //
NG0569:13893: dkyil 'khor dbus su 'khor lo bzhag / yang na 'brug khung steng du lding *//
NG0569:13894: ting nge 'dzin dang rab ldan pas //
NG0569:13895: slob dpon lho nas drag sngags bzlas //
NG0569:13896: grogs gcig shar nas ling ga dang *//
NG0569:13897: drag po rdzas kyi sbyin sreg bya //
NG0569:13898: byang nas ling ga gtor ma dbul //
NG0569:13899: gcig gis nub nas tshogs mchod bya //
NG0569:13900: thun mtshams bcol bskul dgra la rbad //
NG0569:13901: de yang dang po'i thun la 'jig rten dang *//
NG0569:13902: 'jig rten 'das pa'i thun mong sbyin sreg bya //
NG0569:13903: gnyis nas bzhi pa'i bar du ling ga rus chen dang *//
NG0569:13904: sha khrag tshil dang tsha ba'i mar khu @#//
NG0569:13906: bsnyen pa gang bskyal sngags kyi sbyin sreg bya //
NG0569:13907: mtha' ma'i thun la grogs po bzhi log ste //
NG0569:13908: drag po bsad pa las kyi sbyin sreg bya //
NG0569:13909: yang na rnal 'byor bdag nyid gcig pus bya //
NG0569:13910: de nyid dus kyi bsam gtan ting 'dzin ni //
NG0569:13911: bdag nyid khro rgyal rdo rje 'jigs byed kyis //
NG0569:13912: zhabs brgyad g.yas nas nad brgyad spro ba dang *//
NG0569:13913: zhabs g.yon 'og nas 'phra men ma brgyad spro //
NG0569:13914: thugs kha dag nas zhags pa lcags kyu thogs //
NG0569:13915: mtshon cha thogs pa'i 'jigs byed grangs med spros //
NG0569:13916: brnag pa gang yin thal bar byas par bsam //
NG0569:13917: de ltar rtags byung bar du bsgrub par bya //
NG0569:13918: drag po bsad pa'i sbyor ba dang *//
NG0569:13919: dbang drag la sogs las rnams bya'o //
NG0569:13920: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud las /
NG0569:13921: drag po bsgrub pa'i le'u ste brgya brgya don lnga
NG0569:13922: pa'o // // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen gyis
NG0569:13924: rnal 'byor rdo rje 'jigs byed skur gnas pa //
NG0569:13925: thal chen lus byugs skra bsil ha har rgod //
NG0569:13926: sha chen bdud rtsi ril bu kha ru mur //
NG0569:13927: las kyi 'jigs byed dpang gzugs gtor me btang *//
NG0569:13928: dpa' bo'i gnas 'dug dal bsgrub mchod pa bya //
NG0569:13929: 'byung po'i nyi phyed yol nas lhor bltas te //
NG0569:13930: drag po mtshon cha'i 'khrul 'khor bri bar bya //
NG0569:13931: dur khrod ras sam zhing chen bags pa la //
NG0569:13932: lan tshwa skye tshe nim pa du ru sa //
NG0569:13933: dug sna khrag sna tsha ba gsum //
NG0569:13934: rme ba lnga dang ni ra su //
NG0569:13935: skya bcad dung phyis legs bya te //
NG0569:13936: ka ka ni rangs snyug gu yis //
NG0569:13938: sum cu rtsa gnyis bcu pa yi //
NG0569:13939: sngags dgod hu~m brgyad bri bar bya //
NG0569:13940: de phyir spu gri drag po dgod /
NG0569:13941: kha sbyar bsgrub bya'i ming byang dgod //
NG0569:13942: me gnyis dbus su bzhag la bsad //
NG0569:13943: thod pa kha sbyar nang du bzhug yang na gzugs
NG0569:13944: brnyan lto bar gzhug 'khor lo bri ba'i rim pa'o
NG0569:13946: dbus kyi ya yig yongs gyur las //
NG0569:13947: 'chi bdag gshin rje'i grong khyer bsam //
NG0569:13949: 'gro ba rigs drug khang par bsam //
NG0569:13950: drag sngags me gnyis me dpung 'bar //
NG0569:13951: sngags gzhan 'jigs byed pho brang 'jug / sngags rnams las kyi gshin rje mtshon //
NG0569:13952: gang la reg pa gcod par bsam //
NG0569:13953: ming byang ling kha dgra bo dngos //
NG0569:13954: tshe srog las kyi gshin rje yi //
NG0569:13955: mtshon cha'i khang par 'chang zhing gcod //
NG0569:13956: de ltar bsam gtan sbyor ba bya //
NG0569:13958: nim pa'i shing gi me la bsro //
NG0569:13959: bdag nyid 'jigs byed khro bor bsgom //
NG0569:13961: drag sngags thang gcig bzlas byas te //
NG0569:13962: dkyil 'khor dbus sam dong khar lding *//
NG0569:13963: sngags pa mnye bzhag dpa' bor 'dug / gcer bu skra bshig kha lhor @#//
NG0569:13965: tsha ba'i mar gyis lus byugs te //
NG0569:13966: snang mdzad thal chen rak+tas bsgyur //
NG0569:13967: ma he gdong gi rnal 'byor gyis //
NG0569:13968: 'khor lo rkang skyed gsum khar bzhag / dur khrod me la rab tu bsro //
NG0569:13969: shin tu khros pas drag sngags bzlas //
NG0569:13970: gtum po'i me la 'dug byas na //
NG0569:13972: gzhan yang rab tu sbyor ba ni //
NG0569:13973: gshin rje mtshon cha'i 'khor lo de //
NG0569:13974: bsgrub bya'i rgyu rten ling ga yi //
NG0569:13975: snying khar sngags dang 'khor lo brnag rabs chad mon
NG0569:13976: thod ga bur gzhug las kyi gshin rje'i gzugs brnyan
NG0569:13977: gyis // snying khar thod pa'i ga'u gzhug / ma he gdong gi rnal 'byor gyis //
NG0569:13978: gnas lngar mi rkang phur pa gdab //
NG0569:13979: tsher ma rnon po sna tshogs kyis //
NG0569:13980: tshigs rnams kun la gdab par bya //
NG0569:13981: drag tu sngags bzlas 'khor lo bskor //
NG0569:13982: rdzogs nas nyin mtshan phyed dus na //
NG0569:13983: dur khrod gnas sam ro bsregs par //
NG0569:13984: shin tu gting rings gru gsum brko //
NG0569:13985: gzugs brnyan mgo bo lhor bstan te /
NG0569:13986: kha ni thur du phub la sba //
NG0569:13988: rnal 'byor shin tu gsal byas la //
NG0569:13989: drag tu sngags bzlas ming byang spel //
NG0569:13990: nyi ma bdun gyis nges par 'chi'o //
NG0569:13991: gzhan yang rab tu sbyor ba ni //
NG0569:13992: don po'i bshang gcis ling ga bya //
NG0569:13993: ming byang dang bcas dug gis byug / skra bshig bdag kha lhor bltas te //
NG0569:13994: ma he gdong gi rnal 'byor gyis //
NG0569:13995: dur khrod me la mtshan phyed na //
NG0569:13996: gzugs brnyan gtubs te bsreg bya zhing *//
NG0569:13997: ming byang dang bcas drag sngags bzlas //
NG0569:13998: skad cig gis ni nges par 'chi //
NG0569:13999: rdo rje 'jigs byed nyid kyis bshad //
NG0569:14000: gzhan yang rab tu sbyor ba ni //
NG0569:14001: rdzas kyi 'khor lo sngon bzhin bri //
NG0569:14002: rgyu rten drug la ling kha bya //
NG0569:14003: de yi snying khar 'khor lo gzhug / mar khu chen po dag dang sbyar //
NG0569:14004: dur khrod gnas su bdag nyid kyis //
NG0569:14005: lus la rnam par snang mdzad byug / bdag kha lhor bltas rnam par brtsigs //
NG0569:14006: ma he'i gdong gnas drag tu bzlas //
NG0569:14007: mtshon chas gtums la ro bsregs kyi //
NG0569:14009: gzhan yang rims kyi thebs 'dod na //
NG0569:14010: gshin rje'i 'khrul 'kho ra mtshon cha de //
NG0569:14011: mi yi nya phyis ga 'ur gzhug / dur khrod me la rab bsros te //
NG0569:14012: de nyid kyis ni 'og sbas na //
NG0569:14014: gzhan yang rab tu sbyor ba ni //
NG0569:14015: me long bcu drug 'khor lo la //
NG0569:14016: sum cu rtsa gnyis bcu pa'i sngags //
NG0569:14017: bsgrub bya'i ming dang spel bar bya //
NG0569:14018: sngon gsungs rdzas dang lhan cig tu //
NG0569:14019: bya rog zan gtogs lhag ma dang *//
NG0569:14020: rnam par snang mdzad rgyu rten sbyar //
NG0569:14021: dur khrod ris la byug byas la //
NG0569:14022: sngon bzhin cho gas 'khor lo bri //
NG0569:14023: de ltar sbyor ba tshang byas nas //
NG0569:14025: shing gcig drung sbas bskrad par 'gyur //
NG0569:14028: chu yi nang sbas rengs par 'gyur //
NG0569:14029: khyim du bzhag na zhi bar byed //
NG0569:14030: phyung nas legs dkrus grol bar 'gyur //
NG0569:14031: de dag rdo rje 'jigs byed kyis //
NG0569:14032: drag po bsad pa'i sbyor ba bshad //
NG0569:14033: de dag bsam gtan rim pa ni //
NG0569:14035: sbyor ba nyid la gnas pa yis //
NG0569:14036: sngon du sbyor bas thams cad bya //
NG0569:14037: ram las me dpung dkyil 'khor ni //
NG0569:14038: kun tu gsal bar 'bar bar bsam //
NG0569:14039: gsal zhing 'bar la bsreg pa yi //
NG0569:14040: de stengs bsgrub bya gcer bu ni //
NG0569:14041: skra bshig bred par gyur pa de //
NG0569:14042: bdag nyid mdun du gnas par bsam //
NG0569:14043: bdag lus khro bo mang po spros //
NG0569:14044: ral gri btab nas khrag 'thung zhing *//
NG0569:14045: srog gcod sha za rgyu ma 'dren //
NG0569:14046: 'di skad bsgo zhing kun kyang sgrogs //
NG0569:14047: dkon mchog gsum la gnod byed cing *//
NG0569:14048: bla ma la skur 'debs pa la //
NG0569:14049: rgyob cig song cig ces bsam bya //
NG0569:14050: gzhan yang bdag las sprul pa ni //
NG0569:14051: rnam pa sna tshogs sha zan spro //
NG0569:14052: bya rgod bya rog 'ug pa dang *//
NG0569:14053: khyung khra kang ka ne le dang *//
NG0569:14054: sha zan bya gcan gzan sna tshogs dang *//
NG0569:14055: stag dom lce spyang wa khyi dred //
NG0569:14057: btog cing the shul med par byas //
NG0569:14058: gzhan yang bsgrub bya gang yin de //
NG0569:14059: ri rab kyi mnan sa 'og nub //
NG0569:14060: rgya mtsho'i gting dkrug rba rlabs g.yeng *//
NG0569:14061: me dpung gyis bsregs thal bar brlag / las kyi rlung nag tshub mas khyer //
NG0569:14062: dpag tshad brgyar gnas skyes bu yi //
NG0569:14063: sems shes gsal ba'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NG0569:14064: bsam gtan rab tu sbyor ba 'dis //
NG0569:14065: rdo rje 'dzin pa lta bu yi //
NG0569:14067: srog chags gzhan lta smos ci dgos //
NG0569:14068: des na 'di la bsam gtan bya'o //
NG0569:14069: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa gsang sngags snying po'i rgyud la /
NG0569:14070: drag po sbyor ba'i le'u ste brgyad brgya don drug
NG0569:14071: pa'o // // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen gyis
NG0569:14072: // drag po las kyi mtha' btal ba'i //
NG0569:14073: rab tu sbyor ba'i sbyin sreg bshad //
NG0569:14074: sngags pa dur khrod gnas phyin te //
NG0569:14075: mtshan mo phyed na las 'di brtsam //
NG0569:14076: lha yi rnal 'byor la gnas pas //
NG0569:14077: las ni thams cad bya bar gsungs //
NG0569:14078: phung sa gsum gyi me thab ni //
NG0569:14079: drag po dug khrag rgya sol byug tsher ma dug can shing sna la //
NG0569:14080: dur khrod shing dang me spar te //
NG0569:14081: gang gi dri chen la sogs rdzas //
NG0569:14082: ming rus long kha sen mo skra //
NG0569:14083: mi shi mi rus bong bu'i spangs //
NG0569:14084: de dag mar khu chen pos sbyar //
NG0569:14085: de nyid ma he'i zhal sbyor bas //
NG0569:14086: shin tu mnyam par bzhag byas la /
NG0569:14087: kha ni lhor ltas ro bsregs kyi //
NG0569:14088: me la gang gi ming bcas pa //
NG0569:14089: brgya rtsa brgyad du bsreg byas na //
NG0569:14090: zhag gsum gyis ni 'chi bar nges //
NG0569:14091: yang na phyogs gcig tu gnas la //
NG0569:14092: me thab rdzas sbyor sngon gsungs bzhin //
NG0569:14093: gtum po'i me sbar sbyin sreg bya //
NG0569:14097: gzhan yang 'brub khung me thab tu //
NG0569:14098: gdug pa can shing ro shing la //
NG0569:14099: gtum po dur khrod me spar te //
NG0569:14100: rgyu rten ling ga ming rus bcas //
NG0569:14101: ma rti bya glang shi mtshal dug mar khu chen
NG0569:14102: po til nyungs nag / bsreg cing brgya rtsa brgyad
NG0569:14103: du bya // 'dis ni lha yi tshe yod kyang *//
NG0569:14104: myur du gsod par the tshom med //
NG0569:14105: de dag bsam gtan rab sbyor na //
NG0569:14106: ma he gdong khros rnal 'byor gyis //
NG0569:14107: las rnams thams cad bsgrub par bya //
NG0569:14108: ram yig yongs su gyur pa las //
NG0569:14110: dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar dbus su //
NG0569:14111: bsgrub bya bred sngangs 'dar bar bsam //
NG0569:14112: de la bdag lus rnam sprul pa'i //
NG0569:14113: ba spu las spros gshin rje rnams //
NG0569:14114: srin po mi bzad 'jigs pa'i tshul //
NG0569:14115: sna tshogs lus can ma rungs pa //
NG0569:14116: shin tu gtum rngam mtshon cha thogs //
NG0569:14117: mang pos sha za khrag 'thung zhing *//
NG0569:14118: lus dbang thal bar gtong bar bsam //
NG0569:14119: bya dang gcan gzan de bzhin no //
NG0569:14120: rdo rje'i zhal du'ang de bzhin no //
NG0569:14121: mtha' rgyar mnan gtad sbyor ba bya'o //
NG0569:14122: rab tu sbyor ba 'di lta bus //
NG0569:14123: gang yang gsod sgrol the tshom med //
NG0569:14124: gzhan yang rab tu sbyor ba ni //
NG0569:14126: ma he gdong khros skur bsgom ste //
NG0569:14127: drag tu sngags bzlas 'khor lo bskos //
NG0569:14128: thun rdeg mchog chen phur pa gdab //
NG0569:14129: bsam gtan ldan pas sbyor ba bya //
NG0569:14130: rab tu sbyor ba'i bye brag 'di //
NG0569:14131: su la'ang mi smra sbyin mi bya //
NG0569:14132: mi bstan gcig pu dben par bya //
NG0569:14133: de ni las kun 'grub par nges //
NG0569:14134: gal te mi gzhan mang dag la //
NG0569:14135: bstan cing smras dang byin gyur na //
NG0569:14136: rdo rje sems dpas kyang mi 'grub //
NG0569:14137: de nas gang la'ang bstan mi bya //
NG0569:14138: shin tu sba gsang thabs kyis spyad //
NG0569:14139: om ya ma na ta hu~m phat /
NG0569:14140: om hri sh+ti bi kr-i ta na na hu~m phat /
NG0569:14141: ya ma ra tsa sa to me ya /
NG0569:14142: ya me to ru na yo ta ya /
NG0569:14143: ya ta yo ni ra ya k+she ya dza ni ra ma ya /
NG0569:14155: b+ha smim ku ru ma ra ya hu~m /

NG0569:14921: rwa ni g.yas kyi zhal gsum ste //

NG0569:14924: ya ma ro sha sha subs ril da sta da sta ha ku ru ku ru phat /
NG0569:14926: gsang ba ra lug bla gnas 'joms //
NG0569:14927: ya ma nri ma ra du pa tsa pa tsa ram shad rbad /
NG0569:14929: rkang pa ba glang bla gnas 'joms //
NG0569:14930: ya ma ni thums rmugs ma ra ya na /
NG0569:14931: sha ya na sha ya rbad /
NG0569:14932: rwa ni g.yon gyi zhal gsum ste //
NG0569:14934: lag pas ri dgas bla gnas 'joms //
NG0569:14935: ya ma kri ni sha tru?m mun thibs rbad /
NG0569:14937: kha yi nya sram bla gnas 'joms //
NG0569:14938: kra na ya ma rak+sha tsit+ta shag mar thums rbad /
NG0569:14940: lus kun nye drung bla gnas 'joms //
NG0569:14941: rus pa ma ra ya ha ra ti ya ma ma ka la rag sha nri rbad /
NG0569:14942: phung pa'i 'brub khung dug khrag byug / rten drug ling ga ming byang bcas //
NG0569:14943: rabs chad mon pa srubs drug gnag / yan lag
NG0569:14944: gan rkyal byed du bzhug / yungs kar yungs nag
NG0569:14945: ske tshe dang // dri rims khrag chen rak+ta khyi //
NG0569:14946: ra dug spyang dug dug rgod sbyar //
NG0569:14947: da lo sgrol byed rab gnas bya //
NG0569:14948: gshin rje srin po bya gcan tshogs //
NG0569:14949: mtshon cha me 'bar gang yang sgrol //
NG0569:14950: zhag dgu'i bar du smra gcad bzlas //
NG0569:14951: bdag nyid rdo rje 'jigs byed gnas //
NG0569:14952: rang rang bla rtags dang sbyar te //
NG0569:14953: lus kyi gnas rer thun tshon dbab //
NG0569:14954: thub kha re rdzogs mchod bstod bskul //
NG0569:14955: kun rdzogs ling ga mtshon chas gtubs //
NG0569:14956: drag po'i sbyin sreg byas thal ba //
NG0569:14957: ling ga byas mnan zor du 'phang *//
NG0569:14958: des ni myur du gsod par nges //
NG0569:14959: de skad ma he'i gdong gis bshad //
NG0569:14960: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud las /
NG0569:14961: gnad dgu drag sngags kyi le'u brgyad brgya gya drug
NG0569:14962: pa'o // // bcom ldan rdo rje 'chang chen la
NG0569:14963: // khro rgyal rdo rje 'jigs byed kyis //
NG0569:14964: drag sngags mtshon cha 'di skad brjod //
NG0569:14965: dur khrod la sogs bde gnas su //
NG0569:14966: grub pa thob pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NG0569:14967: drag po bzhi bskor las 'di brtsams //
NG0569:14968: drag po'i gnas chen phung sas bya //
NG0569:14969: dug khrag sol chen la sogs byug / snang mdzad la sogs sbyor bas gzugs //
NG0569:14970: rigs dang bod sgra khrag gis gsal //
NG0569:14971: mtshan mo'i rnam pa gsal bar ldan //
NG0569:14972: gsum gnyis gling gi dung chen brnag / gsod byed tsha ba la sogs byed //
NG0569:14973: drag po'i gnas su gsod mgo bstan //
NG0569:14974: bcu gnyis tshad de khru mtho gang *//
NG0569:14975: gsod byed rgyal po la sogs tshogs //
NG0569:14976: rkyen gyi rnam pa sna tshogs khrag / thig le gnyis dang tsha ba'i 'bru //
NG0569:14977: drag po myur bral dung chen du'o //
NG0569:14978: gnam lcags drag po la sogs pa'i //
NG0569:14979: sna tshogs ral gri gsod byed rgyal //
NG0569:14981: tshogs ngar glud de bzhin du //
NG0569:14982: myos khrag rak+tas stobs bskyed bya //
NG0569:14983: yu bor sa ba swa la swa //
NG0569:14984: / de dag dgug rgyal sgrol byed kyis //
NG0569:14985: bsang dang byin brlabs mthu ldan bya //
NG0569:14986: nyin bzhi mtshan bzhi gnyis bsdebs pa //
NG0569:14987: klad mgrin lte ba snying kha dang ste //
NG0569:14988: rdzas bzhi rim par mtha' ma la //
NG0569:14989: gcod byed gsod byed gnyis su'o //
NG0569:14990: brgya stong grangs kyi de bzhi ste //
NG0569:14991: rdo rje 'jigs byed khros pa yi //
NG0569:14992: gnas las 'od zer rab spros pa //
NG0569:14993: de bzhin gyur te rten gnas bcas //
NG0569:14994: des ni las kyi gshin rje gshed //
NG0569:14995: sngo nag gcer bu mi bzad 'jigs //
NG0569:14996: ral gri sdigs 'dzub ma he zhon //
NG0569:14997: skra 'dzings kha gdangs mche ba gtsigs //
NG0569:14998: mig gsum sma ra khro gnyer can //
NG0569:14999: rang gnas langs te de nyid la //
NG0569:15000: ma he gdong gis bka' bsgo bas //
NG0569:15001: klad pa'i rgya bshig rtsa bcad de //
NG0569:15003: mgrin rtsa kha skyugs ngan rgyun gcad //
NG0569:15004: lte ba yid 'khrugs srid rtsa bcad //
NG0569:15005: snying srog rtsa gcad sha khrag tshogs //
NG0569:15006: bstodacing zos te shul med bsad //
NG0569:15007: de ltar mtshon chas rdul byed la //
NG0569:15008: drag po'i mtha' btul las byas te //
NG0569:15009: de nas gzugs brnyan rdul de la //
NG0569:15010: dur khrod la sogs gnas drag tu'o //
NG0569:15011: rab 'bring tha mas bskyod cing dbab //
NG0569:15012: rgyun gyi rnal 'byor la gnas bya'o //
NG0569:15013: om a kro te ka ya man ta ka ha na ma tha b+ha dza hu~m phat /
NG0569:15014: ro tsa na ma ra ta ka pra ma ni thibs rbad /
NG0569:15015: hri ta ni pa tsa ha na rak+ta tsa ra ni shag rbad /
NG0569:15016: si ra thum ril ru thums mur rdza ni hur rbad /
NG0569:15017: tsit+ta tshal pa ni ma ra ya ku ru ni rbad /
NG0569:15018: sngon du bsnyen pa grub rdzogs pas //
NG0569:15019: gang yang myur du sgrol bar byed //
NG0569:15020: gzhan yang drag po sbyor ba ni //
NG0569:15021: sngags pas gcer bur skra bsil la //
NG0569:15022: lus la thal chen la sogs byug / dur khrod
NG0569:15023: gnas su mnyam par bzhag / sngon du bsnyen rdzogs
NG0569:15024: las 'di spyad // dur khrod chen po drag mchog du //
NG0569:15025: dbugs dang bral ba'i dung chen du //
NG0569:15027: thig le dkar brab sngags rgod bzlas //
NG0569:15028: drag po'i gnas su bsgrub bya brnag / ma he gdong gi rnal 'byor gyis //
NG0569:15029: gnas la rab tu spros byas te //
NG0569:15030: srin po mi bzad 'jigs khro rngam //
NG0569:15031: sna tshogs gzugs can mtshon cha thogs //
NG0569:15032: me lce thog zer tsha tsha 'phra //
NG0569:15033: shin tu ma rungs grangs med 'phros //
NG0569:15034: thim pas de ltar gyur pa bsam //
NG0569:15035: bya dang gcan gzan sna tshogs pa //
NG0569:15036: sha za srog gcod de bzhin no //
NG0569:15037: de ltar mtshan ma las rung bzlas //
NG0569:15038: ling kha rgyu rten ming rus bcas //
NG0569:15039: lan tshwa skye tshe myos khrag dug / byug cing thun du dbab par bya //
NG0569:15040: sha za khrag 'thung srog gcod cing *//
NG0569:15041: lus rnams thal bar gtong bar dmigs //
NG0569:15042: khram thod brnag dpag bsreg par bya //
NG0569:15043: dur khrod la sogs mnan gtad bya //
NG0569:15046: 'dis ni nag po'i bdud kyang sgrol //
NG0569:15047: srog chags mi la smos ci dgos //
NG0569:15050: ya ma tsit+ta thums ril ma ra ya hu~m phat /
NG0569:15051: rtsa ba la gdags bsnyen srog bya'o //
NG0569:15052: rdo rje 'jigs byed ma he'i gdong *//
NG0569:15053: gshin rje gshed khros drag sngags ni //
NG0569:15054: dang po dbang thob bsnyen rdzogs bya'o //
NG0569:15055: gnas bdun la sogs sa rnams la //
NG0569:15056: gshin rje 'jigs pa ma he zhon //
NG0569:15057: rdzas kyi sbyor bas byug byas te //
NG0569:15058: zhags pas ske bzung ral gris gdab //
NG0569:15059: rgyu rten ling ga ming byang bcas //
NG0569:15060: 'brub khung mi shigs khrag thod brnag / dug sna nyungs kar khrag la sogs //
NG0569:15061: gnam lcags byin ldan ral gris gdag / srog gcod las kyi gshin rje la //
NG0569:15062: ma he gdong gis bka' bsgo bas //
NG0569:15063: me tog mtshon gyi char phab ste //
NG0569:15064: ral gris btab nas rtsa srog bcad //
NG0569:15065: sha za khrag 'thung rdul du brlag tshe bla gshin rje'i lto bar 'chang *//
NG0569:15066: 'chor mi srid de gsod par bsam //
NG0569:15067: de nas bsgrub bya'i rnam pa de //
NG0569:15068: las kyi gshin rje'i lto bar bzhag / dur khrod gnas su lhor bltas sba //
NG0569:15069: 'dis na gang lang gsod par nges //
NG0569:15070: gzhan yang zhing chen ras ma la //
NG0569:15071: dug khrag skye tshe nim pa dang *//
NG0569:15072: tsha ba gsum dang sme bas byug / kang ka'i sgro rtsas lhor bltas te //
NG0569:15073: khros pa'i sems kyis gshin rjer bsgom //
NG0569:15074: le tshe bcu bdun 'khor lo ni //
NG0569:15075: rtsibs bzhi ldan par bri bar bya //
NG0569:15076: sngags dgong ming byang spu grir ldan //
NG0569:15077: sngags bzlas gshin rje lto bar gzhug / dur khrod gdug pa'i gnas gtad //
NG0569:15078: des ni gang yang sgrol bar nges //
NG0569:15079: mon pa'i rabs chad thod pa ru //
NG0569:15080: rgyu rten drug gi ling ga ni //
NG0569:15081: ming byang dang bcas byad du gzhug / gcan gzan dri bo'i thod pa ru //
NG0569:15082: dug rgod la sogs dug sna tshogs //
NG0569:15083: gri khrag la sogs khrag sna tshogs //
NG0569:15084: yungs kar yungs nag skye tshe dang *//
NG0569:15085: gnam lcags ral gri thun brab brdeg / rdo rje 'jigs byed rnal 'byor gyis //
NG0569:15086: las kyi gshin rje sha za bskul //
NG0569:15087: sna tshogs nad mtshon dbab cing bsad //
NG0569:15088: dgra bo'i pha mes dur chad du /
NG0569:15089: khams kyi dgra yi gza' skar la //
NG0569:15090: mon thod dbus la rabs chad shar //
NG0569:15091: gri thod lho sba gcan gzan nub //
NG0569:15092: byang du 'brub khung gru gsum bru //
NG0569:15093: drag po'i sbyin sreg sbyor ba bya //
NG0569:15094: de ltar phyogs bzhi dbus su mnan //
NG0569:15095: las kyi gshin rje'i pho brang gdab //
NG0569:15096: gu gul nag po mu zi dang *//
NG0569:15097: mi rta khyi gsum brun dud btab //
NG0569:15098: 'dis ni don po ma lus bar //
NG0569:15099: myur du phung gsod brlag par 'gyur //
NG0569:15100: sngon du bsnyen rdzogs drag sngags bzlas //
NG0569:15101: om ya man ta ka badzra b+hai ra ba ma
NG0569:15102: ha kro d+ha ra dza ya ma sa to me
NG0569:15103: ya / ka la ru pa badzra b+he ra ma ha kro d+ha ya kro d+ha ya /
NG0569:15104: me to ra na yo ta ya /
NG0569:15105: hri sh+ti bi kri ta na na badzra d+he ra
NG0569:15106: pa ma ha kro d+ha ro sha ba ya to
NG0569:15108: karma rak+sha badzra b+hai ra ba ya ma ha kro @#//
NG0569:15109: d+ha u kra ma k+she ya dza ni ra ma ya hu~m phat /
NG0569:15110: ya ma ni ma ra ya dza /
NG0569:15111: ya ma nri ma ra ya thum /
NG0569:15112: ya ma ni ma ra ya phat /
NG0569:15113: ya ma nri ma ra ya hum /
NG0569:15114: ya ma nri ma ra ya nan /
NG0569:15115: de lta bu yi sbyor ba yis /
NG0569:15116: gang la btab kyang gsod par nges /
NG0569:15117: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa sbyor ba gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NG0569:15118: mthar thug drag sngags kyi le'u ste brgyad brgya gya
NG0569:15119: bdun pa'o // // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen
NG0569:15120: pos // man ngag gsang ba'i gnas rnams bshad //
NG0569:15121: rgyud rgyal rdo rje'i tshig yin pas //
NG0569:15122: tshig gcig sna tshogs spros par 'gyur //
NG0569:15123: gsung dbyangs yan lag drug cu tshang *//
NG0569:15124: des na gsung gcig don snang grags //
NG0569:15125: sgo gcig dbye zhing lhag ma bcad //
NG0569:15126: dbang bskur slob bu gcig gzhug cing *//
NG0569:15127: slob bu gzhan ming mi gzhug pa'o //
NG0569:15128: bsnyen dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid gcig pu 'jug grogs po gzhan dag mi 'jug pa'o //
NG0569:15129: bsnyen bsgrub sngags bzlas ma he'i zhal sgra dbyung */
NG0569:15130: zhal gzhan brgyad nas sngags sgra mi 'byung ngo *//
NG0569:15131: 'khrul 'khor dbus kyi yang khongs ming byang bra //
NG0569:15132: phyi rol re mig rnams la bri ba'o //
NG0569:15133: gnyis pa rab tu sbyor ba nyi ma bdun zhes pa /
NG0569:15134: las ma grub na sbog pa'i sbyor ba bstan /
NG0569:15135: las dang ye shes gshin rje gnyis la sogs /
NG0569:15136: nyi ma dang por las kyi gshin rje'i gzugs /
NG0569:15137: gom pa bdun por lho ru kha bub mnan /
NG0569:15138: ye shes 'jigs byed bsgom la sngags bzlas so //
NG0569:15139: gnyis pa thab khung de ru ye shes 'jigs byed bskyed /
NG0569:15140: las kyi gshin rje rkang pa nas gtubs sreg gsum pa ye shes 'jigs byed la spogs gsum /
NG0569:15141: sbyor bas spogs pa rdul tshon dkyil 'khor gyi /
NG0569:15142: bdag nyid byang du bsdad de lho ru kha blta'o //
NG0569:15143: sngags kyi spogs pa dbu zhabs log ste bzlas /
NG0569:15144: ting 'dzin spogs pa dkyil 'khor dbus nyid du /
NG0569:15145: khro bo rdo rje hu~m mdzad skad cig gis /
NG0569:15146: mthing nag zhal gsum g.yas dkar g.yon dmar ba /
NG0569:15147: phyag drug rdo rje 'khor lo be chon g.yas /
NG0569:15148: zhing dbyug lcags kyu sdigs mdzub g.yon zhags bzhi /
NG0569:15149: me dpung klong na khro gtum rngam sgra sgrogs /
NG0569:15150: bsreg rdzas ye shes 'jigs byed bsam la sreg gsum pa ji lta'i cho gas sngags btu+u ba /
NG0569:15151: gzhi nyin nus mthu ldan pa'i yan lag sngags sprul dang */
NG0569:15152: gsang sngags dag pa'i yan lag sngags btu+u ba //
NG0569:15153: nus mthu ldan pas byed pa'i yan lag byin gyis brlab /
NG0569:15154: slob bu mthu ldan byed par rjes gnang sbyin /
NG0569:15155: dang po me long sman spos dri zhim byug srin
NG0569:15156: d+hu ra 'am mtshal gyi phye mas btsag de la
NG0569:15157: 'khor lo re mig dgu pa bri /
NG0569:15158: dbus su a bri re mig brgyad po la /
NG0569:15159: sgra dbyangs yi ge mtshan brgyad tshan re bri /
NG0569:15160: de las 'od 'phros phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten khams /
NG0569:15161: dbyangs sgra'i yi ge bkug nas thim par bsgom /
NG0569:15162: sha chen la sogs pas ni mchod par bya'o //
NG0569:15166: me long steng du bzhag la sngar bzhin mchod /
NG0569:15167: gsum pa sngags las 'od 'phros 'jig rten khams /
NG0569:15168: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten thugs kha gnas pa yi /
NG0569:15169: zla ba'i 'khor lo la 'od 'phros pas thim /
NG0569:15170: me mar gcig la gnyis su dbye ba ltar /
NG0569:15171: bkug nas sngags btus ba la thim par bsgom //
NG0569:15172: snga ma bzhin du mchod pa rgyas par bya /
NG0569:15173: bzhi pa mdun gyi sngags de slon dpon gyis /
NG0569:15174: ma he'i zhal nas bcu gnas snying kha yi /
NG0569:15175: bzlas pa'i 'khor lo'i sngags la thim par bsgom /
NG0569:15176: slob dpon rdo rjes lan gsum sngags brjod pas /
NG0569:15177: rjes su brjod de sngags bzlas pas /
NG0569:15178: slob dpon ma he'i zhal nas sngags 'phreng byung */
NG0569:15179: slob bu'i ma he'i zhal du rab zhugs te /
NG0569:15180: snying khar thim pas byin brlabs ldan par bsgom /
NG0569:15181: bzhi pa shin tu mnyam bzhag dpa' bo'i gnas /
NG0569:15182: lho phyogs gnas ni dkyil 'khor du zhugs bzlas /
NG0569:15183: mchod pa rdzogs nas lho yi phyogs nas 'jug lho yi lag pa'i steng nas bzlas pa bya /
NG0569:15184: lnga pa bris sku bris don gsum ste /
NG0569:15185: 'tshogs par byin brlabs rgyun ni brtan bya dang */
NG0569:15186: de la rab gnas bya ba la sogs pa'o /
NG0569:15187: drug pa rje btsun drung du zla ba drug bsnyen bsgrub sbag ma rdo rje 'jigs byed kyis /
NG0569:15188: lha 'dre gnad la bor ba'i sbyor ba brgyad /
NG0569:15189: rdzas dang sngags dang ting nge 'dzin rnams dang */
NG0569:15190: sbyor ba gnyen po lha dang las kyi lha /
NG0569:15191: rtog pa dang po nas 'byung gnyen po lha yi rdzas /
NG0569:15192: so tshas mal yin las kyi lha yi rdzas /
NG0569:15193: sngags kyi rtsa ba gsum ni gnyen po lha yi sngags /
NG0569:15194: de nyid dregs pa'i ngos 'dzin las kyi lha yi sngags /
NG0569:15195: gnyen po lha yi ting 'dzin bdag dang bdun /
NG0569:15196: thab khung gsum du rdo rje 'jigs byed bsgom /
NG0569:15197: las ky-i lha yi ting 'dzin de gsum bya /
NG0569:15198: gdan gyi 'og tu 'chi bdag gshin rje bsgom /
NG0569:15199: gnyen po lha yi sbyor ba grogs dang bcas //
NG0569:15200: mtshan ma'i sum cha nam stong dang po'i sbyor ba rdul tshon nam /
NG0569:15201: lnga pa'i thang kha la brten bzhi pa'i bsgom pa dang */
NG0569:15202: gsum pa'i sngags tshan gsum po bzlas pa'o //
NG0569:15203: mtshan mo'i gung la dang po'i lnga pa la /
NG0569:15204: rten pa'i bsgrub pa bzhi bsgom pa /
NG0569:15205: gsum pa'i sngags bzlas pa dang ldan par bya'o //
NG0569:15206: nam gyi cha smad sum cha gzhan kun sngar dang 'dra /
NG0569:15207: drug bdun gnyis kyi sbyin sreg mnan pa bya /
NG0569:15208: gnyen po lha yi sreg rdzas ma he'i zhal du dbul /
NG0569:15209: las kyi lha yi sreg rdzas 'chi bdag zhal du dbul /
NG0569:15210: de dus gnyen po'i lha sngags ma he'i zhal nas bzlas /
NG0569:15211: las kyi lha yi sngags ni srin po'i zhal nas bzlas /
NG0569:15212: de ltar nyin mtshan thun gsum drug tu bzlas /
NG0569:15213: dkyil 'khor gzugs brnyan de bzhin zla drug bya'o /
NG0569:15214: bdun pa'i snying rje chen po yid brlan gces /
NG0569:15215: mtshan ma gyen bsgreng rnal 'byor lam bsgom pa /
NG0569:15216: lha yi sku nyid 'ja' tshon bzhin du bsgom /
NG0569:15218: ba khong stong nang du mthing nag hu~m /
NG0569:15219: steng ngam 'og tu om ni dmar po bsgom //
NG0569:15220: ma he'i zhal gyi sna bug steng rlung thur la
NG0569:15221: sdig 'og rlung bsdams nas rlung de yar log pas
NG0569:15222: / yi ge gnyis la thim pas rlung de yar log pas /
NG0569:15223: yi ge gnyis la thim pas rlung de gyen la
NG0569:15224: log sna bug gnyis nas dmar nag 'od zer 'phros
NG0569:15225: / snang ba rten 'brel thams cad gsal bar byas /
NG0569:15226: 'od zer sna bug gnyis nas tshur bsdus nas /
NG0569:15227: yi ge gnyis la thim pas de gnyis gsal bar bsgom /
NG0569:15228: sa bon dag la sems dge zung ba'o //
NG0569:15229: de la brten nas nad sems bzung ba //
NG0569:15230: snang ba rten 'brel dmar nag som snang byas /
NG0569:15231: bsdus pas snang ba thams cad rang la bsdu /
NG0569:15232: rang yang g.yas pa'o rwa zhal gsum la thim /
NG0569:15233: de gsum ma he'i sna bug g.yas nas zhugs /
NG0569:15234: g.yon gyi zhal gsum sna bug g.yon nas zhugs //
NG0569:15235: sku de thams cad yi ge gnyis la thim //
NG0569:15236: yi ge gnyis zhu thig le dmar nag gyur //
NG0569:15237: de yang na da shin tu cha 'phrar gyur //
NG0569:15238: sems gtad pa ni na da sems bzung ba'o //
NG0569:15239: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud las /
NG0569:15240: man ngag gi gnas bdun gyi le'u ste brgyad brgya
NG0569:15241: gya brgyad pa'o // // de nas rdo rje 'chang
NG0569:15242: chen gyis // rdzogs rim byang chub snying po bshad //
NG0569:15243: de kho na nyid sbyar ba la /
NG0569:15244: dpa' bo'i gnas la gnas zhes pa /
NG0569:15245: de la rnam pa gsum ste /
NG0569:15246: zab dang rgya che zung 'jug pa'o //
NG0569:15247: rgya che ba la sems gnas pa //
NG0569:15248: dang po bdag nyid dam tshig sems dpa' yi //
NG0569:15249: thugs khar ye shes sems dpa' de thugs na //
NG0569:15250: sngags kyi 'khor lo gnas pa'i hu~m la dmigs /
NG0569:15251: khrag rlung shas che hu~m nyid dkar dmar ro //
NG0569:15253: de la dbugs drug bar du sems bzung ba /
NG0569:15254: de yi 'od zer gshin rje gshed la spro //
NG0569:15255: de la dmigs te de nas hu~m che spro //
NG0569:15256: de la sems brtan mtha' ma'i sngags la spro //
NG0569:15257: de nas phyi ya yid dang nyi ma ye shes sems dpa' dang *//
NG0569:15258: dam tshig sems dpa' rnams la sngar bzhin spro //
NG0569:15259: hu~m la sems brtan bar du bsgom bar bya'o //
NG0569:15260: de nas phyi yi gzhal yas zhing khams dang *//
NG0569:15261: snang ba rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba kun la spro //
NG0569:15262: 'od de bsdus la ma he'i zhal du bsdu //
NG0569:15263: de la sems gtad gsal ba'i bar du bsgom //
NG0569:15264: gnyis pa zab pa nyid la sems bzung ba //
NG0569:15265: hu~m gsal snang ba rten 'brel kun la spro //
NG0569:15266: lnga pa ltar spros snang ba bdag la bsdu //
NG0569:15267: de bzhin rim par bsdus la hu~m de nyid //
NG0569:15268: na da'i bar du bsdus la na da'i cha phra ba //
NG0569:15269: shin tu mi dmigs gsal zhing brtan par bsgom //
NG0569:15270: gsum pa zung du 'jug la sems gnas pa //
NG0569:15271: spro dang bsdu ba thams cad sngar bzhin bya //
NG0569:15272: rgya che'i dus su snang ba rang rgyud dmigs pa yin //
NG0569:15273: zab pa'i dus kyi na dus gcal pa @#//
NG0569:15275: de nyid snang ba rang bzhin med par bsgom pa'o //
NG0569:15276: de stengs a dmar lte bar hu~m nag bsgom //
NG0569:15277: steng sgo gnyis rlung mnan pa'o //
NG0569:15278: sa bon dang ni thig ler sems bzung bas //
NG0569:15279: sems de dngos med byang chub sems su gsal //
NG0569:15280: rang rig ye shes ma yengs gsal bsgom na //
NG0569:15281: tshe 'dis sa bon byang chub thob par 'gyur //
NG0569:15282: gzhan yang rdzogs pa'i rim pa ni //
NG0569:15283: de kho na nyid sbyor ba la //
NG0569:15284: shin tu mnyam par bzhag pa yi //
NG0569:15285: sngags pas rtag tu bsgom par bya //
NG0569:15286: pho mtshan gyen sgreng zhes pa la //
NG0569:15288: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med do //
NG0569:15289: kun rdzob sems gnas rnam gnyis //
NG0569:15290: hum dang na da la gnas pa'o //
NG0569:15291: dang po lha yi sku nyid ni //
NG0569:15292: snang la gsal ba rang bzhin med //
NG0569:15293: 'ja' tshon lta bu'i rnam par bsgom //
NG0569:15294: de yi lte ba'i gnas nyid du //
NG0569:15295: hu~m yig mthing nag gcig tu gsal //
NG0569:15296: de stengs thig le dmar po bsgom //
NG0569:15297: de nas ma he sna bug ni //
NG0569:15298: g.yas g.yon gnyis rlung mar bsdigs la //
NG0569:15299: 'og sgo bsdams pas rlung de nyid //
NG0569:15300: gyen la yar log hu~m la thim //
NG0569:15302: dngos po thams cad dmar nag gyur //
NG0569:15304: de la rnam par sems gtad gnas pa'o //
NG0569:15305: na da la ni sems gtad gnas pa'o //
NG0569:15306: dngos po kun 'dus rang la thim //
NG0569:15307: g.yas kyi zhal gsum sna bug g.yas nas zhugs //
NG0569:15308: g.yon gyi zhal gsum sna bug g.yon nas zhugs //
NG0569:15309: de dag sku gsum hu~m la bsdus te thim //
NG0569:15310: hu~m nyid na da ra gyur te na da stong pa nyid //
NG0569:15311: de ltar gyur te de la sems gnas pa'o //
NG0569:15312: don dam dag la sems gnas pa //
NG0569:15313: de ltar hu~m dang na da kun //
NG0569:15314: snang la rang bzhin med pa ste //
NG0569:15315: chu zla lta bu'i rnam par bsgom //
NG0569:15316: de yang dngos med skye ba med //
NG0569:15317: stong pa nyid du sems gnas pa'o //
NG0569:15318: / dbyer med ngang la gnas pa ni //
NG0569:15319: de ltar don dam kun rdzob gnyis //
NG0569:15320: ma 'gags ngos bzung med pa ste //
NG0569:15321: yod pa ma yin med pa min //
NG0569:15322: yod med rtag chad mtha' las grol //
NG0569:15323: dngos pos ma rig 'dus ma byas //
NG0569:15324: byang chub sems nyid dngos med stong *//
NG0569:15325: stong la ma zhen sems gnas pa'o //
NG0569:15326: des ni chos sku rang grol ba'o //
NG0569:15327: gzhan yang gsang sngags bzlas pa yi //
NG0569:15328: sems bzung ba yi lugs gnyis te //
NG0569:15329: bsnyen cing bsgrub pa byed dus su //
NG0569:15330: dbugs gnyis phar 'gro sngags bzlas pas //
NG0569:15331: mdun gyi ma he'i zhal du zhugs //
NG0569:15332: mchod phul rgyud bskul byin brlabs bsdus //
NG0569:15333: tshur 'dus byin brlabs dngos grub bdag la thim //
NG0569:15334: rgyun gyi bsnyen pa byed dus su //
NG0569:15335: dbugs nyid thub tshad mar bsdigs la //
NG0569:15336: hu~m la sngags rim gsum gyis bskor //
NG0569:15338: sems can don byas sangs rgyas mchod //
NG0569:15341: de ltar rab tu gsal bsgoms nas //
NG0569:15343: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa snying po gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NG0569:15344: de kho na nyid kyi sbyor ba'i le'u ste brgyad
NG0569:15345: brgya gya dgu pa'o // // de nas rdo rje
NG0569:15346: 'chang chen pos / man ngag rig pa 'di bshad do //
NG0569:15347: ye shes las kyi lha grub pa'i //
NG0569:15348: rtags dang nyams kyi rim pa ni //
NG0569:15349: dbang thob dam tshig mnyam bzhag sngags //
NG0569:15350: rab kyis lha yi sku nyid ni //
NG0569:15351: rdo rje 'jigs byed sngon du mthong *//
NG0569:15352: ci 'dod gsung zhing byin gyis rlob //
NG0569:15353: de la rnal 'byor bsgrub pa pos //
NG0569:15357: lung ston rmi lam mthong bar 'gyur //
NG0569:15358: tha mas zhin can mon pa dang *//
NG0569:15359: mi nag bya nag mchod rten sngo //
NG0569:15360: rlung nag tshub ma 'brug sgra sgrogs //
NG0569:15361: sna tshogs mtshan ma mthong bar 'gyur //
NG0569:15362: gzhan yang go chas lus brgyan dang *//
NG0569:15363: lag na mtshon cha 'bar ba dang *//
NG0569:15364: seng ge la sogs gcan gzan tshogs //
NG0569:15365: bdag gi drung 'khor pho nyar byed //
NG0569:15366: sems gsal ting sran tshugs shing *//
NG0569:15367: snang srid phyag rgya 'bar la sogs //
NG0569:15369: de dus dngos grub blang ba ni //
NG0569:15370: grub pa'i rdzas dang bdud rtsi dang *//
NG0569:15371: snying po lnga dang sha chen lnga //
NG0569:15372: bza' btung longs spyod sna tshogs kyis //
NG0569:15373: dang pos lha la phyag mchod bya //
NG0569:15374: de nas dngos grub rdzas rnams la //
NG0569:15375: om a hu~m gis byin brlabs te //
NG0569:15376: ye shes las kyi lha rnams kyis //
NG0569:15377: snying po bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs //
NG0569:15378: rnal 'byor pa yi sbyor bar bya //
NG0569:15379: bdag gi spyi mgrin snying kha ru //
NG0569:15382: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas byang chub sems //
NG0569:15383: khro bo khro mo thams cad dang *//
NG0569:15384: rdo rje 'jigs byed chen po yi //
NG0569:15385: gnas gsum sku la thim gyur pas //
NG0569:15386: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa phul //
NG0569:15387: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub bsdus //
NG0569:15389: bdag gi lus gnas gsum du thim //
NG0569:15390: lus ngag yid gsum sgrib pa sbyangs //
NG0569:15391: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob //
NG0569:15392: spyi bor om dkar 'od du zhu //
NG0569:15393: sku mdog dkar po dri med 'od //
NG0569:15394: khro bo zla ba'i gdan la bzhugs //
NG0569:15395: thugs khar 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad dkar //
NG0569:15396: snying po om dkar shel 'dra bsgom //
NG0569:15398: sku mdog dmar po dbang dang ldan //
NG0569:15399: khro bo pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs //
NG0569:15401: snying po a dmar dbang ldan sgom //
NG0569:15402: snying khar hu~m mthing 'od du zhu //
NG0569:15403: sku mdog mthing nag drag po'i sku //
NG0569:15404: khro bo'i nyi ma'i gdan la bzhugs //
NG0569:15405: thugs kar rdo rje mthing nag gdengs //
NG0569:15406: rnal 'byor lus ngag yid dang gsum //
NG0569:15409: thun mong mchog gi dngos grub nyid //
NG0569:15410: yang dag nges par thob par 'gyur //
NG0569:15411: gang brtsams las rnams thogs med 'grub //
NG0569:15412: om ya man ta ka hu~m ma ha kro d+ha
NG0569:15413: badzra b+ha ra ba ka ya badzra sid d+hi om
NG0569:15414: / om ka la ru pa a ma ha kro d+ha b+he ra ba ka badzra sid+d+hi om /
NG0569:15415: om hrihsh+tihwi kro ta na na maha kro d+ha badzra b+hai re ba tsit+ta badzra sid d+hi hu~m /
NG0569:15417: de ltar dngos grub mchog thob bya'o //
NG0569:15418: gzhan yang drag po'i sbyor ba yis //
NG0569:15419: las kyi mtha' brgya btul ba ni //
NG0569:15420: ling ga 'khor lo thun dang gces //
NG0569:15421: rabs chad nag po'i thod par bcug / bdud nag drag po'i gnas gtad na //
NG0569:15423: mon pa las byung thod pa bcug / dur khrod gnyan po'i sar mnan na //
NG0569:15424: glo bur glang thabs gsod par 'gyur //
NG0569:15425: mdze can dmar chod thod par bcug / klu nag po la gtad byas na //
NG0569:15426: mdze shul phol 'bras nad kyis gsod //
NG0569:15427: dri bo dmar chod thod par bcug / yul btsan khan dmar la gtad na //
NG0569:15428: gri rgod khram gyis gsod par 'byed //
NG0569:15429: yugs sa mo yi thod par bcug / klu bdud mtsho bdud mo la gtad //
NG0569:15430: rims dal nad kyis gsod par byed //
NG0569:15431: 'byung ba'i lto gshags dbang chen mnan //
NG0569:15432: 'dis ni gang yang tshor mi srid //
NG0569:15433: hri ti bzhi bskor sngags kyis mnan //
NG0569:15434: gzhan yang thun 'phang sbyor ba ni //
NG0569:15435: de bzhin thod par thun gtor sbyar //
NG0569:15436: nad kyi bskal ba sha za'i tshogs //
NG0569:15437: nam mkha' gang bas dgra la gtibs //
NG0569:15438: don po srog gcod brlag par dmigs //
NG0569:15439: gong bzhin thun gyi sngags kyis 'phang *//
NG0569:15440: myur du gsod par gdon mi za //
NG0569:15441: de skad rdo rje 'chang gis bshad //
NG0569:15442: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa snying po gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NG0569:15443: man ngag rim pa'i le'u ste brgyad brgya dgu bcu
NG0569:15444: pa'o // // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen pos
NG0569:15445: // 'phags pa ma he'i gdong can la //
NG0569:15446: bstod cing las bcol 'di gsungs so //
NG0569:15447: snang mdzad tshil chen spos btang ste //
NG0569:15448: rdo rje 'jigs byed skur gnas nas //
NG0569:15450: 'phags mchog khros pa'i rgyal po 'jigs byed ni /
NG0569:15451: skye med rnam dag kyi dbyings nyid las /
NG0569:15452: 'gag med rang byung chen po'i skur bzhengs shig /
NG0569:15453: bdud 'dul dpal chen phyag rgya 'di ston cig /
NG0569:15454: sku mdog mthing nag mi 'gyur drag por mdzad //
NG0569:15455: dbu dgu gab pa mtshon cha gnad dgu 'bebs //
NG0569:15456: dbus zhal ma he'i gdong khros khrag 'thungs ba //
NG0569:15457: spyi gtsug khro 'jigs dmar po srin po'i zhal //
NG0569:15458: steng zhal 'jam dpal zhal ser 'dzum khro 'jigs //
NG0569:15459: rwa g.yas zhal gsum sngon dmar ser po khros //
NG0569:15460: rwa g.yon zhal gsum dkar dud kha gnag / spyan gsum mche gtsigs sma ra ag tshom ser //
NG0569:15461: smin ma khro gnyer glog stong 'od du 'gyu //
NG0569:15462: g.yas zhal gsum nas hum sgra rngam @#//
NG0569:15464: stong gsum dregs pa ma lus bran du 'khol //
NG0569:15465: g.yon zhal gsum nas phat sgra rngam bsgrags pas //
NG0569:15466: gdug pa'i dgra bgegs thal bar rlog par mdzad //
NG0569:15467: dbus zhal gsum nas phem mo'i sgra bsgrags pas //
NG0569:15468: dur khrod ma tshogs thams cad dbang du bsdus //
NG0569:15469: zhal dgus ha he khro gtum bzhad pa yis //
NG0569:15470: stong gsum ma lus g.yo 'gul ldeg par mdzad //
NG0569:15471: phyag gnyis glang po'i lpags rlon 'dzin cing bsnams //
NG0569:15472: bzhi pa chu gri mi yi rkang pa bsnams //
NG0569:15473: lnga pa rdo rje rtse gcig zhags pa bsnams //
NG0569:15474: drug pa sta re ha sta bsnam //
NG0569:15475: bdun pa mdung thung rgyu ma bsnams //
NG0569:15476: brgyad pa mda' chen 'od khung bsnams //
NG0569:15477: dgu pa lcags kyu thams cad tshal bsnams //
NG0569:15478: bcu pa dbyug tho dur khrod ras //
NG0569:15479: bcu gcig kha t+wam gsal shing bsnams //
NG0569:15480: bcu gnyis 'khor lo me thab bsnams //
NG0569:15481: bcu gsum rdo rje dril bu 'khrol //
NG0569:15482: bcu bzhi rdo rje tho ba sdigs mdzub bsgreng *//
NG0569:15483: bco lnga ral gri 'phan rtse gsum //
NG0569:15484: bcu drug cang te'u rlung bskyod pas //
NG0569:15485: sna tshogs mtshon chas gdug pa kun 'dul zhing *//
NG0569:15486: dgra bgegs ma lus myur du sgrol bar mdzad //
NG0569:15487: bcu drug zhabs ni brkyang bskum tshul bzhugs pas //
NG0569:15488: zhabs kyi dang po mi dang bya rgod mnan //
NG0569:15489: gnyis pa'i zhabs kyis ma he 'ug pa mnan //
NG0569:15490: gsum pa'i zhabs kyis glang po bya rog mnan //
NG0569:15491: bzhi pa'i zhabs kyis bong bu ne tso mnan //
NG0569:15492: lnga pa'i zhabs kyis rnga mo bya khra mnan //
NG0569:15493: drug pa'i zhabs kyis khyi dang khyung chen mnan //
NG0569:15494: bdun pa'i zhabs kyis lug dang ri skeg mnan //
NG0569:15495: brgyad pa'i zhabs kyis wa dang bzhad mnan pa'o //
NG0569:15496: 'jig rten byad dang dud 'gro thams cad gdan du mdzad //
NG0569:15497: pho mtshan gyen du sgreng bas 'jig rten gyi //
NG0569:15498: bdud bzhi zil gnon mkha' 'gro dbang du sdud //
NG0569:15499: gsang ba'i rdo rjes ma mo re 'dod skongs //
NG0569:15500: gcer bu mi 'gyur dbyar gyi char sprin 'dra //
NG0569:15501: 'jig rten lha dang gnod sbyin dregs pa can //
NG0569:15502: mgo gcad thod rlon 'phreng bas do shal mdzad //
NG0569:15503: thod pa skam po'i 'phreng bas rab brgyan mdzad //
NG0569:15504: dur khrod keng rus mang po'i rgyan chas mdzes //
NG0569:15505: ye shes me dpung 'bar bas sred gsum bsreg / rdo rje'i sku mchog khro gtum rngam pa yis //
NG0569:15506: bdud dang mu stegs 'jigs byed 'jigs par byed //
NG0569:15507: bdud kyi bdud sde bdud rnams sgrol mdzad pa //
NG0569:15508: rnga sgra nga ro 'brug stong ldir ba yis //
NG0569:15509: 'jig rten dregs pa'i pho mo zil gyis gnon //
NG0569:15510: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na //
NG0569:15511: shin tu mi bzad gtum rngam gar stabs bzhugs //
NG0569:15512: tshangs pa brgya byin khyab 'jug dbang phyug che //
NG0569:15513: khro bo'i gad rgyangs bsgrags pas snying khrag skyug / ma mo mkha' 'gro bdud mo srin mo'i tshogs //
NG0569:15514: dges pa'i gad mos dbang sdud bran du @#//
NG0569:15516: dur khrod sha za srin po ro langs dang *//
NG0569:15517: lce spyang stag dom kang ka bya gcan tshogs //
NG0569:15518: sha za ma lus pho nya sprul par 'gyed //
NG0569:15519: kun bzang 'jigs pa'i nga ro ha ha sgrogs //
NG0569:15520: rngam pa'i rgyal po khrag 'thung gshin rje gshed //
NG0569:15521: rang byung 'gyur med thams cad 'joms mdzad pa //
NG0569:15522: rdo rje 'jigs byed sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0569:15523: bstan pa bshig pa thal ba rdul du rlogs //
NG0569:15524: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud las /
NG0569:15525: rdo rje'i sku la bstod pa'i le'u ste brgyad brgya
NG0569:15526: dgu bcu go gcig pa'o // // de nas rdo
NG0569:15528: 'jam dpal gzhon nus yang gsol pa //
NG0569:15529: dus ngan tha ma'i 'jig rten la //
NG0569:15530: rbod gtong ngan byed nang 'khrug tshe //
NG0569:15531: phyir bzlog 'khor lo bshad du gsol //
NG0569:15532: de skad gsol pas bka' stsal pa //
NG0569:15533: nyon cig 'jam dpal gzhon nu khyod //
NG0569:15534: khro rgyal gshin rje gshed po yis //
NG0569:15535: 'di skad gsungs pa ngas bshad bya'o //
NG0569:15536: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyang *//
NG0569:15537: khro rgyal gshin rje gshed por snang *//
NG0569:15538: nga ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NG0569:15539: ye shes yin te thugs la gnas //
NG0569:15540: nga ni dus gsum mngon pa'i lha //
NG0569:15541: nga ni bde gshegs kun gyi thugs //
NG0569:15542: nga ni khro rgyal kun gyi rje //
NG0569:15543: nga ni nyon mongs bdud 'dul dpal //
NG0569:15544: nga ni dus gsum mngon du byung *//
NG0569:15545: rnam par gzigs la sogs pa yi //
NG0569:15546: sangs rgyas kun pas nga sngar byung *//
NG0569:15547: 'das dus sgron me'i bskal pa ni //
NG0569:15548: me tog 'od ldan bya ba ru //
NG0569:15549: de bzhin gshegs pa 'gro ba'i mgon //
NG0569:15550: klu yi rigs mchog dbyangs zhes bya //
NG0569:15551: nga ni dus gsum da ltar gsan //
NG0569:15552: dus gsum dus med nga yi dus //
NG0569:15553: da ltar 'jam dpal dbyangs zhes bya //
NG0569:15554: nga ni dus gsum phyis kyang 'byung *//
NG0569:15555: byams pa la sogs mos pa yis //
NG0569:15556: bar gyi sgrol ma'i bskal pa ni //
NG0569:15557: yon tan yid 'ong bya ba ya //
NG0569:15558: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes thugs //
NG0569:15559: kun tu gzigs pa'i dbyangs zhes bya //
NG0569:15560: de ltar sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs //
NG0569:15561: ye shes sku nyid rang byung ba //
NG0569:15562: gdul dka' drag po 'dul ba'i phyir //
NG0569:15563: khro rgyal gshin rje gshed por mdzad //
NG0569:15564: dus mtha'i 'jig rten snyigs ma la //
NG0569:15565: byad sngags nus mthu stobs 'gran tshe //
NG0569:15566: sngags pa stobs can rang gi sngags //
NG0569:15567: rang la bzlos ste bsad pa yi //
NG0569:15569: dbang bskur thob pas bsgom par bya'o //
NG0569:15570: rnam dag spros med mtha' bral chos nyid pas //
NG0569:15571: b+h+rum yig dmar ser yongs su gyur ba las /
NG0569:15572: mtshon cha'i 'khor lo rtsibs bcu 'bar ba bsgom //
NG0569:15573: de dbus mthing nag yongs gyur pas //
NG0569:15574: khro rgyal rdo rje 'jigs byed gsal bar bskyed //
NG0569:15575: de yi thugs kyi rdo rje snying po las //
NG0569:15576: phyogs bcu'i rtsibs las rang mdog hu~m yig spro //
NG0569:15577: de nas phyogasas bcu'i khro bo gsal bar bskyed //
NG0569:15578: rdo rje drag po smug nag 'khor lo @#//
NG0569:15580: rdo rje snying po ser nag rdo rje lho //
NG0569:15581: rdo rje rgyal po dmar nag be con nub //
NG0569:15582: rdo rje gtum po ljang nag ral gri byang *//
NG0569:15583: de bzhin shar lho lho nub byang *//
NG0569:15584: byang shar rtsibs la gnas pa'i khro bo ni //
NG0569:15585: rdo rje rnon po dkar ser kha t+wam kha //
NG0569:15586: rdo rje 'bar pa dmar ser me dpung 'bar //
