NG0569:15996: 'chi byed kun las nges par thar //
NG0569:15997: nad dal rims kyis thebs mi srid //
NG0569:15998: ma mo mkha' 'gro gnod sbyin mo //
NG0569:15999: bdag la dga' zhing gus phyag 'tshal //
NG0569:16000: gnod pa'i bsam pa gtan mi rgyu //
NG0569:16001: gang gis bdag mthong dga' zhing byams //
NG0569:16002: bsam pa thams cad yid bzhin 'grub //
NG0569:16003: sgrib pa kun byang ye shes ldan //
NG0569:16004: mig sbyar snang srid sal le mthong *//
NG0569:16006: rnal 'byor kun gyis nyams su blang *//
NG0569:16007: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa don gyis snying po'i rgyud las /
NG0569:16008: rten 'brel yid bzhin gyi le'u ste brgyad brgya dgu
NG0569:16009: bcu go bzhi pa'o // // de nas rdo rje
NG0569:16010: 'chang chen gyis // gshin rje rdo rje 'jigs byed de //
NG0569:16011: las mi byed cing 'khu ldog na //
NG0569:16012: mtshan ma ldog dang gong rkyen 'byung *//
NG0569:16013: nyams mi bde zhing snying mi dga' //
NG0569:16014: de tshe rnal 'byor dam tshig gso //
NG0569:16015: dbang bskur tshogs kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NG0569:16018: yi ge brgya pas mang du bshags //
NG0569:16019: 'jam dpal mtshan ni yang dang brjod //
NG0569:16020: sa tsha sbyin gtong mchod pa bya //
NG0569:16021: des kyang grub par ma gyur na //
NG0569:16022: las kyi gshin rje 'jigs byed la //
NG0569:16023: spogs par bya ba'i rim pa dang *//
NG0569:16024: ye shes 'jigs byed la sogs pa'o //
NG0569:16025: gang byed gnyis la mthun pa ru //
NG0569:16026: dam rdzas gtor ma dkyil 'khor dang *//
NG0569:16027: sbyin sreg mchod pa gsar pa bsham //
NG0569:16028: de nas gzhung bzhin bsgrub par bya //
NG0569:16029: des kyang grub par ma gyur na //
NG0569:16030: gnas bdun sa la byas pa yi //
NG0569:16031: sngar gyi las kyi 'jigs byed dam //
NG0569:16032: yang na gsar pa gcig byas la //
NG0569:16033: sngags pa ye shes 'jigs byed kyis //
NG0569:16034: thugs las ye shes 'od spros la //
NG0569:16035: 'chi bdag gshin rje'i grong khyer nas //
NG0569:16036: las kyi 'jigs byed bkug la bstim //
NG0569:16037: de la don po'i sha khrag sbyin //
NG0569:16038: sngags bzlas las la bskul byas te //
NG0569:16039: lho phyogs gom pa bdun bor gyis //
NG0569:16040: sa ru gru gsum dong brus la //
NG0569:16041: nang du kha bub mgo lhor bstan //
NG0569:16042: sbas te de stengs ye shes kyi //
NG0569:16043: rdo rje 'jigs byed kyis mnan bsgom //
NG0569:16044: gdug pa'i shing la gtum me spar //
NG0569:16045: mi yi rus pa'i sbyin sreg bya //
NG0569:16046: des ni gshin rje las byed 'gyur //
NG0569:16047: des kyang 'grub par ma gyur na //
NG0569:16048: las kyi gshin rje 'jigs byed kyi //
NG0569:16049: sngar bzhin gzugs la dgug gzhug bya //
NG0569:16050: drag po'i me thab gru gsum du //
NG0569:16051: dur khrod gdug pa'i shing sna la //
NG0569:16052: dur khrod gtsubs me spar ba yis //
NG0569:16053: rnal 'byor bdag dang me thab tu //
NG0569:16054: ye shes rdo rje 'jigs byed bsgom //
NG0569:16055: las kyi gshin rje 'jigs byed de //
NG0569:16056: rkang pa gnyis nas gtub byas la //
NG0569:16057: sha chen tshil chen bsgrub bya yi //
NG0569:16058: dri chen ming rus dang sbrags la //
NG0569:16059: sbyin sreg rtsa brgyad la sogs bya //
NG0569:16060: ye shes rdo rje 'jigs byed des //
NG0569:16061: las kyi gshin rje 'jigs byed de //
NG0569:16062: gsol te snam nas bton byas na //
NG0569:16063: rang dbang med par las la bskul //
NG0569:16064: las kyi gshin rje 'chi bdag bdud //
NG0569:16065: ma lus sbran te dgra bo yi //
NG0569:16067: dgra la nad mtshon char ba phab //
NG0569:16068: srog gcod sha za khrag 'thung zhing *//
NG0569:16069: rjes shul med par byed par bsam //
NG0569:16070: des ni gang yang brlag par 'gyur //
NG0569:16071: las kyi gshin rje 'jigs byed la //
NG0569:16072: spogs pa zhes su bshad pa yin //
NG0569:16073: des kyang 'grub par ma gyur na //
NG0569:16074: ye shes rdo rje 'jigs byed la //
NG0569:16075: spogs pa'i thabs ni rnam pa gsum //
NG0569:16077: 'dug thabs byad nas lho ru blta //
NG0569:16078: skra bshig thal chen lus thugs la //
NG0569:16079: sha chen mur zhing zhing chen bgo sngags kyi spogs pa zhes bya ba //
NG0569:16080: drag po rtsa ba'i sngags gsum mo //
NG0569:16081: mgo mjug bzlog la bzlas bya zhing *//
NG0569:16082: de la gcod pa'i spu gri gdags //
NG0569:16083: sbyor ba spogs pa zhes bya ba //
NG0569:16084: gnas bdun la sogs sa rnams kyi //
NG0569:16087: dur khrod ras la khrag dug gis //
NG0569:16088: ya brus gzugs de bdag mdun bzhag bdag nyid rdo rje hu~m mdzad sku //
NG0569:16089: zhal gsum phyag drug khro gtum bskyed //
NG0569:16091: ye shes 'jigs byed gnas nas dgug gzugs brnyan de la yang yang bstim //
NG0569:16092: sngags bzlas mchod pa gtor ma sogs //
NG0569:16093: brnag pa'i sha khrag dmigs la dbul //
NG0569:16094: drag po'i gru gsum me thab tu //
NG0569:16095: dur khrod shing dang tsher ma can //
NG0569:16096: bse dri can dang dug can shing *//
NG0569:16098: dur khrod gdug pa'i me spar la //
NG0569:16099: de dbus rdo rje hu~m mdzad sku //
NG0569:16100: sngags kyis gsal bar rab tu bskyed //
NG0569:16101: shin tu khro 'gying gtum par bsgom //
NG0569:16102: ye shes rdo rje 'jigs byed gzugs //
NG0569:16103: hu~m mdzad ral gris rkang nas gtubs //
NG0569:16104: zhal du gsol dmigs bsrog par bya //
NG0569:16105: de lta ra bsreg grangs mtshan mas dbab //
NG0569:16106: sha chen tshil chen khrag chen dang *//
NG0569:16107: dmar nag skye tshe nyungs kar dang *//
NG0569:16108: don po'i dri chen ming byang bsregs //
NG0569:16109: rdzogs nas rdo rje hu~m mdzad kyi //
NG0569:16110: sna nas ye shes 'jigs byed bton //
NG0569:16111: drag po bsad pa la sogs pa'i //
NG0569:16112: las rnams kun la mngag par bya //
NG0569:16113: thal bas gzugs byas ming byang brnag / dur khrod gshin rje'i gnas su sba *//
NG0569:16114: des ni don po myur du gsod //
NG0569:16115: log non drag po'i rab sbyor ro //
NG0569:16119: ka ra ma ha ba la /
NG0569:16128: rtsa ba swa ha'i sngags bar du /
NG0569:16129: brnag pa gang yin gzhug par bya //
NG0569:16130: 'di ltar log gnon sbyor ba yis //
NG0569:16131: las dang ye shes gshin rje gshed //
NG0569:16132: rdo rje 'jigs byed rnam pa gnyis //
NG0569:16133: rang dbang med par las byed de //
NG0569:16134: don po mngon du gsod par 'gyur //
NG0569:16135: de skad rdo rje 'chang gis bshad //
NG0569:16136: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa mchog gi rgyud las /
NG0569:16137: log non drag po'i le'u ste brgyad brgya dgu bcu
NG0569:16138: go lnga pa'o // // de nas 'khor gyi gtso
NG0569:16139: bo yis // che mchog dpal la yang gsol pa //
NG0569:16140: de bzhin gshegs pa kun bdag dpal //
NG0569:16141: dpal chen gshin rje gshed rgyal po //
NG0569:16142: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan dang *//
NG0569:16144: sbyor ba'i rnam grangs bshad du gsol //
NG0569:16145: de skad gsol ba gsan nas kyang *//
NG0569:16146: rdo rje 'chang gis bka' stsal pa //
NG0569:16148: legs par nyon la yid la zung *//
NG0569:16149: skye med chos sku'i rang bzhin las //
NG0569:16150: skye ba'i cho 'phrul gzugs skur bstan //
NG0569:16151: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag / bcom ldan gshin rje gshed chen gyi //
NG0569:16152: sku gsung yon tan 'phrin las thugs //
NG0569:16153: rdo rje las byung 'khor lo mtshon //
NG0569:16157: dgug dang dbye dang bsad dang mnan //
NG0569:16160: sprul pa rang byung ngos shar zhing *//
NG0569:16161: dus gsum rgyal ba'i bka' ba'o //
NG0569:16162: lte ba thig le spros med las //
NG0569:16163: rtsibs rnams ye shes rtsal du 'phro //
NG0569:16165: gdug pa drag sngags dpal 'bar gyis //
NG0569:16166: nyon mongs sreg phyir nyi ma'o //

NG0569:16168: lus sems gcod pas 'khor lo yin //
NG0569:16169: bsgrub bya'i bya ba gang yin la //
NG0569:16170: mtshan nam nyi ma bzhi bzhi 'grub //
NG0569:16171: de phyir nyi ma bzhi zhes bya //
NG0569:16174: dbang gi gnang ba thob rdzogs nas //
NG0569:16175: dam tshig la gnas rnal 'byor pas //
NG0569:16176: sngon du bya ba'i las rdzogs nas //
NG0569:16177: dur khrod dgu 'dus tshal chen rtsogs //
NG0569:16178: gnas der dge bcu slob ma //
NG0569:16180: dur khrod ras la bam chen gyi //
NG0569:16181: sme ba lnga yi thang pa bya //
NG0569:16182: ni rangs su yi thal ba yis //
NG0569:16183: mtha' mar rgya thang skya bcad de //
NG0569:16184: mchog phran rkang gis pir bya la //
NG0569:16185: snag tsha dug chu zhun ma dang *//
NG0569:16186: bam chen don gyi khrag rnams kyis //
NG0569:16187: rjes su mthun pa'i 'khor lo bri //
NG0569:16188: snying po rtsa ba'i 'khor lo dang *//

NG0569:16211: khro rgyal gshin rje gshed po ni //
NG0569:16213: rdo rje sku yi 'khor lo ni //
NG0569:16214: dbus nas thig bskor rim pa gsum //
NG0569:16215: dbus su thig bzhi rgya gram gdab //
NG0569:16216: 'khrul mig lnga dang gsang mdzod bzhi //
NG0569:16217: phyir rim 'khrul mig bcu gnyis ldan //
NG0569:16218: tha ma rtsibs chen bco brgyad ldan //

NG0569:16220: dbus su khro bdag dpal 'bru lnga //
NG0569:16221: phyi rim sku yi 'phreng ba dgod //
NG0569:16222: rtsibs la gcod byed spu gri dgod /

NG0569:16228: dbye ba dag gi las bya'o //

NG0569:16250: tshangs pa'i tshe dang ldan pa yang *//
NG0569:16253: stobs kyi rgyal po nyid kyang gzir //
NG0569:16254: gzhan lta kun la smos ci dgos //

NG0569:16256: spu gri lnga char mthun pa yin //
NG0569:16257: rtsa ba'i snying po 'di la ste //

NG0569:16310: 'khrul dmigs lnga dbus gnas pa ni //

NG0569:16378: de nas snying po yon tan rdzogs //

NG0569:16380: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa stong phrag brgya pa'i rgyud las /
NG0569:16381: yon tan gyi 'khrul 'khor gyi le'u ste dgu brgya
NG0569:16382: nyi shu pa'o // // de nas rdo rje 'chang
NG0569:16383: chen pos // 'phrin las drag po'i 'khrul 'khor bshad //
NG0569:16384: gshed chen khro rgyal dpa' bo yis //
NG0569:16385: thog med rol pa'i byin rlabs las //
NG0569:16387: dbus nas mu khyud rim pa gsum //
NG0569:16388: dbus kyi lcags mkhar lnga po la //
NG0569:16389: rtsa ba'i snying po 'bru lnga dgod //
NG0569:16390: phyi rim lca gas mkhar lnga po la //
NG0569:16391: me dpal snying po bcu gnyis dgod //
NG0569:16392: tha ma'i rab la gang rung sogs /
NG0569:16393: kha sbyar 'dod pa'i sgrub bya dgod //
NG0569:16394: g.yas g.yon 'bru dad dkrug la sogs //
NG0569:16395: bsad dbab bsrung gzir ro langs sbyar //
NG0569:16396: 'khor lo de dag mnan pa'i thabs //
NG0569:16397: bsad pa drag po'i las byed na //
NG0569:16398: klu'am mtsho bdud btsan la mnan //
NG0569:16399: chu 'khyags dbab pa'i las byed na //
NG0569:16400: yul lha klu dang dmu la mnan //
NG0569:16401: bsrung gzir dag gi las byed na //
NG0569:16402: bka' rten mgon po rgyun srang mnan //
NG0569:16404: 'khrul 'khor rin po che'i rgyal mtshan sa 'phrul gyi me long khri drug stong pa'i rgyud las /
NG0569:16405: 'phrin las kyi 'khor lo'i rgyud las le'u ste dgu
NG0569:16406: brgya nyi shu gcig go / de nas rdo rje
NG0569:16407: 'chang chen gyis // drag po ngan sngags 'di bshad do //
NG0569:16408: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NG0569:16409: ngan sngags bsad pa'i sbyor ba bya //
NG0569:16410: dben la gnyan pa'i dur khrod du //
NG0569:16411: phung sa'i gru gsum sol chen thug / rgyu rten ling ga ming byang bcas //
NG0569:16412: rab chad thod pa srubs drug brnag / dug dang
NG0569:16413: tsha ba gsum gyis thug / dkar nag thig le
NG0569:16414: me 'bar 'brub // khrag chen myos pa gdug pa gsum //
NG0569:16415: 'chi byed sna tshogs thod chen sbyar //
NG0569:16416: dgongs pa ldan pas byin gyis brlabs //
NG0569:16419: byin rlabs dang bcas drag tu bzlas //
NG0569:16420: me 'bar khol lud rlangs pa dros //
NG0569:16421: mthong nas brab cing srog rtsa bcad //
NG0569:16422: nyi shu gcig nas gsod rtags 'byung *//
NG0569:16423: thon nas ling ga gdug par mnan //
NG0569:16424: zor thun dmigs pa'i 'khor la brdeg / badzra kro
NG0569:16425: d+ha ya man ta ka hri te ka la ru
NG0569:16426: pa ya man ta ka nag po srog nan rtsa
NG0569:16427: rbad dbugs khyer kri myags srog la ma ra ya
NG0569:16428: rbad / mi 'gyur nges par dus bzhin gsod //
NG0569:16429: de nas drag po mchog ces bya //
NG0569:16430: de nas thugs mchog gshed chen gyis //
NG0569:16431: rdo rje 'chang chen la zhus pas //
NG0569:16432: dus ngan mtha' ma'i 'jig rten la //
NG0569:16433: sangs rgyas bstan pa 'jig kha ru //
NG0569:16434: skye bo bden pas mi 'dul te //
NG0569:16435: dam tshig gnyan po mi gnas pas //
NG0569:16436: dus der nyams pa bsgral ba'i phyir //
NG0569:16437: drag po ngan sngags mtshon cha rnams //
NG0569:16438: 'khor la rgyas par bshad du gsol //
NG0569:16439: de skad gsol pa gsan nas kyang *//
NG0569:16440: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0569:16441: nyon cig gshed chen 'khor gyi gtso //
NG0569:16442: dus ngan mtha' ma'i 'jig rten la //
NG0569:16443: dam tshig nyams pa bsgral ba'i phyir //
NG0569:16444: ngan sngags rdzogs pa ngas bshad do //
NG0569:16445: 'di nas lho yi phyogs rol na //
NG0569:16446: dpag tshad brgyad khri'i 'og rol na //
NG0569:16447: dur khrod gdug pa'i gnas de na //
NG0569:16448: lcags mkhar thod pa'i pho brang na //
NG0569:16449: gshin rje rnams kyi grong khyer yod //
NG0569:16450: las kyi gshin rje'i sde dpon po //
NG0569:16451: ro langs nag po zhes bya ste //
NG0569:16452: smug nag mdog la shin tu 'jigs //
NG0569:16453: ral gri sdigs mdzub rgyu zhags 'phyar //
NG0569:16454: mig gsum mche gtsigs rtse gdengs pa //
NG0569:16455: ral pa kham nag thod pas gdams //
NG0569:16456: glang chen zhing gyon stag sham can //
NG0569:16457: thod rlon 'phreng ba'i do shal can //
NG0569:16458: rgyu ma sprul dang rak+tas brgyan //
NG0569:16459: / dur khrod me dpung glong na bzhugs //
NG0569:16460: ro rlon stan la brkyang bskum tshul //
NG0569:16461: las kyi gshin rje drug khri gtong *//
NG0569:16462: mngag pa bran dang pho nyar rtsol //
NG0569:16463: dur khrod kang ka lce spyang tshogs //
NG0569:16464: yang sprul ro la gtod cing za //
NG0569:16465: de yi kha nas ngan sngags kyi //
NG0569:16466: mtshon cha drag po'i dbal byung ste //
NG0569:16467: skye 'gro thams cad sgrol zhing zos //
NG0569:16468: de lta bu yi dregs pa des /
NG0569:16469: dpal chen ya man ta ka yi //
NG0569:16470: spyan sngar srog gi snying po phul //
NG0569:16471: bstan pa bsrung bar bro yis bor //
NG0569:16472: de lta bu yi ngan sngags mtshon cha de //
NG0569:16473: nga yis da ltar bshad kyis nyon //
NG0569:16474: babs ni ro langs rag sha snying la dbabs //
NG0569:16475: ya ma ra dza snying la khug thum ril rbad /
NG0569:16476: ya ma ra dza snying myags tshal pa byi ma ya /
NG0569:16479: tshal pa snying rtsa ro la bam ril rbad /
NG0569:16481: che ge mo hri sti ya ma ta kri snying khrag la bam ril rbad /
NG0569:16482: ya ma ra dza snying rtsol rtsa ri me bam ril rbad /
NG0569:16483: ya ma ra dza glo rtsa la bam ril rbad /
NG0569:16484: mchin rtsa rul snying la hri ting rtsa ro me bam ril rbad /
NG0569:16488: srog la de par rtsa snying la rbad /
NG0569:16489: rtsa rag sha khug snying ro la bam ril rbad /
NG0569:16490: ya ma ra dza snying la tod pa rak+sha ma bam ril rbad /
NG0569:16492: snying la khug mchin rtsa bka' pa rtsa ro ma g.yas /
NG0569:16493: ro la gsha' bkra me bam ril rbad /
NG0569:16498: ya ma ra dza sa to me ya /
NG0569:16499: snying la to ru me ya /
NG0569:16500: ya k+she ya ta yo ni snying la to ru me ya /
NG0569:16504: snying la rtsa ro me bam ril rbad /
NG0569:16505: ya ma ra dza rtsa la rod pa khug thum ril /
NG0569:16506: snying la rag sha me bam ril rbad /
NG0569:16507: ya ma ra dza snying la rtsa rtsa nan nan /
NG0569:16508: srog srog rmugs rmugs che ge mo khung thum ril rbad /
NG0569:16509: ya ma ra dza sa to me ya snying la ro sha bam ril rbad /
NG0569:16512: snying la khug bka' sa pa tshal pa /
NG0569:16513: snying la ro tsa bam ril rbad /
NG0569:16514: ya ma ra dza ni dza /
NG0569:16515: gshin rje gshed kyi 'khrul 'khor rin po che'i rgyal
NG0569:16516: mtshan 'phrul gyi me long khri drug stong pa'i rgyud
NG0569:16517: las / lo rgyus drag sngags kyi le'u ste dgu
NG0569:16518: brgya lnga bcu'o // // de nas rdo rje dpal
NG0569:16519: las / chen gyis // sbyor ba'i rim pa 'di bshad do //
NG0569:16520: ngan sngags de nyid bsgrub 'dod pas //
NG0569:16521: dbang thob dam tshig bla ma mchod //
NG0569:16522: dge ba bcu yi las rnams bya //
NG0569:16523: bsnyen pa drod tshad thon tshad bya //
NG0569:16524: dben la gnyan pa'i dur khrod du //
NG0569:16525: ra'i rgod pa la man+dal brtsig khru gang khru do
NG0569:16526: rag tas byug phung po'i gru gsum khru gang ba
NG0569:16527: // kha la thod 'phreng nang logs sbrul //
NG0569:16528: gdug shing rtsang ni nyi shu gcig / zur gsum gri lcags mchog shing gis //
NG0569:16529: phur pa sor brgyad pa re dgod //
NG0569:16530: phyi ru dur khrod sol bas byug / nang du
NG0569:16531: dug sna khrag snas byug / de nang rgyu rten
NG0569:16532: ling ga ni // sor brgyad dbang po yan lag dod //
NG0569:16533: ming rus lo khams snying khar snag / tsha ba
NG0569:16534: gsum dang myos pas byug / yugs sa mo'i skra'i
NG0569:16535: thag pas bcings // bkra mi shis pa'i thod chen brnag / thig le dkar nag tsha ba'i 'bru //
NG0569:16536: rdo phye lcags phye zangs phye dang *//
NG0569:16537: rgyal po g.yung zhing 'chi rkyen dang *//
NG0569:16538: ni ra la sogs gdug khrag bzhi //
NG0569:16539: bkra mi shis pa'i ka pa lar //
NG0569:16540: drag po gnas pa'i mtshan ma dgod //
NG0569:16541: gud du bsrungs la zhing chen dgab //
NG0569:16542: bdag nyid phyag rgyar gsal rdzogs nas //
NG0569:16543: g.yon du shes rab sgrol byed ma //
NG0569:16544: mdun du las kyi gshin rje ni //
NG0569:16545: ro langs nag po 'khor bcas bsgoms //
NG0569:16546: las kyi gshin rje sha za bzhi //
NG0569:16547: khrag 'thung srog gcod drug khri stong *//
NG0569:16548: mtshon cha sna tshogs srog la rngam //
NG0569:16549: 'bru drug sngags kyis gsal bar bskyed //
NG0569:16550: bdag thugs ye shes 'od zer gyi //
NG0569:16551: gnas nas bkug la sngags kyis bstim //
NG0569:16553: gsal bas sngags gsum gtor las bzlas //
NG0569:16554: gtor ma khugs bcas dus gsum bskul //
NG0569:16555: bdun bdun nyi shu gcig tu bzlas //
NG0569:16558: rmi lam sna tshogs sgra snyan 'byung *//
NG0569:16559: klu bdud dmu btsan myos pas sbyang *//
NG0569:16560: de bzhin thun nang ya las bskyed //
NG0569:16561: dgug bstim gtor la bskul dang btab //
NG0569:16563: stong na thun brab dum dril bzlas /
NG0569:16564: khol dang sdud dang rlangs pa dros //
NG0569:16565: zhing skra mchog chen pir gyis brab //
NG0569:16566: srog rten khrag sbal me mar ni //
NG0569:16567: nad mtshon dug dpal tsha tshar 'phro //
NG0569:16568: zhu bcad de sbal bar gyur //
NG0569:16569: brgya brgyad tshad ldan gtor bstab bskul //
NG0569:16570: dngos sam phyugs bshas dud 'gro sha / gsod pa'i mtshan ma byung ba dang *//
NG0569:16571: ling ga zhing chen zhabs mas gril //
NG0569:16572: thod pa dang bcas gnas su mnan //
NG0569:16573: mtshon nag 'khyil ba'i bdud mo la //
NG0569:16574: mnan nas chur grir gsod par 'gyur //
NG0569:16575: ri rul mchan snying bdag po la //
NG0569:16576: gtad khang rti bas dag tu gsod //
NG0569:16577: / byang bltas nyi ma mi 'char zhing *//
NG0569:16578: rlung 'tshub chu mig klu nag la //
NG0569:16579: gtad ma blo bur mdze grir gsod //
NG0569:16580: yul btsan khang dmar gnyan po la //
NG0569:16581: gtad na mtshon gri gzer thab gsod //
NG0569:16582: lha khang 'dre can nang sbas na //
NG0569:16583: smyo 'bog dran pa nyams te gsod //
NG0569:16584: kho rangs pha mes dungs kyi dkyil //
NG0569:16585: mnan na kha phung nyal gyis 'chi //
NG0569:16586: dus brgyad kha gso rgyun du bya //
NG0569:16587: gzhan yang las kyi mchong chen ni //
NG0569:16588: drag po las kyi 'brub khung de //
NG0569:16590: sha tshil mi byang mar nag dug / mjug ma la dz+wa la ram gsum gdags //
NG0569:16591: brgya rtsa brgyad du bsreg byas te //
NG0569:16592: thal ba ling kha gong bzhin mnan //
NG0569:16593: thun zor dmigs pa'i rten la brdeg / 'dis ni tshangs pa'i tshe ldan yang *//
NG0569:16595: srog chags mi la smos ci dgos //
NG0569:16596: gshin rje gshed kyi 'khrul 'khor khri drug stong pa'i rgyud las /
NG0569:16597: ro langs nag po'i le'u ste dgu brgya lnga bcu
NG0569:16598: nga gcig go / // de nas rdo rje dpal
NG0569:16599: chen gyis // gshin rje gshed gsum drag sngags bshad //
NG0569:16600: gong bzhin rnal 'byor sngon byas pas //
NG0569:16601: man+dal dbus su gru gsum bka'o //
NG0569:16602: khrag chen rgya sol sbyar bas byug / zur re gshin rje re re dgod //
NG0569:16603: de yang ji ltar yin zhe na //
NG0569:16604: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NG0569:16606: dpal chen ya man ta ka dang *//
NG0569:16607: yum chen e ka dza ti gnyis //
NG0569:16608: gnyis med rol pa'i byin brlabs las //
NG0569:16609: drag po gshin rje gshed gsum 'khrungs //
NG0569:16610: 'gan dang pa ti stobs mchog dang *//
NG0569:16611: rkang pa'i rgyal po gsum du byung */
NG0569:16612: khams gsum dus gsum sgo gsum la /
NG0569:16613: dbang sgyur tshe srog bdag por byung *//
NG0569:16614: sha za khrag 'thung srog gcod cing *//
NG0569:16615: srid pa kun kyang 'jigs par nus /
NG0569:16617: bstan pa bsrung ba'i mtshon char mngags //
NG0569:16618: skye 'gro thams cad sgrol byed pa //
NG0569:16621: badzra ki li badzra bi ga ta /
NG0569:16622: mi sba nya tu tra ba sni /
NG0569:16626: shag pa sni ma ra ya rbad rbad /
NG0569:16627: badzra ki li badzra bi ga te /
NG0569:16630: ki kam rbad thuri li ri li dza hi b+h+yo /
NG0569:16631: ka ma li shag snying kha rag ya ti ta dza /
NG0569:16632: bi sna ma ra ya rbad rbad /
NG0569:16633: ardza na ki la ya hu~m phat /
NG0569:16634: mu ti pa tu snying khag rag rbad /
NG0569:16635: ka mu li shag snying rbad /
NG0569:16636: mgo shag ga ba sni ma ra ya rbad rbad /
NG0569:16637: de lta bu yi drag sngags kyis /
NG0569:16638: srog chags rnams kyi srog gcod de /
NG0569:16639: 'khrul 'khor rin po che rgyal mtshan 'phrul gyi me long gi rgyud las /
NG0569:16640: drag sngags byung khungs kyi le'u ste dgu brgya lnga
NG0569:16641: bcu nga gnyis so // // de nas dpal chen
NG0569:16642: rdo rje khros // drag sngags sbyor ba'i thabs 'di bshad //
NG0569:16643: 'brub khung gru gsum shar zur du //
NG0569:16644: gzugs med khams la dbang sgyur zhing *//
NG0569:16645: 'gro ba'i yid la mnga' mdzad pa //
NG0569:16646: 'das pa'i gshin rje gshed rgyal po //
NG0569:16647: ga na pa ti dgod par bya //
NG0569:16648: gri lcags thog lcags phur pa gzugs //
NG0569:16649: de bzhin gru gsum lho zur du //
NG0569:16650: gzugs kyi khams la dbang sgyur zhing *//
NG0569:16651: 'gro ba'i lus la mnga' mdzad pa //
NG0569:16652: de ltar gnas pa'i gshin rje gshed //
NG0569:16653: stobs mchog rgyal po dgod par bya //
NG0569:16654: seng ldeng smug po'i phur ba gzugs //
NG0569:16655: de bzhin 'brub khung bya zur du //
NG0569:16656: 'dod pa'i khams la dbang sgyur zhing *//
NG0569:16657: 'gro ba'i dag la mnga' mdzad pa'i //
NG0569:16658: ma 'ongs gshin rje gshed chen po //
NG0569:16659: dga' ba'i rgyal po dgod par bya //
NG0569:16660: mchog chen phur pa dag kyang gzugs //
NG0569:16661: rtan drug grog mkhar bag phye la //
NG0569:16662: ling kha ming rus snying khar dgod //
NG0569:16663: gan rkyal 'og rkang shar nub bzhag chags myos thig le gnyis thod chen //
NG0569:16664: gtor ma rag ta gzhung bzhin bsham //
NG0569:16665: dang po bdag nyid 'ga' na lta //
NG0569:16666: sku mdog nag po dbus mthing ka / spyan rtsa dmar bzlog mche ba gtsigs //
NG0569:16667: phyag g.yas gnam lcags phur pa bsnams //
NG0569:16668: phyag g.yon lcags kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NG0569:16669: gsal bsgom drag sngags sum khri bzlas //
NG0569:16670: tho rangs skya rengs shar tsam na //
NG0569:16671: dpral ba'i skra mtshams lcags phur gdab //
NG0569:16672: ngan sngags phur bus mgo lus gzams //
NG0569:16673: rtsa srog gcad de thal bar bsams //
NG0569:16674: gnyis pa bdag nyid stobs mchog gshed //
NG0569:16675: sku mdog sngon po dbus dkar po //
NG0569:16676: mche gtsigs spyan rtsa ser po bzlog / phyag g.yas seng ldeng phur pa bsnams //
NG0569:16677: phyag g.yon zangs kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NG0569:16678: der gsal zhal nas ngan sngags bsgrags //
NG0569:16679: rkang pa g.yon pa'i bol gong du //
NG0569:16680: skya rings seng lding phur bsngags gdab //
NG0569:16681: mtha' mar bdag nyid dga' ba'i rgyal //
NG0569:16682: sku mdog dmar po dbus nag po'i //
NG0569:16683: spyan rtsa dkar bsgrigs mche ba gtsigs //
NG0569:16684: phyag g.yas mchog chen phur pa bsnams //
NG0569:16687: des bsgom zhal nas ngan sngags bzlas //
NG0569:16688: rkang pa g.yas la skya rengs gdab //
NG0569:16689: nyi ma'i tshe la phur pa dbyung *//
NG0569:16690: thun la bsngags shing khung bur blug / nyi phyed
NG0569:16691: rgya tshil me la mug / brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas
NG0569:16692: mgo nas gtub // khrag gi thig pa re re dang *//
NG0569:16693: ming rus nas phyung li dum bsreg / thal ba rlung 'phyar chu chen 'bab //
NG0569:16694: gong gi gnas su mnan par bya //
NG0569:16695: 'di lta bu yi ngan thabs kyis //
NG0569:16697: zhag bdun zla bdun lo dus na //
NG0569:16698: thal ba'i ling ga gnas su mnan //
NG0569:16700: de nas shin tu gsang ste spyad //
NG0569:16701: gshin rje gshed kyi 'khrul 'khor khri drug stong pa'i rgyud las /
NG0569:16702: gshin rje gsum gyi le'u ste dgu brgya lnga bcu
NG0569:16703: nga gsum mo // // de nas rdo rje 'chang
NG0569:16704: chen gyis // gshin rje gshed kyi drag sngags bshad //
NG0569:16705: ra dza ha la yag sha ni //
NG0569:16706: mi dbal gshed chen zungs thar byed //
NG0569:16707: ya ma chos kyi rgyal po ni //
NG0569:16708: ma he nag po la zhon nas //
NG0569:16710: bsal gshin nag po ya pa ti //
NG0569:16711: bdag bting chu glang nag po zhon //
NG0569:16712: khrag skyug byed cing srid bzhi 'dzin //
NG0569:16713: myos byed 'bar bas glang mgo can //
NG0569:16714: dud kha rdo rje ro langs te //
NG0569:16715: bran byas srid pa'i khog 'bubs byed //
NG0569:16716: gshin rje gsod byed smug nag de //
NG0569:16717: ral pa tshar dgu pho nyar gtong *//
NG0569:16718: sbrul nag zhon nas gang dmigs pa'i //
NG0569:16719: gsod cing srid pa'i byag byed do //
NG0569:16720: gshin rje phya sangs chos kyi rgyal po yis //
NG0569:16721: 'khor lam rgyud lnga skos dbang byed //
NG0569:16722: ded dpon tshangs pa kun 'dres ni //
NG0569:16723: nyi zla'i 'khor lo la zhon te //
NG0569:16724: srid pa kun gyi skos 'debs so //
NG0569:16725: gcod cing sbyor ba'i las byed do //
NG0569:16726: rtel pa ya ba ta'i 'khor na //
NG0569:16727: dbugs 'phrog dbang po ther shag ni //
NG0569:16728: rlung gi rnga mo la zhon nas //
NG0569:16729: srid pa kun gyi dbugs len no //
NG0569:16730: dam sri nag po gnod sbyin no //
NG0569:16731: lcags kyi spyang zhon glang mgo'i 'khor //
NG0569:16732: dbang po 'khar byed dmigs pa ni //
NG0569:16733: smyo 'bog sha ba la zhon nas //
NG0569:16734: srid pa kun gyi bla rnams rku //
NG0569:16735: mig dmar ral pa tshar dgu'i 'khor //
NG0569:16736: srog gcod dbang po ma ru rtse //
NG0569:16737: lkugs pa lug la zhon nas kyang *//
NG0569:16738: gang la bya ba'i srog gcod do //
NG0569:16739: de ltar sprul pa yang sprul bcos //
NG0569:16740: lha mchog ya man ta ka yi //
NG0569:16741: bka' sdod pho nya mngag par 'khol //
NG0569:16742: chos kyi rgyal po bka' sdod 'khor //
NG0569:16743: ya ba ya ti gdan du bting *//
NG0569:16744: a ba glang mgo bran du 'khol //
NG0569:16745: ral pa tshar dgu pho nyar 'gyed //
NG0569:16746: phya sangs srid pa'i skos 'debs so //
NG0569:16747: rtel pa srid pa'i dbugs len no //
NG0569:16748: rmig pa srid pa'i bla rnams rku //
NG0569:16749: mig dmar srid pa'i srog gcod byed //
NG0569:16750: de ltar dpal chen gshed 'khor na //
NG0569:16751: las kyi gshin rje mi zad pa //
NG0569:16752: dregs pa can ni bsam mi khyab //
NG0569:16755: bla rku dbugs len tshe 'phrog cing *//
NG0569:16757: ngan sngags mtshon chas nad 'bebs cing *//
NG0569:16758: sgrol byed bstan pa gnyan po srung *//
NG0569:16759: gshin rje gshed kyi 'khrul 'khor khri drug stong pa'i rgyud las /
NG0569:16760: las byed tshul gyi le'u ste dgu brgya lnga bcu
NG0569:16761: bzhi pa'o // // de nas rdo rje che mchog
NG0569:16762: gis // drag sngags sbyor ba'i rim pa bshad //
NG0569:16763: gzhung dang mthun pa'i bde gnas su //
NG0569:16764: sngon du bya ba'i las rdzogs nas //
NG0569:16765: gru gsum 'bar bar ling kha brnag / mchog phur seng ldeng gri lcags phur //
NG0569:16767: dang po byin brlabs rtags la dbab //
NG0569:16768: dgos pa dang bcas brdeg cing gsad //
NG0569:16769: 'bru thun spyang thod myos pa phag / 'chi byed mi shis thod chen no //
NG0569:16770: phur pa dang bcas dgongs ldan pas //
NG0569:16771: spyi bo snying kha lte bar dbab //
NG0569:16772: rus dang ming snying khams la bcad //
NG0569:16773: drod dang ldan nas bsreg par bya //
NG0569:16774: brgya rtsa brgyad rdzogs rten thal ba //
NG0569:16775: de bzhin ling kha gnyan sar gnan //
NG0569:16776: thal ba rlung chu thun rten ma'o //
NG0569:16777: 'dis ni nag po'i bdud kyis gsod //
NG0569:16778: gzhan srog chags smos ci dgos //
NG0569:16779: slob dpon la skur smad byas na //
NG0569:16781: de nas bla ma slob dpon bkur //
NG0569:16782: de dag drag sngags 'di lta ste //
NG0569:16783: a kro te ka ya man ta ka a ba ye /
NG0569:16784: ka la ru ma mu kha la /
NG0569:16786: ya ma sa ma ya dza /
NG0569:16787: srog la gzir dgra bo ma ra ya rbad /
NG0569:16788: om hrish+tihbi kri ta a na na dgra bo ma ra ya hu~m phat /
NG0569:16789: shri many+dzu dza man ra ra ka ya ma ra dza /
NG0569:16792: dgra bo ma ra ya sod /
NG0569:16793: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa rtog pa'i rgyal po chen po'i rgyus las /
NG0569:16794: sku gsung thugs kyi gzer sngags kyi le'u ste dgu
NG0569:16795: brgya lnga bcu nga lnga pa'o // // gzhan yang
NG0569:16797: 'brub khung ling kha thod chen brnag / sha chen la sogs gtor ma bca' //
NG0569:16798: srubs drug mi shis ka pa lar //
NG0569:16799: sbyor ba btab la thun kyang bca' //
NG0569:16800: thal chen bkram la byad rjes brtags /
NG0569:16801: khugs nas bdeg pa'i las bya'o //
NG0569:16802: gshin rje gshed chen khro rgyal gyis //
NG0569:16803: las kyi gshin rje dbang med bkol //
NG0569:16804: dgra la nad mtshon bskal pas gsod //
NG0569:16805: sbyor ba thon nas bsreg mnan 'phang *//
NG0569:16806: bla ma bkur zhingadam tshig ma nyams rdug mi srid //
NG0569:16807: lo yi dus bzhin nges par sgrol //
NG0569:16808: nyams na rang yang 'chi byed na //
NG0569:16809: las de 'grub par smos ci dgos //
NG0569:16810: de ltar drag po'i ngan sngags ni //
NG0569:16811: ya ma rag sha ba hra myags /
NG0569:16813: ya ma tsa srog smugs ra sha na /
NG0569:16817: gshin rje gshed khri drug stong pa'i rgyud las /
NG0569:16818: las kyi gshin rje'i drag sngags kyi le'u ste dgu
NG0569:16819: brgya lnga bcu nga drug pa'o // // gzhan yang
NG0569:16823: gtor ma mchod pa de bzhin bca' //
NG0569:16824: khyad par gdong dmar sho na dang *//
NG0569:16825: gsod byed mkha' lding phag lding phag don sbyar //
NG0569:16826: ting 'dzin ldan pas byin brlabs bsgrub //
NG0569:16827: dbab cing gdab dang gtub byas te //
NG0569:16829: ma nyams lo dus 'gyang mi srid //
NG0569:16830: nyams na rang yang phung bar 'gyur //
NG0569:16831: des na dam tshig srog ltar srung *//
NG0569:16832: gdug pa'i drag po sngags rgod brdeg / ya man
NG0569:16833: ta ka hri sti sarba ka la ru pa hri
NG0569:16834: myags dgra bo ma ra ya sod /
NG0569:16835: ni sha ku ru ni rtsa rbad /
NG0569:16836: u nan khyer b+h+yo yam ram hu~m rbad /
NG0569:16837: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa'i rgyud las /
NG0569:16838: las mchog 'dus pa drag sngags kyi le'u ste dgu
NG0569:16839: brgya lnga bcu nga bdun no // // gzhan yang
NG0569:16841: dong thun ling ga mchod yon bsham //
NG0569:16842: dug khrag snying thun phur pa 'bru //
NG0569:16843: dgongs pa ldan pas tshad mas dbab //
NG0569:16845: thon nas drag po'i shing rnams la //
NG0569:16846: tsan+da li yi me spar bsreg / thal ba la sogs sbyor ba bya //
NG0569:16847: 'dis ni grib so dbab pa bzhin //
NG0569:16848: cis kyang mi bzlog nges pa yin //
NG0569:16849: de dag drag sngags 'di lta ste //
NG0569:16850: ya man ta ka ka la ru pa hri ti /
NG0569:16854: dgra bo srog la thun rmugs ma ra ya rbad rbad /
NG0569:16855: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa'i rgyud las /
NG0569:16856: ar la gtad de gsad pa'i le'u ste dgu brgya
NG0569:16857: lnga bcu nga brgyad do // // gzhan yang rno
NG0569:16859: 'brub khung nang du ling ga brnag / dug 'bru
NG0569:16860: khrag phung snying thun brdeg / srog dbugs me mar
NG0569:16861: gsad cing rbad // shes pa dwangs snyigs phye la rta //
NG0569:16862: dngas ma rab 'bring tha ma yis //
NG0569:16863: chos nyid phyag rgya go char bya //
NG0569:16864: snyigs ma gdug pa'i lag tu gtad //
NG0569:16865: bsreg cing mnan te 'phang byas la //
NG0569:16866: brag dang rdo la btab kyang 'gags //
NG0569:16867: srog chags rnams la smos ci dgos //
NG0569:16868: dam tshig dbang dang slob dpon bskur //
NG0569:16869: rno dbal drag sngags sbyor ba ni /
NG0569:16870: hri sti ya man ta ka tsit+ta sham sham ka la ru pa /
NG0569:16871: a ni ani u ne u ne /
NG0569:16873: ma sha ya dgra bo rtsa la rbad rbad /
NG0569:16875: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa'i rgyud las /
NG0569:16876: rang mnan drag pos bsad pa'i le'u ste dgu brgya
NG0569:16877: lnga bcu nga dgu pa'o // // 'jam dpal gzhon
NG0569:16879: sangs rgyas kun bdag de bzhin gshegs //
NG0569:16880: rdo rje 'chang chen khro bo'i rgyal //
NG0569:16881: khro rgyal dpal chen he ru ka'i //
NG0569:16882: bsgom pa rnam par bkod pa las //
NG0569:16883: phyi nang gsang ba de kho na'i //
NG0569:16884: mthar thug gang lags bshad du gsol //
NG0569:16885: de skad gsol pa gsan nas kyang *//
NG0569:16886: rdo rje 'chang chen gyis gsungs pa //
NG0569:16887: zhus don ngas bshad legs par nyon //
NG0569:16889: bla med byang chub thob bya'i phyir //
NG0569:16890: sangs rgyas thams cad khro bor sprul //
NG0569:16891: de yi mngon rtogs rim pa @#//
NG0569:16893: rnam grangs mang yang rnam bzhir 'dus //
NG0569:16894: phyi dang nang dang gsang ba dang *//
NG0569:16895: mthar thug de kho na nyid do //
NG0569:16896: he ru ka dpal khro rgyal gyi //
NG0569:16897: mtshan bcas mtshan med bskyed rdzogs lam //
NG0569:16898: gang bsgrubs bla med byang chub thob //
NG0569:16899: de dag rgyas pa 'di lta ste //
NG0569:16900: ri rgyal lhun po dur khrod gnas //
NG0569:16902: sngags pa dbang bgrod dam ldan pas //
NG0569:16903: phyi bsgrub sbyor ba'i rim pa ni //
NG0569:16904: dur khrod la sogs gnas sa na //
NG0569:16905: stegs bu rgya dpangs khru do gang *//
NG0569:16906: khrag sna bdud rtsi spos kyis byug / ba sus thig gdab ni rangs kyis /
NG0569:16907: dbus mthing rtsibs bzhi phyogs dang bstun //
NG0569:16908: rtsibs mchan mdzes ldan phyi nang bskos //
NG0569:16909: thod rlon rdo rje'i ra bar bskor //
NG0569:16910: gru chad khrag mtsho dur khrod tshogs //
NG0569:16911: de la gnas pa'i khro rgyal ni //
NG0569:16912: dbus su bud d+ha he ru ka //
NG0569:16913: smug nag zhal gsum phyag drug rngam //
NG0569:16914: g.yas dkar g.yon mthing dbug smug zhal //
NG0569:16915: dang po 'khor lo ri rab bsnams //
NG0569:16916: bar pa be con kha t+wam ga mtha' ma dril bu sbrul zhags 'phen //
NG0569:16917: bdud dang mu stegs gdan la bzhugs //
NG0569:16918: sangs rgyas khro mo dbang phyug la //
NG0569:16919: dur dmar snying thogs stob cing 'khril //
NG0569:16920: shar rtsibs badzra he ru ka / mthing nag zhal gsum phyag drug khros //
NG0569:16921: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NG0569:16922: rdo rje dgra sta phur pa g.yas //
NG0569:16923: dbyug tho me dpung ril spyi g.yon //
NG0569:16924: dri za lha yi gdan la bzhugs //
NG0569:16925: rdo rje khro mo dbang phyug ma //
NG0569:16927: / lho rtsibs rat+na he ru ka / ser nag zhal gsum phyag drug 'jigs //
NG0569:16928: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus ser zhal //
NG0569:16929: rin chen gri gu cang te'u g.yas //
NG0569:16930: gtun shing sdigs mdzub nyi ma g.yon //
NG0569:16931: grul bum gshin rje'i gdan la bzhugs //
NG0569:16932: khro mo rin chen dbang phyug ma'o //
NG0569:16933: nub rtsibs pad ma he ru ka / dmar nag zhal gsum phyag drug brjid //
NG0569:16934: g.yas dkar g.yon sngo dbus dmar zhal //
NG0569:16935: pad ma lcags kyu rgyu zhags g.yas //
NG0569:16936: tho ba zhing dbyug mdung thung g.yon //
NG0569:16937: klu dbang chu bdag gdan la bzhugs //
NG0569:16938: khro mo pad+ma dbang phyug ma'o //
NG0569:16939: byang rtsibs kar ma he ru ka / ljang nag zhal gsum phyag drug gtum //
NG0569:16940: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus ljang zhal //
NG0569:16941: ral gri rgya gram gsal shing g.yas //
NG0569:16943: gnod sbyin 'byung po'i gdan la bzhugs //
NG0569:16944: khro mo las kyi dbang phyug ma //
NG0569:16945: kun kyang zhabs bzhi brkyang bskum bgrad //
NG0569:16946: stod smad glang chen zhing chen stag / thod pa skam rlon dbu rgyan dang *//
NG0569:16947: do shal rigs bzhi sbrul gyis brgyan //
NG0569:16948: khrag zhal thal ba me 'bar dbus //
NG0569:16949: dpa' sgeg bzhad pa'i tshul gyis bzhugs //
NG0569:16950: shar lho nub byang rtsibs mchan bzhir //
NG0569:16951: ye shes khro rgyal chen po bzhi //
NG0569:16954: mthing nag be con 'khor lo bsnams //
NG0569:16955: lho nub shes rab mthar byed sku //
NG0569:16956: ser nag dbyug pa spu gri bsnams //
NG0569:16957: nub byang pad ma mthar byed sku //
NG0569:16958: dmar nag zhing dbyug rgyu zhags bsnams //
NG0569:16959: byang shar bgegs mthar byed pa'i sku //
NG0569:16960: ljang nag rdo rje kha sdengs gram //
NG0569:16961: zhing chen gdan la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NG0569:16962: spyan gsum zhal gdangs mche ba gtsigs //
NG0569:16963: dur khrod chas brgyad rdzogs par ldan //
NG0569:16964: gru chad dur khrod rak+ta'i mtshor //
NG0569:16965: ke ri brgyad dang 'phra men brgyad //
NG0569:16966: gong nas 'dus pa'i tshul du gnas //
NG0569:16967: de ltar dkyil 'khor gsal bkod nas //
NG0569:16968: gtor ma dam rdzas mchod pa'i rdzas //
NG0569:16969: phyi nang gsang ba rdzogs par bsham //
NG0569:16970: dur khrod rgyan dang bu don dgram //
NG0569:16971: zhing chen zhing chung bla re 'phen //
NG0569:16972: ga 'u rgyu zhags thod pa'i rnga //
NG0569:16973: tshil chen mar me gsur chen spos //
NG0569:16974: sha khrag sna tshogs gtor ma dang *//
NG0569:16975: rak+ta bdud rtsi phyi mchod lnga //
NG0569:16976: de dag rdzogs par bshams pa ni //
NG0569:16977: phyi sgrub rdul tshon brten pa yin //
NG0569:16978: gzhan yang dung chen mtshan ldan pas //
NG0569:16979: ging lnga pa 'am dmu lugs gnyis //
NG0569:16980: rag ta bdud rtsi g+hi wang dang *//
NG0569:16981: spos sna tshogs sman sna tshogs //
NG0569:16982: bla ba shing kun chu gtsang sbyar //
NG0569:16983: rang rang tshon rtsi kha dog gis //
NG0569:16984: tshangs pa'i sbug tu badzra he ru ka / dpral
NG0569:16985: bar bud d+ha he ru ka / rna g.yas rang
NG0569:16986: na he ru ka / ltag par pad ma he
NG0569:16987: ru ka rna g.yon kar ma he ru ka /
NG0569:16988: mtshams bzhir khro rgyal mthar byed bzhi //
NG0569:16989: mtha' ma rang rang sngags kyis bskor //
NG0569:16990: gcig la de bzhin yum rnams bri //
NG0569:16991: dung chen ga'u kha sbyar du //
NG0569:16992: snying chen sar pa ma nyams par //
NG0569:16994: ha he b+h+yo phat 'bru rnams dgod //
NG0569:16995: bdud rtsi thig le btab pa yis //
NG0569:16996: dkar dmar dar gyis brgyan pa la //
NG0569:16997: rdzas de man+dal dbus su bzhag / ga'u gzhal yas khang nang du //
NG0569:16998: lha bskyed ye shes spyab drangs bstim //
NG0569:16999: de ltar rdzas bshams bsgom bzlas pa //
NG0569:17000: nang bsgrub thod pa la brten yi //
NG0569:17001: gzhan yang gzugs brnyan ma yin te //
NG0569:17002: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo la //
NG0569:17003: ye shes lha rnams rdzogs par ldan //
NG0569:17004: dbus kyi thig le spros med la //
NG0569:17005: khro rgyal bud d+ha he ru ka / khro mo sangs rgyas dbang phyug ma //
NG0569:17006: mdun gyi chos nyid rtsa dkar la //
NG0569:17007: khro rgyal badzra he ru ka / khro mo rdo rje dbang phyug ma //
NG0569:17008: g.yas kyi ye shes rtsa ser po //
NG0569:17009: khro rgyal he ru ka / khro mo rin chen dbang phyug ma //
NG0569:17010: rgyan gyi yon tan rtsa dmar la //
NG0569:17011: khro rgyal pad ma dbang phyug ma //
NG0569:17012: g.yon gyi rang rgyud rtsa gnag la //
NG0569:17013: khro rgyal ka ra ma he ru ka / khro mo las kyi dbang phyug ma //
NG0569:17014: yab yum rdzogs nas gsal bar bsgom //
NG0569:17015: chos nyid g.yas su gshin rje gshed //
NG0569:17016: g.yon du gzhan gyis mi thub pa //
NG0569:17017: ye shes g.yas su rta mchog dpal //
NG0569:17018: g.yon gyi rtsa la bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NG0569:17021: ke'u ri sid+ha dbang phyug sgo //
NG0569:17022: de bzhin gsal zhing rdzogs par gnas //
NG0569:17023: ye shes dkyil 'khor spyan drang bstim //
NG0569:17024: de ltar gsal ba'i dgongs pa ni //
NG0569:17025: gsang ba snying gi 'khor lo bshed //
NG0569:17026: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa mngon par rtogs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0569:17027: phyi nang gsang ba'i le'u ste dgu brgya gcig go /  // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen gyis //
NG0569:17028: mngon rtogs rim pa 'di bshad do //
NG0569:17029: gtor ma mchod yon dam rdzas rnams //
NG0569:17030: 'dod yon lha mo byin gyis brlabs //
NG0569:17031: ye shes dkyil 'khor lha tshogs la //
NG0569:17032: mnyes shing tshim par mchod pa dbul //
NG0569:17033: phyi nang gsang mtshams dam du bcad //
NG0569:17035: ma rig nyon mongs las dbang gis //
NG0569:17036: nag po gdug pa srid gsum bdud //
NG0569:17037: bsgral zhing log rtog rnam sbyang phyir //
NG0569:17038: sangs rgyas thams cad khro bor mdzad //
NG0569:17040: chos nyid rang bzhin rnam par dag / ye shes dngos med rang snang bar //
NG0569:17041: chos rnams snying po byang chub sems //
NG0569:17042: sangs rgyas kun gyi snying po nyid //
NG0569:17043: dbang chen lnga yi rim par gnas //
NG0569:17044: snang ba rnam dag chos kyi dbyings //
NG0569:17045: ye shes dkyil 'khor phyag rgya'i tshogs //
NG0569:17048: chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NG0569:17049: chos sku'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang *//
NG0569:17050: gdul bya rnam sbyangs mthar bsgral phyir //
NG0569:17051: ye shes rol pa rang snang ba'i //
NG0569:17052: khro rgyal gzugs skur bzhengs su gsol //
NG0569:17054: ye shes khro rgyal 'bar ba'i sku //
NG0569:17055: thabs dang shes rab dkyil 'khor tshogs //
NG0569:17056: thugs rje thabs kyis spyan 'dren na //
NG0569:17057: dbyings las bskyod med gshegs su gsol //
NG0569:17059: skye med chos sku dag pa las //
NG0569:17060: ye shes khro rgyal rngam pa'i sku //
NG0569:17061: thabs dang shes rab dkyil 'khor la //
NG0569:17062: thugs rje thabs kyis spyan 'dren na //
NG0569:17063: dbyings las bskyod med gshegs su gsol //
NG0569:17065: skye med chos sku dag pa las //
NG0569:17066: ye shes khro rgyal rngam pa'i sku //
NG0569:17067: thabs dang shes rab dkyil 'khor la //
NG0569:17068: sgo gsum dang bas phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0569:17069: ye shes rab snang dkyil 'khor la //
NG0569:17070: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor brtan par bzhugs //
NG0569:17072: ye shes khro dpal dkyil 'khor la //
NG0569:17073: gdugs mchog me tog ye shes sgron //
NG0569:17074: dri chab gtsang bshos mchod pa 'bul //
NG0569:17075: thugs rjes bzhes mdzod dngos grub gsol //
NG0569:17077: snang srid ye shes rang shar ba'i //
NG0569:17078: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor bsam mi khyab //
NG0569:17079: mdzad pa'i 'phrin las grub pa rtags //
NG0569:17080: ye shes gar gyis mchod par bzhes //
NG0569:17082: rang byung rnam dag dug lnga sel //
NG0569:17083: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i sman //
NG0569:17084: dug lnga bdud rtsi mchod pa 'di //
NG0569:17085: ye shes khro rgyal dkyil 'khor la //
NG0569:17086: mchod par 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NG0569:17088: chos kyi sku la rang shar ba'i //
NG0569:17089: ye shes khro rgyal 'bar ba'i sku //
NG0569:17091: he ru ka / kro d+hi shwa ri dbyings kyi yum //
NG0569:17092: gshin rje mthar byed la sogs pa'i //
NG0569:17093: khro ba'i rgyal po shes rab thabs //
NG0569:17094: gtso 'khor yab yum sprul pa bcas //
NG0569:17095: gnas yul phyag rgya dbang phyug tshogs //
NG0569:17096: pho nya phyag brnyan bran g.yog bcas //
NG0569:17098: bla med mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NG0569:17099: snang srid mchod pa'i longs spyod mchog ye shes 'dod yon sna tshogs snang *//
NG0569:17100: phyogs bcu rab 'byams rnam dag zhing *//
NG0569:17101: rin chen gzhal yas dpag bsam shing *//
NG0569:17102: 'gro drug lha dang lha mo'i tshogs //
NG0569:17103: snang srid kun bzang mchod pa'i sprin //
NG0569:17104: gzugs mdzes sgra snyan bsam mi khyab //
NG0569:17105: dri zhim zhal zas rol mo tshogs //
NG0569:17106: reg bya mdzes pa sna tshogs brgyan //
NG0569:17107: ye shes khro rgyal dkyil 'khor la //
NG0569:17108: mchod pa 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NG0569:17109: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub gsol //
NG0569:17111: thabs dang shes rab dgyes sbyor ba'i //
NG0569:17113: bde ba chen po rab gsal nas //
NG0569:17114: khro rgyal dkyil 'khor mnyes gyur cig / bo d+hi tsit+ta ma ha su ka pu tsa ho /
NG0569:17115: bud d+ha he ru ka hu~m /
NG0569:17116: khams gsum bskul ba'i zhing gyur rnams //
NG0569:17117: khro chen sprul pa'i byin brlabs rnams //
NG0569:17118: khro chen sprul pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NG0569:17119: bsgral te rnam shes dag par sbyangs //
NG0569:17120: sha khrag lus po mchod pa 'bul //
NG0569:17123: snang srid rtsi bcud zhal zas tshogs //
NG0569:17125: ro mchog brgyad ldan bza' btung mchog / 'dod yon lha mo mdzes ldan brgyan //
NG0569:17126: stabs byed gar bsgyur glu dbyangs len //
NG0569:17127: ye shes khro rgyal dkyil 'khor la //
NG0569:17128: mchod pa 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NG0569:17130: khyad par rmad du byung ba yi //
NG0569:17131: 'bru thog longs spyod gtor ma dang *//
NG0569:17132: sha chen khrag chen sna tshogs dang *//
NG0569:17133: sa yi snying po ra sa ya //
NG0569:17134: zhal zas mchog chen mchod pa 'di //
NG0569:17135: ye shes khro rgyal dkyil 'khor la //
NG0569:17136: mchod pa 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NG0569:17137: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub gsol //
NG0569:17139: ma rig lus ngag yid gsum gyi //
NG0569:17140: nyams shing 'khrul pas nongs bgyis rnams //
NG0569:17141: ye shes khro rgyal dkyil 'khor du //
NG0569:17142: gnong zhing 'gyod pas mthol lo bshags //
NG0569:17143: tshangs pa bzhes la dngos grub gsol //
NG0569:17144: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wan /
NG0569:17145: ma ha shri he ru ka badzra kro d+ha tsa ya /
NG0569:17150: om ru lu ru lu hu~m /
NG0569:17152: sa ma ya mu tra b+han tsa kra hu~m phat /
NG0569:17153: ma ha kro d+hi shwa ri /
NG0569:17154: badzra ta ki ni hri sta ya /
NG0569:17162: pra be sha ya pra be sha ya /
NG0569:17164: sa ma ya man d+ha la hu~m dza /
NG0569:17165: ma ha su ka a ti pu ho /
NG0569:17169: om sarba ta tha ga ta /
NG0569:17171: ma ha kro d+ha ra tsa ya /
NG0569:17173: shri he ru ka ma ha ban tsa badzra sa ma ya /
NG0569:17177: dz+nyan badzra ma ha ba la ti /
NG0569:17180: ma ha kro ti shwa ri dz+nya na d+ha ki ni prad nya da du badzra da ra /
NG0569:17181: om ru lu ru lu hu~m b+h+yo hu~m /
NG0569:17187: sarba ma ha badzra kro d+hi /
NG0569:17188: ka ya badzra kri ta ya /
NG0569:17192: na mahsarba ta tha ga te b+h+yo /
NG0569:17193: bi sha mu khe b+h+yahsarba tha khang ud ga te /
NG0569:17194: s+pha ra na i mam ga ga na kham swa ha /
NG0569:17195: om shri badzra ra ga d+hu pe du /
NG0569:17200: pu tsa me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye swa ha /
NG0569:17202: sarba ta tha ga ta ma ha pany+tsa a mri ta /
NG0569:17203: rba na kha ram hri ka sa badzra si ti om /
NG0569:17206: om na ma sarba ta tha ga ta /
NG0569:17207: ma ha pu tsa me ka ya ra na /
NG0569:17208: badzra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko\u0f85ham /
NG0569:17217: ma ha me tha maha pan tsa a mri ta /
NG0569:17218: kha hi kha hi kha hi /
NG0569:17222: sa ma ya kha ha ho /
NG0569:17223: i dam ma ha ba ling ta /
NG0569:17228: sa ma ya hu~m b+h+yo hu~m /
NG0569:17229: sha ra lam ga tsa me /
NG0569:17230: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa mngon par rtogs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0569:17231: 'phrin las rim pa'i le'u ste dgu brgya gnyis pa'o
NG0569:17232: // // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen pos rnal
NG0569:17234: rang bzhin rnam dag chos nyid las //
NG0569:17235: dpal chen khro rgyal he ru ka / ye shes lnga yi dbang bskur zhing *//
NG0569:17236: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs //
NG0569:17237: khro chung khrab chags bzhin du brtan nas //
NG0569:17238: thugs khar 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad dang *//
NG0569:17239: rdo rje rtse dgu kha gdengs dang *//
NG0569:17241: pad+ma 'dab brgyad dbang gi cho ga / rdo rje rgya gram ljang khu gnas //
NG0569:17242: ye shes sems dpa' rigs kyi mdog / zhal gcig phyag gnyis khro bo'i sku //
NG0569:17243: mthu mar rang sngags 'phreng ba dang *//
NG0569:17244: bsgom dbyangs yi ge 'bru brgyad gsal //
NG0569:17245: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer gyis //
NG0569:17246: chos kyi dbyings nyid rab 'byams su //
NG0569:17247: sangs rgyas rnams kyi thugs la thim //
NG0569:17248: mchod phul rgyud bskul dngos grub bsdus //
NG0569:17249: byang chub sems dpa' 'gro don bskul //
NG0569:17250: sems can sgo gsum sgrib pa sbyangs //
NG0569:17252: lus ngag yid gsum sgrib pa sbyangs //
NG0569:17253: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rdzogs //
NG0569:17254: mgal me'i 'khor lo bzhin du bsgom //
NG0569:17255: mchod dang bstod pa sum yar bya //
NG0569:17256: tshogs kyi 'khor lo ci nus bskor //
NG0569:17257: de ltar gsang sngags bzlas tshur ni //
NG0569:17258: rang rang sngags dang bsgom dbyangs brgyad //
NG0569:17259: tshom bu thig le stong brgya bcu //
NG0569:17260: gtso 'khor dag kyang de bzhin no //
NG0569:17261: dril ba'i snying po kun la bsdeb //
NG0569:17262: 'di ltar ma yengs bsgom bzlas na //
NG0569:17264: nas ring po mi thogs par //
NG0569:17265: ngo mtshar drod rtags nges par 'byung *//
NG0569:17266: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub blang *//
NG0569:17269: om d+harma ka ya shu dz+nya ta dz+nya /
NG0569:17271: bud d+ha ma ha shri he ru ka ma ha kro d+ha hu~m phat /
NG0569:17272: om badzra ka ya a ta ri sha dz+nya na mo ta /
NG0569:17273: badzra ma ha shri he ru ka ma ha tsan d+ha hu~m phat /
NG0569:17274: om sam bo ka ya sa man ta dz+nya na mo ta na /
NG0569:17275: rat+ta ma ha shri he ru ka ma ha u kra ya hu~m phat /
NG0569:17276: om bo d+hi ka ya pra ta ba sha dz+nya na mo ta na /
NG0569:17277: pad+ma ma ha shri he ru ka maha kri ta hu~m phat /
NG0569:17278: om nir ma ka ya krin da dz+nya na mo ta na /
NG0569:17279: karma maha shri he ru ka ma ha rak+sha hu~m phat /
NG0569:17280: om bud d+ha thad ra pradz+nya da du ma ha kro d+hi shwa ri ni hu~m phat /
NG0569:17281: badzra rat+na pad+ma karma da ra pradz+nya da du ma ha kro d+ha shwa ri hu~m phat /
NG0569:17282: hu~m ya man ta krid pa tsa pa tsa phat /
NG0569:17283: hu~m pad mam ta kr-id hu lu hu lu phat /
NG0569:17284: hu~m bi g+h+nan ta krid tshin d+ha tshin d+ha hu~m phat /
NG0569:17285: om d+harma d+ha du dz+nyi na ka ya ma ha
NG0569:17286: bi ra shri he ru ka badzra ma ha kro
NG0569:17288: prad dz+nya ma ha kro d+hi sho ri /
NG0569:17289: badzra kro d+ha ma ha pa la ti /
NG0569:17293: om ru lu ru lu hu~m b+h+yo hu~m /
NG0569:17294: khro rgyal yab yum la sogs te /
NG0569:17295: thams cad 'dus pa'i snying po sngags /
NG0569:17297: byin brlabs dpag med sangs rgyas sa /
NG0569:17299: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa don gyi snying po'i rgyud las /
NG0569:17300: bsam gtan gsang sngags kyi le'u ste dgu brgya gsum
NG0569:17301: pa'o // // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen gyis
NG0569:17302: / mthar thug de kho na nyid bshad /
NG0569:17303: om ye shes lhun grub nyid /
NG0569:17304: a zhes chos dbyings ye shes te //
NG0569:17305: rnam par snang mdzad de ni rigs //
NG0569:17306: khro rgyal bud d+ha he ru ka zla tshes mnyam nyid ye shes te //
NG0569:17307: rnam par snang mdzad de bzhin rigs //
NG0569:17308: khro rgyal rat+na he ru ka rna ru kunartog ye shes te //
NG0569:17309: snang ba mtha' yas pad+ma'i rigs //
NG0569:17310: khro rgyal pad+ma he ru ka / thig le me long ye shes te //
NG0569:17311: rdo rje sems dpa' rdo rje'i rigs //
NG0569:17312: khro rgyal badzra he ru ka bya ba grub pa'i ye shes te //
NG0569:17313: don yod grub pa las kyi rigs //
NG0569:17314: khro rgyal karma he ru ka / rang 'byung ye shes rang shar ba'o //
NG0569:17315: sa rus sangs rgyas spyan nyid de //
NG0569:17316: bud d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri'o //
NG0569:17317: khrag chu ma ma ki nyid ni //
NG0569:17319: me dang drod ni gos dkar mo //
NG0569:17320: pad ma kro d+hi shwa ri'o //
NG0569:17321: rlung 'byung dam tshig sgrol ma ste //
NG0569:17323: rnam rig nam mkha'i dbyings phyug ma /
NG0569:17325: 'byung ba chen po ye sangs rgyas //
NG0569:17326: de ni phung po skye mched khams //
NG0569:17327: gdod nas sangs rgyas ye shes lha //
NG0569:17328: rang gnas dkyil 'khor rtogs par bya //
NG0569:17329: rtogs mchog ma spangs gnas su dag / sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa yis //
NG0569:17330: snying po'i thig le gsang sngags kyis //
NG0569:17331: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NG0569:17334: chen khro rgyal dpal chen he ru ka / mtshan don lhun grub chos rnams rdzogs //
NG0569:17335: he zhes dngos med byang chub sems //
NG0569:17336: chos nyid ma bcos rnam dag dbyings //
NG0569:17337: sgrib med ye shes rab gsal bas //
NG0569:17338: thams cad der rdzogs dgyes pa che //
NG0569:17339: ru zhes thugs rje kun la khyab //
NG0569:17340: rang bzhin thugs kyi mnyam nyid las //
NG0569:17341: dmigs pa med cing phyogs rigs bral //
NG0569:17342: chags med chags mchog rgyal po'o //
NG0569:17343: ka zhes rol pa cir yang snang *//
NG0569:17344: sna tshogs rang snang ngos bzung med //
NG0569:17345: thabs mkhas 'phrin las rnam mang bas //
NG0569:17346: 'gro don sna tshogs so sor mdzad //
NG0569:17347: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi thugs //
NG0569:17348: dngos po rnam dag ma bcos pa //
NG0569:17349: dngos med mu mtha' med pa nyid //
NG0569:17350: rang bzhin stong chen mtha' yas 'das //
NG0569:17351: 'dus ma byas pa'i chos dbyings de //
NG0569:17352: chos dbyings kro d+hi shwa ri ste //
NG0569:17353: gnyis med bde chen byang chub sems //
NG0569:17354: dbyings nyid ye shes dbyer med pas //
NG0569:17355: dpal chen ye shes mtshan rdzogs pa'o //
NG0569:17357: gnyis med byang chub sems su gsal //
NG0569:17358: snying po byang chub sems nyid de //
NG0569:17359: rgya ma chad cing phyogs ma lhung *//
NG0569:17360: rang byung ye shes rang gsal bas //
NG0569:17361: skye med 'gag med thog mtha' med //
NG0569:17362: rang byung kun khyab 'dus ma byas //
NG0569:17364: de nyid dpal chen he ru ka / lhun grub rang rig ye shes gnyis //
NG0569:17365: ma 'gags rang snang gnyis med pa'o //
NG0569:17367: rig pa brdal khyab ma bcos pa //
NG0569:17368: phyogs med rang snang snying po ste //
NG0569:17370: ru lu 'khor ba'i rnam shes brgyad //
NG0569:17371: / gnas kyi ma mo ki ri brgyad //
NG0569:17372: ma spangs gnas dag rang bzhin te //
NG0569:17373: chos nyid byang chub sems nyid gsal //
NG0569:17374: ru lu yul brgyad snang srid chos //
NG0569:17375: ye nas gnas dag 'phra men brgyad //
NG0569:17376: skye med rnam dag chos nyid de //
NG0569:17377: mtha' la 'das pa'i chos nyid do //
NG0569:17378: hu~m ni yul sems rang snang kun //
NG0569:17379: byang chub sems nyid rang snang bas //
NG0569:17380: he ru ka dpal ngo bo nyid //
NG0569:17381: gnyis med byang chub sems su gcig / b+h+yo /
NG0569:17382: sna tshogs rig pa'i rang bzhin te //
NG0569:17383: rig pa stong gsal ma 'gags shar //
NG0569:17384: de nyid dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad //
NG0569:17387: sna tshogs cir snang de bzhin nyid //
NG0569:17388: ma bcos rang snang ji bzhin nyid //
NG0569:17389: phyag rgya bzhi ldan ye shes te /
NG0569:17391: de nyid rang byung ye shes te //
NG0569:17392: sangs rgyas kun gyi snying po'o //
NG0569:17393: de nyid rang gi sems nyid de //
NG0569:17394: rang sems ma bcos mnyam par bzhag / rig pa brdal khyab ngos bzung med //
NG0569:17395: cir snang ye shes ngo bor shar //
NG0569:17396: ma yengs ji bzhin ngang gnas na //
NG0569:17397: mdzad spyod ma chags blang dor med //
NG0569:17398: ma bsgrubs chos sku lhun gyis grub //
NG0569:17401: 'gro ba las dag thams cad la //
NG0569:17402: mngon par snang de don mdzad do //
NG0569:17404: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa snying po gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NG0569:17405: mthar thug de kho na nyid kyi le'u ste dgu
NG0569:17406: brgya bzhi'o // // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen
NG0569:17407: gyis / drag po las kyi rim pa bshad //
NG0569:17408: phung sa gsum gyi 'brub khung ni //
NG0569:17409: gru gsum rgya dpangs khru mtho gang *//
NG0569:17410: kha khyer dang po thod rlon 'phreng *//
NG0569:17411: bar pa mtsher rtsa srin mo 'gros //
NG0569:17412: mtha' ma gdug pa'i sbrul rigs bzhi //
NG0569:17413: phyi nang dug khrag sna tshogs drug / dgra la
NG0569:17414: rgyu rten drug ling ga / bgegs la gang gnod
NG0569:17415: rdzas kyi gzugs // mtho gang dbang po dod par bya //
NG0569:17416: gro ga ming byang khong par brnag / tsha ba gsum dang dug sna tshogs *//
NG0569:17417: nad khrag sna tshogs byug par bya //
NG0569:17418: khram thod bcug la dong du brnag / dug rgod sbyang dug ra dug pa //
NG0569:17419: 'ol mo re lcag ba spru ba //
NG0569:17420: mon pa kha byung thod par bsham //
NG0569:17421: mi yi nang khrag sna tshogs dang *//
NG0569:17422: gcan gzan sna tshogs ra khyi rta //
NG0569:17423: khrag sna snying sna gri thod sbyar //
NG0569:17424: yungs kar yungs nag ske tshe dang *//
NG0569:17425: ji tse shang tse rdo lcags zangs //
NG0569:17426: phye gsum rabs chad thod par sbyar //
NG0569:17427: gri thod lcags phur seng ldeng mchog phur pa dug khrag ngar blud bsham //
NG0569:17428: bdag nyid dpal chen he ru ka / las byed pho nya sprul pa'i tshogs //
NG0569:17429: shin tu rngam khros mi bzod pas //
NG0569:17430: srog gcod sha za khrag 'thung bsam //
NG0569:17431: des ni brnag pa gang yin pa //
NG0569:17432: rang dbang med bkug rten la bstim //
NG0569:17433: ling ga dgra bgegs dngos su bsam //
NG0569:17434: dug thun bud med 'jigs tshul rngam //
NG0569:17435: khrag thun sha za srin po'i tshogs //
NG0569:17436: 'bru phye mon dang mon mo'i tshogs //
NG0569:17437: shin tu 'jigs khros mtshon cha thogs //
NG0569:17438: nad kyi bskal pa 'bebs byed cing *//
NG0569:17439: dgra bgegs srog gcod sha za bsam //
NG0569:17440: phur pa khro bo'i 'jigs tshul rngam //
NG0569:17441: smad dbal lcags sa thog ltar bsam //
NG0569:17442: drag sngags brgya thun stong thun dbab //
NG0569:17443: srog lus rdul phran brlags par bsam //
NG0569:17444: de nas phur pas gdab par bya //
NG0569:17445: srog lus go cha phyag rgyar bskyed //
NG0569:17446: 'di ltar drag sngags sbyor ba yis //
NG0569:17447: tshangs pa'i tshe dang ldan pa yang *//
NG0569:17449: dgra bgegs rnams la smos ci dgos //
NG0569:17450: ma ma trag rag sha kha lding nag mo //
NG0569:17451: rag mo shan pa dgra bo la ma ra ya dza dza //
NG0569:17452: rag sha rbad ling dgra bo snying khrag tshal pa rbad /
NG0569:17453: ru tra ma tra ma ra ya ha li ha
NG0569:17454: li dgra bo la dun b+h+yo ma ra ya rbad
NG0569:17455: / badzra ki li ya tig sna ha na ha na nri ma ra ya rbad /
NG0569:17456: bsad pa dregs pa can la gtad /
NG0569:17457: gzir ba bka' gnyan mgon pi la'o //
NG0569:17458: thun 'phangs sprul pas nad mtshon dbab //
NG0569:17459: nad byo sngags mthar skabs kyis brdeb //
NG0569:17460: drod tshad ldan byas myur du 'grub //
NG0569:17461: bskal pa nyi shu'i tha ma la //
NG0569:17463: rgyas mu stegs bdag gzhan sdes //
NG0569:17464: lha srin dregs sngags pho mo rnams //
NG0569:17465: mthu rtsal stobs ldan dmod pa 'bor //
NG0569:17466: sprul pa sha zan skar ltar 'khrug / dmod ba'i mtshon cha char ltar 'bab //
NG0569:17467: byin brlabs mthu stobs me ltar 'bar //
NG0569:17468: sngags pa rdo rje dme 'thab byed //
NG0569:17469: de tsho rang gi byed sdebs sngags //
NG0569:17470: phyir la bzlog cing de nyid bsad //
NG0569:17472: rang bzhin rnam dag chos nyid las //
NG0569:17473: brub yig dmar nag yongs gyur las //
NG0569:17474: dbang drag 'khor lo rtsibs bcug pa //
NG0569:17475: rno la rgya chen me 'bar ba //
NG0569:17476: lte ba hu~m yig yongs gyur las //
NG0569:17477: dpal chen bud d+ha he ru ka / yab yum sangs rgyas dbang phyug ma //
NG0569:17478: gsal rdzogs bsgom pa'i thugs kha nas //
NG0569:17479: rtsibs bcu'i gdan la hu~m bcu 'phros //
NG0569:17480: de dag yongs su gyur pa las //
NG0569:17481: shar rtsibs badzra he ru ka / khro mo rdo rje dbang phyug bsgom //
NG0569:17482: lho rtsibs rat+na he ru ka / khro mo rin chen dbang phyug bsgom //
NG0569:17483: nub rtsibs pad+ma he ru ka khro mo dbang phyug pad+ma bsgom //
NG0569:17484: byang rtsibs karma he ru ka / khro mo las kyi dbang phyug bsgom //
NG0569:17485: shar lho gshin rje mthar byed gnas //
NG0569:17486: lho nub shes rab mthar byed gnas //
NG0569:17487: nub byang pad+ma mthar byed gnas //
NG0569:17488: steng rtsibs gtsug gtor 'khor lo sgyur //
NG0569:17489: ser nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa //
NG0569:17490: spyan gsum mche gtsigs rin chen brgyan //
NG0569:17491: 'khor lo ral gri phyag na bsnams //
NG0569:17492: lha chen gdan la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NG0569:17493: 'og rtsibs rdo rje hu~m mdzad de //
NG0569:17494: mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis pas //
NG0569:17495: rdo rje dgra sta phyag na bsnams //
NG0569:17496: ma bdud gdan brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NG0569:17497: ye shes 'khor lo spyan drangs bstim //
NG0569:17498: dbang bskur byin brlabs skye mched brlab //
NG0569:17499: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa 'bul //
NG0569:17500: bdud rtsi myang zhing bstod pa bya //
NG0569:17502: drag tu 'khor zhing gang dmigs pa'i //
NG0569:17503: lha srung rig sngags bcad bzlog gsad //
NG0569:17504: de bzhin dur khrod rab la bri //
NG0569:17505: rtsibs bzhi lte bar hu~m bcu gcig / mu khyud nang mar rtsa ba'i sngags //
NG0569:17506: phyi mar spu bri'i drag sngags dgos //
NG0569:17507: rig sngags drag po smra bcad bzlas //
NG0569:17508: bdud bzhi nyon mongs dug lnga gcad //
NG0569:17510: bsrung dang bzlog dang bsad pa dang *//
NG0569:17511: byang chub bsgrub pa'i las rnams 'grub //
NG0569:17512: rgyu rten ling ga ming byang bcas //
NG0569:17513: snying khar mtshon cha'i 'khor lo gzhug sgrub khang rgyun srang rten la mnan //
NG0569:17514: de dag gsang sngags 'di lta ste //
NG0569:17515: na ma sa man ta ka ya ba ka tsit+ta badzra he ru ka ni /
NG0569:17516: om a hu~m badzra ma ha kro d+ha ra dza ya /
NG0569:17517: shri he he ru ru ka ka ma ha tsan d+ha u kra ye hu~m /
NG0569:17518: badzra kro d+ha pa la ti ma ha kro d+ha ra dza ya /
NG0569:17520: ma ha kro d+hi shwa ri ma ha yo gi ni tsin+da da ki ni /
NG0569:17538: 'khor lo bskor zhing sngags bzlas pas /
NG0569:17539: 'byung ba'i rgyun kyang phyir bzlog na /
NG0569:17540: sngags byang sbod gtong smos ci dgos /

NG0569:17924: da mun ha du sti rag sha ya tsa thum
NG0569:17925: thum ra tri ru shag kri ka ra shu la
NG0569:17926: ma ma bam hi mang du ru /
NG0569:17927: dgra bo tsit+ta ro myags rbad ma ra ya rbad b+h+yo /
NG0569:17928: dregs pa can gyis sbyor ba ni /
NG0569:17929: me lce btsan dug khol ma 'dra //
NG0569:17930: dam nyams rang srog nyams par 'gyur //
NG0569:17931: dam nyams dus las 'gyang mi srid //
NG0569:17932: 'jam dpal khros pa'i rgyal po khri drug stong pa'i rgyud las /
NG0569:17933: dregs pa bzhi sreg gi le'u ste dgu brgya dgu
NG0569:17934: bcu rtsa dgu pa'o // // de nas rdo rje
NG0569:17935: dpal chen pos / mtha' rgya bsdus pa 'di bshad do //
NG0569:17936: drag po bsad pa'i mtha' rgya ru //
NG0569:17937: mnan gtad las kyi sbyor bas btul //
NG0569:17938: de yang ji ltar bya zhe na //
NG0569:17939: khrims ldan btsun pa dgrar langs na //
NG0569:17940: bud med yugs mo'i thod par bcug / dme khrag bskus la zhabs mas gril //
NG0569:17941: lha khang rgyal the la mnan na //
NG0569:17943: sngags pa nag po dgrar langs na //
NG0569:17944: mdze can dmar chod thod par bcug / dug dang
NG0569:17945: rme ba'i rdzas kyis byug / dmangs ris nag po'i
NG0569:17946: klu la gtad // bsrung khog mdze shus 'chi bar nges //
NG0569:17947: mi yi rgyal po dgrar langs na //
NG0569:17948: ma smin mi yi thod par gzhug / dug sna byugs la zhing lpags gril //
NG0569:17949: mtsho bdud klu bdud la gtad na //
NG0569:17952: bon po dgrar langs rme ba'i rdzas //
NG0569:17953: sna tshogs tshil chen byug byas te //
NG0569:17954: rabs chad nag po'i thod par gzhug / brag bdud dur bdud la gtad na //
NG0569:17956: skye bo phal pa dgrar langs na //
NG0569:17957: dri bo dmar chod thod par gzhug / gri thag
NG0569:17958: dug sna tshil chen byug / gong gsum yul btsan
NG0569:17959: la gtad na // gri rgod dag gis 'cho bar nges //
NG0569:17960: bud med dri mo'i thod par gzhug / dug sna
NG0569:17961: khrag sna mngal khrag byug / lha btsan bdud btsan
NG0569:17962: la gtad na // lcebs sam khyo pos gsod par nges //
NG0569:17963: gshin rje gshed kyi rtogs pa'i rgyal po khri drug stong pa'i rgyud chen po las /
